#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you already know your way around your operating system, you probably also "
"know how to start &amarok;, and you can <link linkend=\"first-time"
"\">continue</link>. Else, continue reading."
msgstr ""
"Če že poznate svoj operacijski sistem, verjetno znate tudi zagnati &amarok; "
"in lahko <link linkend=\"first-time\">nadaljujete</link>. Sicer pa "
"nadaljujte z branjem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "From Plasma"
msgstr "Iz Plasme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are running the <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"mylanguage/Plasma\">Plasma Workspace</ulink>, you can start &amarok; by "
"either:"
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/Plasma"
"\">delovni prostor Plasma</ulink>, lahko zaženete &amarok; bodisi z:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"pressing on <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/Kickoff"
"\">Kickoff</ulink> and then <menuchoice><guimenu>Multimedia</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Amarok</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"pritisnite <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/Kickoff"
"\">Kickoff</ulink> in nato <menuchoice><guimenu>Multimedia</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Amarok</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"invoking <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/KRunner"
"\">KRunner</ulink> (<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> by "
"default), entering <varname>amarok</varname> and then pressing &Enter;."
msgstr ""
"priklic <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/KRunner"
"\">KRunner</ulink> (<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> privzeto), "
"vnesite <varname>amarok</varname> in nato pritisnite &Enter;."

