#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the file manager"
msgstr "Iz upravljalnika datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a multimedia file that &amarok; is known to play."
msgstr ""
"Odprite večpredstavnostno datoteko, ki je &amarok;u znana, da jo predvaja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "First Time"
msgstr "Prvič"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first time you use &amarok;, a dialog box will come up asking you to "
"specify your locale:"
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič uporabite &amarok;, se bo prikazalo pogovorno okno, v katerem boste "
"morali določiti svoje jezikovno okolje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, a First Start dialog box will come up asking you to specify where your "
"music is located. If you have a music directory already <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/paths\">configured in your system</ulink>, &amarok; should detect "
"it and ask you to use it:"
msgstr ""
"Nato se prikaže pogovorno okno Prvi zagon, v katerem morate določiti, kje se "
"nahaja vaša glasba. Če imate glasbeni imenik že <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"paths\">konfiguriran v vašem sistemu</ulink>, &amarok; naj ga zazna in vas "
"prosi, da ga uporabite:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <guilabel>No</guilabel> in this dialog, you will be presented "
"with another one which allows you to select your music folder:"
msgstr ""
"Če v tem pogovornem oknu izberete <guilabel>Ne</guilabel>, se vam prikaže "
"drugo, ki vam omogoča izbiro glasbene mape:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"setting-up-a-collection\">Setting Up a Collection</link>"
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"setting-up-a-collection\">Nastavitev zbirke</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have selected the folder where your music is, &amarok; will scan "
"the folder and sub-folders, creating the collection. This can take some "
"time, depending on the number of tracks and the speed of the location."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete mapo, v kateri je vaša glasba, &amarok; skenira mapo in podmape "
"ter ustvari zbirko. To lahko traja nekaj časa, odvisno od števila skladb in "
"hitrosti lokacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closing Amarok"
msgstr "Zapiranje Amaroka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to close &amarok;:"
msgstr "Če želite zapreti &amarok;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> when you are in the "
"&amarok; window, or"
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>, ko ste v oknu "
"&amarok; okno, ali"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the <guilabel>Quit</guilabel> option in the &amarok; menu, or"
msgstr "Izberite možnost <guilabel>Zapri</guilabel> v oknu &amarok; meni, ali"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click on the blue wolf icon in the <guilabel>System Tray</guilabel> at "
"the bottom of your screen. You will be presented with the following:"
msgstr ""
"Z desno miškino tipko kliknite ikono modrega volka v <guilabel>Sistemski "
"vrstici</guilabel> na dnu zaslona. Predstavljeno vam bo naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you close the &amarok; window by clicking <guilabel>Close</guilabel> on "
"the window border, &amarok; will continue to run in the background and only "
"show the blue wolf icon in the <guilabel>System Tray</guilabel>:"
msgstr ""
"Če zaprete &amarok; s klikom na <guilabel>Zapri</guilabel> na meji okna, bo "
"&amarok; še naprej deloval v ozadju in prikazal samo ikono modrega volka v "
"<guilabel>Sistemski vrstici</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you log out of your session or shut down your computer without quitting "
"&amarok;, some of your settings will not be saved."
msgstr ""
"Če se odjavite iz seje ali zaustavite računalnik, ne da bi zapustili "
"&amarok;, nekatere vaše nastavitve ne bodo shranjene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Amarok window"
msgstr "Okno Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &amarok; window is designed to let you rediscover your music. So, it "
"gives you as much information about your music as possible. While many users "
"will enjoy the default layout, it is fully customizable."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; okno je zasnovano tako, da vam omogoča ponovno odkrivanje vaše "
"glasbe. Tako vam daje čim več informacij o vaši glasbi. Čeprav bo veliko "
"uporabnikov uživalo v privzeti postavitvi, je ta popolnoma prilagodljiva."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default layout of the Amarok window"
msgstr "Privzeta postavitev okna Amarok"

