msgstr "<phrase>Amarok 2.8, na novo nameščen</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Amarok 2.8, newly installed</para>"
msgstr "<para>Amarok 2.8, na novo nameščen</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &amarok; window has four main parts:"
msgstr "&amarok; Okno ima štiri glavne dele:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"under the top-level menus is the <emphasis>Toolbar</emphasis> which lies "
"above three panes:"
msgstr ""
"pod meniji na najvišji ravni je <emphasis>Orodna vrstica</emphasis>, ki leži "
"nad tremi podokni:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"your <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> (music collection and other media) "
"in the left pane,"
msgstr ""
"vaši <guilabel>medijski viri</guilabel> (glasbena zbirka in drugi mediji) v "
"levem podoknu,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <guilabel>Context</guilabel> pane in the center, and"
msgstr "podokno <guilabel>Kontekst</guilabel> na sredini in"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> in the right-hand pane."
msgstr "<guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel> v desnem podoknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Amarok window to manage and play your music"
msgstr "Uporaba okna Amarok za upravljanje in predvajanje glasbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing music using &amarok; usually takes two steps:"
msgstr "Predvajanje glasbe z &amarok; običajno zahteva dva koraka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a playlist by selecting some of the tracks in your collection, which "
"you will find listed in the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane, and "
"send your music to the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite seznam predvajanja tako, da izberete nekaj skladb v svoji zbirki, "
"ki jih boste našli na seznamu v podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>, "
"in pošljite svojo glasbo v podokno <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Play the music in your playlist, using the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> "
"pane and/or the Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Predvajajte glasbo na svojem seznamu predvajanja z uporabo podokna "
"<guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel> in/ali orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also, you may want to transfer some of your music to a mobile music player, "
"such as an iPod. The next sections will explain how."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako boste morda želeli prenesti nekaj vaše glasbe v mobilni "
"predvajalnik glasbe, kot je iPod. V naslednjih razdelkih bo pojasnjeno, kako."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Music Collection"
msgstr "Glasbena zbirka"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:273 index.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Media Sources pane"
msgstr "Podokno Medijski viri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane is the place where you browse "
"and display your complete collection of music. This includes the tracks on "
"your local hard disk, as well as those on any external devices or media "
"connected to your computer, such as audio CD, USB devices, media players, "
"network disks or Internet sources."
msgstr ""
"Podokno <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel> je mesto, kjer brskate in "
"prikazujete celotno zbirko glasbe. To vključuje skladbe na vašem lokalnem "
"trdem disku, pa tudi tiste na zunanjih napravah ali medijih, povezanih z "
"vašim računalnikom, kot so avdio CD, naprave USB, predvajalniki medijev, "
"omrežni diski ali internetni viri."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting up a collection"
msgstr "Postavitev zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do you have music tracks in <emphasis>mp3</emphasis>, <emphasis>Ogg</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>FLAC</emphasis> format on your computer? Begin by "
"telling &amarok; where to find those files, so it can create your "
"collection. In the top-level menu: <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Local "
"Collection</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Ali imate v računalniku skladbe v formatu <emphasis>mp3</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Ogg</emphasis> ali <emphasis>FLAC</emphasis>? Začnite tako, da "
"&amarok;u poveste; kje najti te datoteke, da lahko ustvari vašo zbirko. V "
"meniju na najvišji ravni: <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Lokalna "
"zbirka</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure Collection Dialog, as of version 2.8</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguriraj pogovorno okno zbirke od različice 2.8</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Configure Collection Dialog, as of version 2.8</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo zbirke, od različice 2.8</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A tree-view of your home directory is shown above. Click the check box where "
"your music is stored; usually <menuchoice><guimenu>home</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Music</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then choose "
"<guilabel>Fully Rescan Entire Collection</guilabel>. This will take some "
"time, so do not be alarmed if &amarok; seems slow for a while. Once the scan "
"is complete, it is best to quit &amarok; using the top-level &amarok; menu, "
"or <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>, and then restart it. Your "
"newly-added music should show up under the <guilabel>Local Collection</"
"guilabel> section."
msgstr ""
"Drevesni pogled vašega domačega imenika je prikazan zgoraj. Kliknite "
"potrditveno polje, kjer je shranjena vaša glasba; običajno "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>domov</guimenu><guimenuitem>Glasba</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Nato izberite <guilabel>Popolnoma ponovno preglej celotno "
"zbirko</guilabel>. To bo trajalo nekaj časa, zato naj vas ne skrbi, če "
"&amarok; nekaj časa deluje počasi. Ko je skeniranje končano, je najbolje, da "
"zaprete &amarok; z uporabo najvišje ravni &amarok; meni ali <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> in ga nato znova zaženite. Vaša na novo dodana "
"glasba bi se morala prikazati v razdelku <guilabel>Lokalna zbirka</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More about configuring your collection <link linkend=\"collection\">here</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Več o konfiguraciji vaše zbirke <link linkend=\"collection\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The set of multimedia formats recognized by &amarok; is not restricted to "
"those mentioned above; is controlled by the <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde."
"org/Special:Mylanguage/Phonon\">Phonon</ulink> back end."
msgstr ""
"Nabor večpredstavnostnih formatov, ki jih prepozna &amarok; ni omejeno na "
"zgoraj omenjene; nadzira zaledje<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"Mylanguage/Phonon\">Phonon</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Media Devices to the Collection"
msgstr "Dodajanje medijskih naprav v zbirko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Underneath the search bar near the top of the <guilabel>Media Sources</"
"guilabel> pane you see the different devices and/or content categories "
"within the <guilabel>Content Browser</guilabel>. If you insert an Audio CD "
"in the CD drive it will appear in the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> "
"pane, along with media players, thumb drives, and other USB devices. After "
"an external device has been mounted, it will show automatically within the "
"<guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane."
msgstr ""
"Pod iskalno vrstico blizu vrha podokna <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel> "
"vidite različne naprave in/ali kategorije vsebine znotraj "
"<guilabel>Brskalnika vsebin</guilabel>. Če zvočni CD vstavite v CD-pogon, se "
"bo prikazal v podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>, skupaj z "
"multimedijskimi predvajalniki, bliskovnimi pogoni in drugimi napravami USB. "
"Ko je zunanja naprava nameščena, se bo samodejno prikazala v podoknu "
"<guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a screenshot showing three connected sources with music: Audio CD, "
"mp3 player, and the <guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je posnetek zaslona, ki prikazuje tri povezane vire z glasbo: avdio "
"CD, mp3 predvajalnik in <guilabel>Lokalna zbirka</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ripping a CD into the collection"
msgstr "Ripanje CD-ja v zbirko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't have any music files on your computer, it's easy to "
"<emphasis>rip</emphasis> them (copy the tracks from your CDs to your "
"collection). Just pop in a CD, and right-click on the banner of the CD "
"device in the <guilabel>Content Browser</guilabel> to play, or copy to your "
"collection, which will rip and <emphasis>tag</emphasis> your tracks (see "
"image below). If you copy music from an audio CD to your <guilabel>Local "
"Collection</guilabel>, the <emphasis>message bar</emphasis> at the bottom of "
"the &amarok; window will indicate that it is busy copying. The ripping may "
"take several minutes. Once the rip is complete, the message in the message "
"bar disappears and the music appears in the content browser of your "
"<guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel>. If the ripped music does not appear "
"in your <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane it's best to quit &amarok; "
"from the &amarok; top-level menu, or <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></"
"keycombo>, and then restart it. Now you should see it in your collection. "
"The screenshot below shows how you move tracks from your audio CD, iPod or "
"other device to your collection, using the context (right-click) menu."
msgstr ""
"Če v računalniku nimate glasbenih datotek, jih lahko preprosto "
"<emphasis>ripate</emphasis> (kopirate skladbe s svojih CD-jev v svojo "
"zbirko). Samo vstavite CD in z desno miškino tipko kliknite pasico CD "
"naprave v <guilabel>Brskalniku vsebine</guilabel> za predvajanje ali "
"kopiranje v svojo zbirko, ki bo kopirala in <emphasis>označila</emphasis> "
"vaš skladbe (glej sliko spodaj). Če kopirate glasbo z zvočnega CD-ja v svojo "
"<guilabel>Lokalno zbirko</guilabel>, <emphasis>sporočilna vrstica</emphasis> "
"na dnu &amarok; okno bo pokazalo, da je zaposlen s kopiranjem. Kopiranje "
"lahko traja nekaj minut. Ko je kopiranje končano, sporočilo v vrstici s "
"sporočili izgine in glasba se prikaže v brskalniku vsebine vaše "
"<guilabel>Lokalne zbirke</guilabel>. Če se kopirana glasba ne prikaže v "
"podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>, je najbolje, da zaprete &amarok; "
"iz &amarok; meni najvišje ravni ali <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></"
"keycombo> in ga nato znova zaženite. Zdaj bi ga morali videti v svoji "
"zbirki. Spodnji posnetek zaslona prikazuje, kako premaknete skladbe z "
"zvočnega CD-ja, iPod-a ali druge naprave v svojo zbirko z uporabo "
"kontekstnega menija (desni klik)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the above context menu, you can also see the choice to <guilabel>Edit "
"Track Details</guilabel>. Use this option if you have a track that needs a "
"tag edited. This becomes important when you rip music to .WAV format, losing "
"some of the tags. If quite a bit of your collection needs tagging, consider "
"dedicated tagging software, such as"
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem kontekstnem meniju lahko vidite tudi izbiro <guilabel>Urejanje "
"podrobnosti skladbe</guilabel>. Uporabite to možnost, če imate skladbo, za "
"katero je treba urediti oznako. To postane pomembno, ko kopirate glasbo v "
"format .WAV in pri tem izgubite nekatere oznake. Če kar nekaj vaše zbirke "
"potrebuje označevanje, razmislite o namenski programski opremi za "
"označevanje, kot je"

#. Tag: ulink
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Picard"
msgstr "Picard"

#. Tag: ulink
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "EasyTag"
msgstr "EasyTag"

#. Tag: ulink
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kid3"
msgstr "Kid3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Correct tagging is important to help &amarok; show your tracks in the "
"appropriate albums and proper sort order. Learn more about <link linkend="
"\"tags\">ripping and tagging</link>."
msgstr ""
"Pravilno označevanje je pomembno za pomoč &amarok;u pokaže svoje skladbe v "
"ustreznih albumih in pravilnem vrstnem redu. Več o <link linkend=\"tags"
"\">ripanju in označevanju</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accessing other media sources"
msgstr "Dostop do drugih medijskih virov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might have wondered why the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane is "
"not called the 'Collections' pane. &amarok; gives you access to much more "
"music than just your collection -- Internet shops, audio books, podcasts, "
"music files stored outside your collection, and previously stored playlists. "
"The &amarok; <emphasis>breadcrumb navigation</emphasis> is the key to all of "
"this. The starting icon for the breadcrumb navigation is the home folder "
"icon at the extreme top left of the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane. "
"This icon expands and contracts as you browse through the <guilabel>Media "
"Sources</guilabel> pane, allowing you to easily navigate your collection by "
"clicking your desired folder in the breadcrumb bar."
msgstr ""
"Morda ste se spraševali, zakaj se podokno <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel> "
"ne imenuje podokno 'Zbirke'. &amarok; vam omogoča dostop do veliko več "
"glasbe kot le vaše zbirke -- internetnih trgovin, zvočnih knjig, podcastov, "
"glasbenih datotek, shranjenih zunaj vaše zbirke, in predhodno shranjenih "
"seznamov predvajanja. &amarok; <emphasis>Navigacija po drobtinicah</"
"emphasis> je ključ do vsega tega. Začetna ikona za navigacijo po drobtinicah "
"je ikona domače mape v skrajnem zgornjem levem kotu podokna "
"<guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>. Ta ikona se razširi in skrči, ko brskate "
"po podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>, kar vam omogoča preprosto "
"krmarjenje po zbirki s klikom želene mape v vrstici drobtinic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click the &amarok; home folder you see the <guilabel>Media Sources</"
"guilabel> pane on the left below, containing icons to available resources. "
"If you click <guilabel>Files</guilabel> (left image below, second item from "
"the bottom), you will see something similar to the image on the right, "
"below. Notice how the breadcrumb bar expands and how the content of the "
"selected folder is shown in the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane "
"(right image below). Clicking the <guilabel>&gt;</guilabel> symbols among "
"the breadcrumbs allows you to view the folders available at that level of "
"the folder structure. The &amarok; file browser gives you access to your "
"entire file system, even outside your <guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete &amarok; domača mapa vidite podokno <guilabel>Medijski viri</"
"guilabel> na levi spodaj, ki vsebuje ikone razpoložljivih virov. Če kliknete "
"<guilabel>Datoteke</guilabel> (leva slika spodaj, drugi element od spodaj), "
"boste videli nekaj podobnega sliki na desni, spodaj. Opazite, kako se "
"vrstica z drobtinicami na dnu strani razširi in kako je vsebina izbrane mape "
"prikazana v podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel> (desna slika spodaj). "
"S klikom na simbole <guilabel>&gt;</guilabel> med drobnimi orodji si lahko "
"ogledate mape, ki so na voljo na tej ravni strukture map. &amarok; datotečni "
"brskalnik vam omogoča dostop do celotnega datotečnega sistema, tudi zunaj "
"vaše <guilabel>lokalne zbirke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Media Sources pane"
msgstr "Podokno Viri medijev"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files icon clicked"
msgstr "Klik na ikono datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The functions of the icons in the &amarok; Home folder (left above) are:"
msgstr "Funkcije ikon v aplikaciji &amarok; Domača mapa (levo zgoraj) je:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Icon</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Ikona</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:417 index.docbook:5263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:418 index.docbook:7932 index.docbook:8103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Action</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Dejanje</entry>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Local Music</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Lokalna glasba</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your &amarok; collection"
msgstr "Vaša zbirka &amarok;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Internet</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Internet</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Internet shops such as <emphasis>Magnatune</emphasis>, <emphasis>Jamendo</"
"emphasis> and <emphasis>Last.fm</emphasis>. First configure your internet "
"resources in: <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Internet Services</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Internetne trgovine, kot so <emphasis>Magnatune</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Jamendo</emphasis> in <emphasis>Last.fm</emphasis>. Najprej "
"konfigurirajte svoje internetne vire v: <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Internetne "
"storitve</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Playlists</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Seznami predvajanja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saved playlists -- see also <link linkend=\"playlists\">Playlists</link>. "
"Also playlists on media devices"
msgstr ""
"Shranjeni seznami predvajanja -- glejte tudi <link linkend=\"playlists"
"\">Seznami predvajanja</link>. Tudi seznami predvajanja na medijskih napravah"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Files</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Datoteke</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your file system"
msgstr "Vaš datotečni sistem"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Podcasts</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Podcasti</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access to Podcasts via RSS feed"
msgstr "Dostop do podcastov prek vira RSS"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>Local Music</guilabel> in the root of <guilabel>Media "
"Sources</guilabel> (image above) or in the breadcrumb bar returns you to "
"your collection, showing you a list of all the available resources, artists, "
"albums and tracks that you have previously defined as part of your "
"collection. The breadcrumb bar indicates that you are viewing "
"<guilabel>Local Music</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guilabel>Lokalna glasba</guilabel> v korenu <guilabel>Medijski "
"viri</guilabel> (slika zgoraj) ali v vrstici z drobtinicami, se vrnete v "
"vašo zbirko in prikažete seznam vseh razpoložljivih virov, izvajalcev, "
"albumi in skladbe, ki ste jih predhodno opredelili kot del svoje zbirke. "
"Vrstica navigacijskih poti kaže, da gledate <guilabel>Lokalno glasbo</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Streams and Podcasts"
msgstr "Tokovi in podcasti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two ways to listen to streams."
msgstr "Obstajata dva načina za poslušanje tokov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a favorite station, get the stream URL and add it: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlist</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Stream</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If you then save your playlist, later you can "
"find it again in <guilabel>Playlists</guilabel>, as a <emphasis>Saved "
"Playlist</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate priljubljeno postajo, pridobite URL toka in ga dodajte: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj tok</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če nato shranite seznam predvajanja, ga lahko "
"pozneje znova najdete v <guilabel>Seznamih predvajanja</guilabel> kot "
"<emphasis>Shranjenem seznamu predvajanja</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Browse through the scripts available in our <guilabel>Script Manager</"
"guilabel>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Script Manager</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> up to Amarok 2.4.0, after 2.4.1 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Scripts</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. There are some "
"excellent collections available, which will show up in the "
"<guilabel>Internet</guilabel> section of your <guilabel>Media</guilabel> "
"pane."
msgstr ""
"Prebrskajte med skripti, ki so na voljo v našem <guilabel>Upravljalnik "
"skriptov</guilabel>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljalniku skriptov</guimenuitem></menuchoice> do "
"Amarok 2.4.0, po 2.4 .1 <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Skripte</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Na voljo je nekaj odličnih zbirk, ki bodo "
"prikazane v razdelku <guilabel>Internet</guilabel> v podoknu "
"<guilabel>Mediji</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Podcasts have their own section in the <guilabel>Media</guilabel> pane, "
"above. If you have an RSS or Atom feed URL, click the <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> and add it there. If you have an OPML file "
"to import, that choice is available also. Use the context (right-click) "
"menus to <guilabel>Add to playlist</guilabel>, <guilabel>Configure</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Remove Subscription</guilabel>, <guilabel>Update "
"Channel</guilabel>, or mark an episode as <guilabel>New</guilabel>. If you "
"are interested in browsing through a large collection of podcasts, check out "
"the <guilabel>Podcast Directory</guilabel> available through the "
"<guilabel>Script Manager</guilabel>, referred to above."
msgstr ""
"Podcasti imajo svoj razdelek v zgornjem podoknu <guilabel>Mediji</guilabel>. "
"Če imate URL vira RSS ali Atom, kliknite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> in ga dodajte tja . Če imate datoteko OPML za uvoz, je na "
"voljo tudi ta izbira. Uporabite kontekstne (desni klik) menije za "
"<guilabel>Dodaj na seznam predvajanja</guilabel>, <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Odstrani naročnino</guilabel>, <guilabel>Posodobi "
"kanal</guilabel>, ali označite epizodo kot <guilabel>Novo</guilabel>. Če vas "
"zanima brskanje po veliki zbirki podcastov, si oglejte <guilabel>Imenik "
"podcastov</guilabel>, ki je na voljo prek zgoraj omenjenega "
"<guilabel>Upravljalnika skriptov</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More about configuring <guilabel>Amaroks</guilabel> <guilabel>Internet "
"Services</guilabel> <link linkend=\"internet-services\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Več o konfiguraciji <guilabel>Amaroks</guilabel> <guilabel>Internetnih "
"storitev</guilabel> <link linkend=\"internet-services\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Content Browser"
msgstr "Uporaba brskalnika vsebine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The hard disk of your computer, audio CDs, external devices and the Internet "
"are the basic resources for your collection. After your collection has been "
"set up, it is likely that your collection will hold a large number of albums "
"and tracks, much more than can be shown on a single window."
msgstr ""
"Trdi disk vašega računalnika, zvočni CD-ji, zunanje naprave in internet so "
"osnovni viri za vašo zbirko. Ko je vaša zbirka nastavljena, bo vaša zbirka "
"verjetno vsebovala veliko število albumov in skladb, veliko več, kot jih je "
"mogoče prikazati v enem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to change the display of your collection, below:"
msgstr "Kako spremeniti prikaz svoje zbirke, spodaj:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hiding or expanding information"
msgstr "Skrivanje ali širjenje informacij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The area of the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane below the search bar "
"is called the <guilabel>Content Browser</guilabel>. Three media sources are "
"indicated in the image of a <guilabel>Content Browser</guilabel> below: CD, "
"Local Collection and a Media Player:"
msgstr ""
"Območje podokna <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel> pod iskalno vrstico se "
"imenuje <guilabel>Brskalnik vsebin</guilabel>. Na spodnji sliki "
"<guilabel>Brskalnika vsebin</guilabel> so označeni trije medijski viri: CD, "
"lokalna zbirka in predvajalnik predstavnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the banner for a device (the blue bar for the Sansa above) shows or "
"hides the content of that device. The direction of the arrow on the right "
"indicates whether the contents for that device is hidden or shown. The "
"content on a particular device can, in turn, be hidden or shown using the "
"same principle, clicking on the appropriate artist or album. An arrow "
"pointing down on the left of an artist or an album indicates that the "
"contents has been expanded. An arrow pointing right indicates that more "
"content for that category is available but currently hidden. In the image "
"above, the information for <emphasis>Mike Oldfield - The Songs of Distant "
"Earth</emphasis> CD has been expanded, showing the individual tracks. On the "
"other hand, the albums and tracks in the <guilabel>Local Collection</"
"guilabel> are hidden. By clicking these arrows you also can expand or hide "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Klik na pasico za napravo (modra vrstica za Sansa zgoraj) prikaže ali skrije "
"vsebino te naprave. Smer puščice na desni kaže, ali je vsebina te naprave "
"skrita ali prikazana. Vsebino na določeni napravi lahko po istem principu "
"skrijete ali prikažete s klikom na ustreznega izvajalca ali album. Puščica, "
"ki kaže navzdol na levi strani izvajalca ali albuma, pomeni, da je bila "
"vsebina razširjena. Puščica, ki kaže desno, označuje, da je na voljo več "
"vsebine za to kategorijo, vendar je trenutno skrita. Na zgornji sliki so "
"bile informacije za CD <emphasis>Mike Oldfield – The Songs of Distant Earth</"
"emphasis> razširjene in prikazujejo posamezne skladbe. Po drugi strani pa so "
"albumi in skladbe v <guilabel>Lokalni zbirki</guilabel> skriti. S klikom na "
"te puščice lahko tudi razširite ali skrijete informacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the order of tracks and albums"
msgstr "Spreminjanje vrstnega reda skladb in albumov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The order in which tracks are sorted in the <guilabel>Content Browser</"
"guilabel> can be customised by using the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-preferences-other.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button at the top of the <guilabel>Media "
"Sources</guilabel> pane:"
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red, po katerem so skladbe razvrščene v <guilabel>Brskalniku vsebin</"
"guilabel>, je mogoče prilagoditi z uporabo <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-preferences-other.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> Gumb </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> na vrhu podokna <guilabel>Medijski viri</"
"guilabel>:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Collection sort options for version 2.8</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti razvrščanja zbirke za različico 2.8</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Collection sort options for version 2.8</para>"
msgstr "<para>Možnosti razvrščanja zbirke za različico 2.8</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sort order is indicated on the top left of the <guilabel>Media Sources</"
"guilabel> pane, just below the <guilabel>Search</guilabel> text box. The "
"default order is <guilabel>Artist / Year - Album</guilabel>. The display "
"order of the <guilabel>Content Browser</guilabel> can be temporarily "
"switched between the user-defined sort order (described above) and a "
"<emphasis>Merged view</emphasis> in which artists are listed alphabetically, "
"no matter on which media the music is stored. To toggle the <emphasis>Merged "
"view</emphasis>, click the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-view-list-tree.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> icon at the top right-hand of the <guilabel>Media "
"Sources</guilabel> pane:"
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red je prikazan v zgornjem levem kotu podokna <guilabel>Medijski "
"viri</guilabel>, tik pod besedilnim poljem <guilabel>Iskanje</guilabel>. "
"Privzeti vrstni red je <guilabel>Izvajalec/leto - album</guilabel>. Vrstni "
"red prikaza <guilabel>Brskalnika vsebine</guilabel> je mogoče začasno "
"preklopiti med uporabniško določenim vrstnim redom (opisanim zgoraj) in "
"<emphasis>Združenim pogledom</emphasis>, v katerem so izvajalci navedeni po "
"abecedi, ne glede na kateri medij je shranjena glasba. Če želite preklopiti "
"<emphasis>Združeni pogled</emphasis>, kliknite <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-view-list-tree.png\" format=\"PNG\"/"
"> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject > v zgornjem desnem kotu podokna "
"<guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To search your collection, type your search term into the <guilabel>Search "
"bar</guilabel> at the top of the <guilabel>Local Music</guilabel> section. "
"Not only can you search by artist, album or track name, but any part. You "
"might create a nice playlist by searching for <replaceable>winter</"
"replaceable>, for instance, or merely find a track when you only remember "
"one word of the title. You can also search by rating, playcount, even "
"filetype. See <link linkend=\"search-in-collection\">Search in Collection</"
"link> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje po zbirki vnesite iskalni izraz v <guilabel>Iskalno vrstico</"
"guilabel> na vrhu razdelka <guilabel>Lokalna glasba</guilabel>. Ne samo, da "
"lahko iščete po imenu izvajalca, albuma ali skladbe, ampak po katerem koli "
"delu. Ustvarite lahko lep seznam predvajanja tako, da na primer poiščete "
"<replaceable>winter</replaceable>, ali preprosto najdete skladbo, ko se "
"spomnite le ene besede naslova. Iščete lahko tudi po oceni, številu "
"predvajanj in celo vrsti datoteke. Za več podrobnosti glejte <link linkend="
"\"search-in-collection\">Iskanje v zbirki</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting items from the collection"
msgstr "Brisanje predmetov iz zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can delete any item from your collection by right-clicking on it and "
"choosing the bottom item <guilabel>Move Tracks to Trash</guilabel>. A "
"confirmation dialog will appear, preventing the accidental deletion of any "
"tracks. More than one item can be selected with <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>click</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Iz svoje zbirke lahko izbrišete kateri koli element tako, da ga kliknete z "
"desno tipko miške in izberete spodnji element <guilabel>Premakni skladbe v "
"koš</guilabel>. Prikaže se potrditveno pogovorno okno, ki preprečuje "
"nenamerno brisanje skladb. Več kot en element lahko izberete s "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>klik</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Playlists</title>"
msgstr "<title>Seznami predvajanja</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:605 index.docbook:1981
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Playlist pane"
msgstr "Podokno seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that &amarok; has scanned your collection of music, you want to listen "
"to it. So use the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane to create a playlist "
"containing the selection of tracks you want. This is where you play your "
"music, streams, or podcasts."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj ko je &amarok; pregledal vašo zbirko glasbe, jo želite poslušati. Zato "
"uporabite podokno <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel>, da ustvarite "
"seznam predvajanja, ki vsebuje izbrane skladbe, ki jih želite. Tukaj "
"predvajate svojo glasbo, tokove ali podcaste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can sort your playlist by title, album, artist, genre and many others. "
"For instance you can sort your tracks by year first, then by artist and so "
"on."
msgstr ""
"Seznam predvajanja lahko razvrstite po naslovu, albumu, izvajalcu, žanru in "
"mnogih drugih. Svoje skladbe lahko na primer najprej razvrstite po letu, "
"nato po izvajalcu in tako naprej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search box lets you search or filter your tracks. The "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-up.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> and <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> icons near the top of the "
"<guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane lets you skip to the next or previous "
"track containing the letters you have chosen. The <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button lets you filter your tracks by "
"artist, album, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Iskalno polje vam omogoča iskanje ali filtriranje skladb. "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-up.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> in <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> ikone na vrhu podokna <guilabel>Seznam "
"predvajanja</guilabel> vam omogočajo, da preskočite na naslednjo ali "
"prejšnjo skladbo, ki vsebuje črke, ki ste jih izbrali . Gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> omogoča filtriranje "
"skladb po izvajalcu, albumu, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout of the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> can be changed through the "
"top-level menu: <menuchoice><guimenu>Playlist</guimenu><guimenuitem>Playlist "
"Layouts</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev <guilabel>Seznama predvajanja</guilabel> lahko spremenite v "
"meniju na najvišji ravni: <menuchoice><guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Postavitve seznama predvajanja</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:615
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding music to a playlist"
msgstr "Dodajanje glasbe na seznam predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are five ways to add music to the playlist."
msgstr "Glasbo na seznam predvajanja lahko dodate na pet načinov."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Pop-up Dropper when adding a single track</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pojavna kaplja pri dodajanju posamezne skladbe</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Pop-up Dropper when adding a single track</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pojavna kaplja pri dodajanju posamezne skladbe</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose some of your music in the content browser and drag it to the right. "
"If you drag it over the <guilabel>Context</guilabel> pane you will see the "
"<emphasis>Pop-Up Dropper</emphasis>, also known as <emphasis>PUD</emphasis>. "
"The image above shows PUD in action. PUD provides three options: "
"<guilabel>Add to Playlist</guilabel>, <guilabel>Replace Playlist</guilabel>, "
"and <guilabel>More...</guilabel>. The option highlighted in the gray area "
"(<guilabel>Add to Playlist</guilabel> in this image) is the active one. "
"Dropping the album there adds it to the playlist in the <guilabel>Playlist</"
"guilabel> pane. Choose one of the other options to do something else with "
"your selection. Dragging it over <guilabel>More...</guilabel> brings up a "
"new menu of choices in <emphasis>PUD</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"V brskalniku vsebine izberite nekaj svoje glasbe in jo povlecite v desno. Če "
"ga povlečete čez podokno <guilabel>Kontekst</guilabel>, boste videli "
"<emphasis>Pojavno kapalko</emphasis>, znano tudi kot <emphasis>PUD</"
"emphasis>. Zgornja slika prikazuje PUD v akciji. PUD ponuja tri možnosti: "
"<guilabel>Dodaj na seznam predvajanja</guilabel>, <guilabel>Zamenjaj seznam "
"predvajanja</guilabel> in <guilabel>Več ...</guilabel>. Možnost, označena v "
"sivem območju (<guilabel>Dodaj na seznam predvajanja</guilabel> na tej "
"sliki), je aktivna. Če album spustite tja, ga dodate na seznam predvajanja v "
"podoknu <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel>. Izberite eno od drugih "
"možnosti, da naredite nekaj drugega s svojo izbiro. Če ga povlečete čez "
"<guilabel>Več ...</guilabel>, se prikaže nov meni izbir v <emphasis>PUD</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag your selection all the way onto the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane "
"on the right-hand side of the &amarok; screen."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite svojo izbiro do konca v podokno <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</"
"guilabel> na desni strani zaslona &amarok;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Double-click</keycap> the album/track to append to the playlist, "
"doesn't start to play."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>Dvokliknite</keycap> album/skladbo, da jo dodate na seznam "
"predvajanja, predvajanje se ne začne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Middle-click</keycap> the album/track to append it to the playlist "
"and play immediately."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>Srednji klik</keycap> album/skladbo, da jo dodate na seznam "
"predvajanja in takoj predvajate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Right-click</keycap> the album or track. In your right-click menu, "
"you will find similar choices. The image below shows the context menu that "
"appears after an item has been right-clicked. Select <guilabel>Add to "
"Playlist</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>Z desno miškino tipko kliknite</keycap> album ali skladbo. V meniju "
"z desnim klikom boste našli podobne možnosti. Spodnja slika prikazuje "
"kontekstni meni, ki se prikaže, ko z desno miškino tipko kliknete element. "
"Izberite <guilabel>Dodaj na seznam predvajanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Toolbar"
msgstr "Uporaba orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Toolbar</guilabel> at the top of the &amarok; screen provides "
"a simple interface to control the playing of music in the "
"<guilabel>Playlist</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Orodna vrstica</guilabel> na vrhu &amarok; ponuja preprost vmesnik "
"za nadzor predvajanja glasbe na <guilabel>Seznamu predvajanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the round icon on the left to start your music playing, and click it "
"again to pause. On the right is the volume and mute control; click on the "
"center of the icon to mute. Use your mouse scroll wheel to control the "
"volume, or drag/click your mouse on the outside ring of the volume icon."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite okroglo ikono na levi, da začnete predvajati glasbo, in jo kliknite "
"znova, da začasno ustavite. Na desni je nadzor glasnosti in izklopa zvoka; "
"kliknite na sredino ikone za izklop zvoka. Za nadzor glasnosti uporabite "
"drsno kolesce miške ali povlecite/kliknite miško na zunanji obroč ikone za "
"glasnost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a track or stream begins to play, the <emphasis>Artist / Album / Track "
"title</emphasis> slowly alternates in bold in the center. On the right is "
"the next track, which you can click to start it playing immediately. Once a "
"track has played it will be on the left, so you can click on the title to go "
"back to it. The progress bar in the middle of the <guilabel>Toolbar</"
"guilabel> indicates the time elapsed (left hand) and time remaining (right "
"hand) for the track that is currently playing."
msgstr ""
"Ko se skladba ali tok začne predvajati, se <emphasis>Izvajalec/album/naslov "
"skladbe</emphasis> počasi izmenjuje v krepkem tisku na sredini. Na desni je "
"naslednja skladba, ki jo lahko kliknete, da začnete takoj predvajati. Ko se "
"skladba predvaja, bo na levi strani, tako da lahko kliknete naslov, da se "
"vrnete nanjo. Vrstica napredka na sredini <guilabel>Orodne vrstice</"
"guilabel> prikazuje pretečeni čas (leva roka) in preostali čas (desna roka) "
"za skladbo, ki se trenutno predvaja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you'd rather see a more traditional toolbar, you can select "
"<guilabel>Slim Toolbar</guilabel> from the <guilabel>View</guilabel> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če bi raje videli bolj tradicionalno orodno vrstico, lahko izberete "
"<guilabel>Vitko orodno vrstico</guilabel> v meniju <guilabel>Pogled</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manipulating playlists"
msgstr "Manipulacija seznamov predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may want to delete albums or tracks from your playlist, rearrange the "
"displayed items for each track or rearrange the display order of tracks."
msgstr ""
"Morda boste želeli izbrisati albume ali skladbe s seznama predvajanja, "
"preurediti prikazane elemente za vsako skladbo ali preurediti vrstni red "
"prikaza skladb."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing a track"
msgstr "Odstranjevanje skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can remove any track or album from your playlist by:"
msgstr ""
"Katero koli skladbo ali album lahko odstranite s seznama predvajanja tako:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Right-click</keycap> on the item in the playlist and choose the "
"option <guilabel>Remove from playlist</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>Desni klik</keycap> na predmet na seznamu predvajanja in izberite "
"možnost <guilabel>Odstrani s seznama predvajanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag the item to be deleted over the <guilabel>Context</guilabel> pane to "
"activate <emphasis>PUD</emphasis>. Several options will appear over the "
"<guilabel>Context</guilabel> pane. Drag the item to the area marked "
"<guilabel>Delete from playlist</guilabel>. See the image below that shows a "
"track being dragged onto the <guilabel>Remove</guilabel> option in "
"<emphasis>PUD</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite element, ki ga želite izbrisati, čez podokno <guilabel>Kontekst</"
"guilabel>, da aktivirate <emphasis>PUD</emphasis>. V podoknu "
"<guilabel>Kontekst</guilabel> se prikaže več možnosti. Povlecite predmet v "
"območje, označeno z <guilabel>Izbriši s seznama predvajanja</guilabel>. "
"Glejte spodnjo sliko, ki prikazuje vlečenje skladbe na možnost "
"<guilabel>Odstrani</guilabel> v <emphasis>PUD</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting the track or tracks and use your <keycap>Delete</keycap> key. "
"Multiple tracks can be selected using &Shift; or &Ctrl;."
msgstr ""
"Izbira skladbe ali skladb in uporaba tipke <keycap>Delete</keycap>. Več "
"skladb je mogoče izbrati z &Shift; ali &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Pop-up Dropper when removing a track</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pojavna kapalka pri odstranjevanju skladbe</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:700
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Pop-up Dropper when removing a track</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pojavna kapalka pri odstranjevanju skladbe</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Undo your delete by pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> "
"or by clicking the arrow in the <guilabel>Playlist Toolbar</guilabel> at the "
"bottom of the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane (see below)."
msgstr ""
"Izbris razveljavite tako, da pritisnete <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> ali kliknete puščico v <guilabel>orodni vrstici seznama "
"predvajanja</guilabel> na dnu <guilabel>seznama predvajanja</guilabel > v "
"podoknu (glejte spodaj)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Playlist tools at the bottom"
msgstr "Uporaba orodij seznama predvajanja na dnu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane are seven icons:"
msgstr "Na dnu podokna <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel> je sedem ikon:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:717 index.docbook:2236
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Icon</para>"
msgstr "<para>Ikona</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:720 index.docbook:2239
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Action</para>"
msgstr "<para>Dejanje</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear playlist of all albums and tracks."
msgstr "Počisti seznam predvajanja vseh albumov in skladb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save your playlist. If you do not rename, saves the date as a name."
msgstr ""
"Shranite svoj seznam predvajanja. Če ga ne preimenujete, shrani datum kot "
"ime."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:777 index.docbook:2296
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo your last edit to playlist."
msgstr "Razveljavi zadnje urejanje seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:796 index.docbook:2315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Redo your last undo to playlist."
msgstr "Uveljavi zadnjo razveljavitev na seznamu predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlight the track currently playing. Useful for long playlists."
msgstr ""
"Označi skladbo, ki se trenutno predvaja. Uporabno za dolge sezname "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:834 index.docbook:2353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the play mode: repeat tracks, random order, prefer rarely played, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Nastavi način predvajanja: ponavljanje skladb, naključni vrstni red, raje "
"redko predvajano, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the playlist queue; which are tracks played first before the playlist "
"resumes."
msgstr ""
"Uredi čakalno vrsto seznama predvajanja; ki so najprej predvajane skladbe, "
"preden se seznam predvajanja nadaljuje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These buttons provide convenient alternatives to several keyboard actions."
msgstr "Ti gumbi ponujajo priročne alternative za več dejanj na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving and retrieving your favorite playlists"
msgstr "Shranjevanje in pridobivanje vaših priljubljenih seznamov predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The disk icon, in the popup which can be called from the bottom of your "
"<guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane, allows you to save the current &amarok; "
"playlist. This enables you to recall a particular selection of music from "
"your collection at any time. Playlists only contain pointers to the music "
"you selected, not the music itself. So if your playlist is pointing to music "
"on an external device, it must be connected and mounted, otherwise the music "
"cannot be played. There are three places to store playlists:"
msgstr ""
"Ikona diska v pojavnem oknu, ki ga lahko prikličete na dnu podokna "
"<guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel>, vam omogoča, da shranite trenutni "
"&amarok; seznam predvajanja. To vam omogoča, da kadar koli prikličete "
"določen izbor glasbe iz svoje zbirke. Seznami predvajanja vsebujejo samo "
"kazalce na glasbo, ki ste jo izbrali, ne pa same glasbe. Torej, če vaš "
"seznam predvajanja kaže na glasbo v zunanji napravi, mora biti povezana in "
"nameščena, sicer glasbe ni mogoče predvajati. Sezname predvajanja lahko "
"shranite na treh mestih:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid "outside &amarok; on your computer file system,"
msgstr "zunaj &amarok; v datotečnem sistemu vašega računalnika,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid "in your &amarok; playlist database"
msgstr "v vašem &amarok; bazi podatkov seznamov predvajanj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "on an portable media device."
msgstr "na prenosni medijski napravi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the disk icon at the bottom of the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> "
"pane stores your playlist in the &amarok; playlist database. To save to "
"disk, click and hold, then scroll to that choice."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete ikono diska na dnu podokna <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</"
"guilabel>, shranite seznam predvajanja v mapo &amarok; bazo podatkov seznama "
"predvajanja. Če želite shraniti na disk, kliknite in pridržite, nato se "
"pomaknite do te izbire."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:881
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Current playlist saving options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Trenutne možnosti shranjevanja seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Current playlist saving options</para>"
msgstr "<para>Trenutne možnosti shranjevanja seznama predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, your saved playlist has a name composed of the date and time "
"when you saved it (see image below). Right-click the playlist name to rename "
"it. Right-clicking on a playlist name also allows you to add it to your "
"existing playlist in the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane, or to replace "
"your existing playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ime shranjenega seznama predvajanja je privzeto sestavljeno iz datuma in "
"ure, ko ste ga shranili (glejte sliko spodaj). Z desno miškino tipko "
"kliknite ime seznama predvajanja, da ga preimenujete. Desni klik na ime "
"seznama predvajanja vam omogoča tudi, da ga dodate na svoj obstoječi seznam "
"predvajanja v podoknu <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel> ali zamenjate "
"obstoječi seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Context View"
msgstr "Kontekstni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The power of &amarok; is in the <emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane (in the "
"center of the default &amarok; window), where you can install various "
"<emphasis>applets</emphasis> to help you enjoy and explore your music. Most "
"of this additional information is obtained from the Internet, so a "
"connection is important to get the most out of your <emphasis>Context</"
"emphasis> pane. By default, three <emphasis>applets</emphasis> are preset: "
"<emphasis>Current Track</emphasis>, <emphasis>Lyrics</emphasis> and "
"<emphasis>Wikipedia</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Moč &amarok;a je v podoknu <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> (na sredini "
"privzetega okna &amarok;), kjer lahko namestite različne "
"<emphasis>programčke</emphasis>, ki vam bodo pomagali uživati in raziskovati "
"svojo glasbo. Večina teh dodatnih informacij je pridobljenih iz interneta, "
"zato je povezava pomembna, če želite kar najbolje izkoristiti podokno "
"<emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis>. Privzeto so prednastavljeni trije "
"<emphasis>programčki</emphasis>: <emphasis>Trenutna skladba</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Besedilo</emphasis> in <emphasis>Wikipedia</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default layout"
msgstr "Privzeta postavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default <emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane shows the following items: "
"CurrentTrack, Analyzer, Wikipedia and Lyrics. Depending on the screen size "
"the Lyrics might not be visible, but clicking on the button at the bottom "
"will make it visible. When nothing is playing, the CurrentTrack applet will "
"show the last played tracks and information about the Local Collection"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto podokno <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> prikazuje naslednje elemente: "
"Trenutna skladba, Analizator, Wikipedia in Lirika. Odvisno od velikosti "
"zaslona besedilo morda ne bo vidno, vendar bo vidno s klikom na gumb na dnu. "
"Ko se nič ne predvaja, bo programček Trenutna Skladba prikazal zadnje "
"predvajane skladbe in informacije o lokalni zbirki"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The default view as of Amarok 2.8</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Privzeti pogled od Amaroka 2.8</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The default view as of Amarok 2.8</para>"
msgstr "<para>Privzeti pogled od Amaroka 2.8</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing the Context pane"
msgstr "Prilagajanje kontekstnega podokna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the <emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane are four buttons for "
"the default applets. On the right of these buttons you see "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, clicking on it will "
"show <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-application-"
"exit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> allowing you "
"to remove these applets. Click the applets to add them to the pane. Drag the "
"labeled buttons to re-order the applets you have, and click "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> again to save your "
"selections."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu podokna <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> so štirje gumbi za privzete "
"programčke. Na desni strani teh gumbov vidite <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, s klikom nanj se prikaže "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-application-exit."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, ki vam omogoča, "
"da odstranite te programčke. Kliknite programčke, da jih dodate v podokno. "
"Povlecite označene gumbe, da prerazporedite programčke, ki jih imate, in "
"znova kliknite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, da "
"shranite vaše izbire."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This makes the <emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane extremely flexible, "
"maximizing the possibility of a custom display that fits your preferences. "
"More <link linkend=\"the-context-pane\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zaradi tega je podokno <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> izjemno prilagodljivo, "
"kar poveča možnost prikaza po meri, ki ustreza vašim željam. Več <link "
"linkend=\"the-context-pane\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to deal with problems"
msgstr "Kako se spopasti s težavami"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some of the music is being rapidly skipped over"
msgstr "Nekatera glasba se hitro preskoči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may not have installed the necessary <emphasis>codecs.</emphasis> More "
"about that here:"
msgstr ""
"Morda niste namestili potrebnih <emphasis>kodekov.</emphasis> Več o tem "
"tukaj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"what-media-types-does-amarok-support\">FAQ: What Media Types "
"Does Amarok Support</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"what-media-types-does-amarok-support\">Pogosta vprašanja: "
"Katere vrste medijev podpira Amarok</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid "Please refer to your distribution."
msgstr "Oglejte si svojo distribucijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid "After my iPod has been mounted, it is not shown in the Content Browser"
msgstr "Ko je moj iPod nameščen, ni prikazan v brskalniku vsebine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This should not happen. Check that the device has been properly mounted. "
"Simply typing <userinput>mount</userinput> in a console will show you all "
"mounted devices."
msgstr ""
"To se ne bi smelo zgoditi. Preverite, ali je naprava pravilno nameščena. Če "
"preprosto vtipkate <userinput>mount</userinput> v konzolo, se vam bodo "
"prikazale vse nameščene naprave."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After I have updated my collection, the additions are not shown in the "
"Content Browser"
msgstr "Ko posodobim svojo zbirko, dodatki niso prikazani v brskalniku vsebine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the top-level menu <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Update Collection</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If they "
"don't show up, quit &amarok; from the &amarok; menu, or use <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> to quit. Once you restart &amarok;, your "
"collection should show your updates."
msgstr ""
"V meniju na najvišji ravni <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi zbirko</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če se ne "
"prikažejo, zaprite &amarok; iz &amarok; ali uporabite <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> za izhod. Ko znova zaženete &amarok;, bi "
"morala vaša zbirka prikazati vaše posodobitve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amarok cannot find the lyrics of the songs that I play"
msgstr "Amarok ne najde besedila pesmi, ki jih predvajam"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid "Possibilities:"
msgstr "Možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lyrics are not available in the sites checked on the Internet. You may "
"wish to add more sites via the script menu."
msgstr ""
"Besedila niso na voljo na straneh, preverjenih na internetu. Morda boste "
"želeli dodati več spletnih mest prek menija skripta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The track numbering system within an album in your collection is not correct."
msgstr "Sistem številčenja skladb v albumu v vaši zbirki ni pravilen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The title of your song contains special characters with a cedille, accent, "
"&etc; that do not show in your track title; therefore the lyrics script "
"applet cannot find a match for your title. Check your tags and track "
"numbering system with a tagger such as <ulink url=\"http://musicbrainz.org/"
"doc/MusicBrainz_Picard\">Picard</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Naslov vaše pesmi vsebuje posebne znake s cedillom, naglasom itd. ki niso "
"prikazani v naslovu vaše skladbe; zato skriptni programček besedila ne more "
"najti ujemanja z vašim naslovom. Preverite svoje oznake in sistem "
"številčenja skladb z označevalcem, kot je <ulink url=\"http://musicbrainz."
"org/doc/MusicBrainz_Picard\">Picard</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:975
#, no-c-format
msgid "My question isn't answered here"
msgstr "Tukaj ni odgovora na moje vprašanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More complex issues are covered in this handbook, including <link linkend="
"\"troubleshooting-and-common-problems\">Troubleshooting and Common Problems</"
"link>, and the <link linkend=\"frequently-asked-questions\">Amarok FAQ</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"V tem priročniku so obravnavana bolj zapletena vprašanja, vključno z <link "
"linkend=\"troubleshooting-and-common-problems\">odpravljanjem težav in "
"pogostimi težavami</link> ter <link linkend=\"frequently-asked-questions"
"\">pogostimi vprašanji o Amaroku</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "Glosar"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:981
#, no-c-format
msgid "Breadcrumbs"
msgstr "Drobtinice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a way of navigating a hierarchical file structure; on &amarok; near "
"the top of the Media Sources pane. Starting at the Home folder level, it "
"shows how deep one has navigated into the file system. When you have gone to "
"a particular place in the file system, you will see all folders at a higher "
"level. In &amarok; the <guilabel>&gt;</guilabel> links between folder levels "
"allow you to find out what alternative folders are available at a particular "
"level. The breadcrumbs are an efficient mechanism to navigate the whole file "
"system on your computer."
msgstr ""
"To je način krmarjenja po hierarhični strukturi datotek; na &amarok; blizu "
"vrha podokna Medijski viri. Začenši na ravni domače mape, prikazuje, kako "
"globoko ste se pomaknili v datotečni sistem. Ko greste na določeno mesto v "
"datotečnem sistemu, boste videli vse mape na višji ravni. V &amarok; "
"Povezave <guilabel>&gt;</guilabel> med ravnmi map vam omogočajo, da "
"ugotovite, katere alternativne mape so na voljo na določeni ravni. "
"Drobtinice so učinkovit mehanizem za krmarjenje po celotnem datotečnem "
"sistemu v vašem računalniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:985 index.docbook:3627
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Collection</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zbirka</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All the sound files that &amarok; has compiled in the database. Your "
"collection may vary in size and composition of music tracks, depending which "
"external devices (such as audio CDs or portable players with music) are "
"connected and mounted on your computer."
msgstr ""
"Vse zvočne datoteke, ki jih &amarok; je zbral v bazi podatkov. Vaša zbirka "
"se lahko razlikuje po velikosti in sestavi glasbenih posnetkov, odvisno od "
"tega, katere zunanje naprave (kot so zvočni CD-ji ali prenosni predvajalniki "
"z glasbo) so povezane in nameščene na vašem računalniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:989
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection Browser"
msgstr "Brskalnik po zbirkah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is in the <emphasis>Media Sources</emphasis> pane for your <quote>Local "
"Music</quote> section and shows you the list of the music that you have in "
"your collections. The Collection Browser allows you to search and sort your "
"track lists by various id3 tags."
msgstr ""
"To je v podoknu <emphasis>Medijski viri</emphasis> za razdelek "
"<quote>Lokalna glasba</quote> in prikazuje seznam glasbe, ki jo imate v "
"svojih zbirkah. Brskalnik po zbirkah vam omogoča iskanje in razvrščanje "
"vaših seznamov skladb po različnih oznakah id3."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:993 index.docbook:1516 index.docbook:5159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Playlist</title>"
msgstr "<title>Seznam predvajanja</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:994
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A selection of tracks from your collection that you wish to play. Some "
"portable music players have predefined playlists that are likely to differ "
"from your &amarok; playlists."
msgstr ""
"Izbor skladb iz vaše zbirke, ki jih želite predvajati. Nekateri prenosni "
"predvajalniki glasbe imajo vnaprej določene sezname predvajanja, ki se bodo "
"verjetno razlikovali od vašega seznama predvajanja &amarok;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script"
msgstr "Skripta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; plugin to extend functionality. Scripts are available from "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Scripts</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Add more lyrics "
"sources, more streaming stations, save covers to your album folders, burn "
"CDs from playlists, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"&amarok; vtičnik za razširitev funkcionalnosti. Skripti so na voljo v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Skripte</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Dodajte več "
"virov besedil, več postaj za pretakanje, shranite naslovnice v svoje mape "
"albumov, zapišite CD-je s seznamov predvajanja, &etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrobble"
msgstr "Scrobble"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To scrobble a track means that as you listen to it, the title of the track "
"and artist are sent to a Web site such as <emphasis>Last.fm</emphasis>, "
"where the information is added to your profile."
msgstr ""
"Scrobble po skladbi pomeni, da sta med poslušanjem naslov skladbe in "
"izvajalec poslana na spletno mesto, kot je <emphasis>Last.fm</emphasis>, "
"kjer se informacije dodajo vašemu profilu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stream, streaming"
msgstr "Pretakanje, pretakanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like 20th-century radio stations, Internet radio stations send out "
"<quote>streams</quote> of content. One can find music, news, commentary and "
"opinion. Many streams can be accessed through &amarok;, either through "
"scripts such as <emphasis>Cool Streams</emphasis>, or individually added by "
"menu, <menuchoice><guimenu>Playlist</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Stream</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot radijske postaje 20. stoletja tudi internetne radijske postaje "
"pošiljajo <quote>tokove</quote> vsebine. Najdete lahko glasbo, novice, "
"komentarje in mnenja. Do številnih tokov je mogoče dostopati prek &amarok;, "
"bodisi prek skriptov, kot je <emphasis>Cool Streams</emphasis>, bodisi "
"posamično dodanih z menijem, <menuchoice><guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj tok</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1009 index.docbook:3757 index.docbook:4702
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The information about each of the tracks you listen to, &eg; album name, "
"track title, composer, artist, year, &etc; There is a standard called ID3 "
"for including this information on audio CDs. You can edit the tags of "
"individual tracks within &amarok; if the file permissions are correct."
msgstr ""
"Informacije o vsaki skladbi, ki jo poslušate, npr. ime albuma, naslov "
"skladbe, skladatelj, izvajalec, leto, &etc; Obstaja standard, imenovan ID3, "
"za vključitev teh informacij na zvočne CD-je. Oznake posameznih skladb lahko "
"urejate znotraj &amarok;a če so dovoljenja za datoteko pravilna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Amarok Window"
msgstr "Okno Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you open &amarok;, this is what you will see, once &amarok; has fully "
"loaded:"
msgstr "Ko odprete &amarok;, boste videli to, ko &amarok; ima polno naloženo:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Default startup window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Privzeto zagonsko okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1029
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Default startup window</para>"
msgstr "<para>Privzeto zagonsko okno</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Layout"
msgstr "Postavitev oken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid "&amarok; is organized in four main areas, the toolbar and three panes:"
msgstr ""
"&amarok; je organiziran v štirih glavnih področjih, orodni vrstici in treh "
"podoknih:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"main-toolbar\">The Main Toolbar</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"main-toolbar\">Glavna orodna vrstica</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"slim-toolbar\">The Slim Toolbar</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"slim-toolbar\">Vitka orodna vrstica </link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"the-media-sources-pane\">The Media Sources pane</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"the-media-sources-pane\">Podokno Medijski viri</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"the-context-pane\">The Context pane</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"the-context-pane\">Kontekstno podokno</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Toolbar</emphasis> is used to manage the currently playing "
"song. You can switch between the main and slim Toolbar using the "
"<guilabel>View</guilabel> menu in the <emphasis>Menubar</emphasis>. The "
"Menubar can optionally be hidden; use <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></"
"keycombo> to hide or re-display."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Orodna vrstica</emphasis> se uporablja za upravljanje trenutno "
"predvajane pesmi. Med glavno in vitko orodno vrstico lahko preklapljate z "
"menijem <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> v <emphasis>Menijski vrstici</emphasis>. "
"Menijsko vrstico lahko po želji skrijete; uporabite <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>, da skrijete ali znova prikažete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Toolbar can be undocked and moved anywhere on your screen, and even used "
"without the rest of the &amarok; window displayed. To undock the Toolbar you "
"should first make sure that the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Lock Layout</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item is "
"unselected. Now you can grab the toolbar at its left edge and drag it "
"anywhere. To get it back just drag it into its old position while the layout "
"is still unlocked."
msgstr ""
"Orodno vrstico je mogoče odklopiti in premakniti kamor koli na zaslonu ter "
"jo celo uporabljati brez preostalega &amarok; prikazanega okna. Če želite "
"odklopiti orodno vrstico, se morate najprej prepričati, da menijska postavka "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zakleni postavitev</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ni izbrana. Zdaj lahko zgrabite orodno vrstico na "
"njenem levem robu in jo povlečete kamor koli. Če jo želite vrniti, jo "
"preprosto povlecite na stari položaj, medtem ko je postavitev še vedno "
"odklenjena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Main Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Glavna orodna vrstica</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default Toolbar. It has a <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> / <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-pause.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button on the left and displays the song "
"title, album and artist in the center-top."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeta orodna vrstica. Ima gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> / <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref= \"Icon-media-playback-pause.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> na levi strani in na sredini na vrhu "
"prikazuje naslov pesmi, album in izvajalca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The previous and next track are shown on either side of the song title. "
"Clicking one of them will make &amarok; skip to that track."
msgstr ""
"Prejšnja in naslednja skladba sta prikazani na obeh straneh naslova pesmi. "
"Če kliknete enega od njih, bo &amarok; preskočil na to skladbo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis>Progressbar</emphasis> with the already played time on the left "
"and remaining time on the right shows the current position in the song. If "
"you have <emphasis>Moodbars</emphasis> enabled, and .mood files for your "
"tracks, this is where they will be displayed. More about <link linkend=\"the-"
"moodbar\">the Moodbar</link> later."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Vrstica napredka</emphasis> z že predvajanim časom na levi in "
"preostalim časom na desni prikazuje trenutni položaj v pesmi. Če imate "
"omogočene <emphasis>Razpoloženjske vrstice</emphasis> in datoteke .mood za "
"svoje skladbe, bodo tukaj prikazane. Več o <link linkend=\"the-moodbar"
"\">barvi razpoloženja</link> pozneje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By using the slightly transparent <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-emblem-favorite.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> and <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-flag-green.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> buttons next to the text you can add the current song to "
"your loved tracks on <ulink url=\"http://www.last.fm/\">last.fm</ulink> or "
"add a position marker."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo rahlo prosojnih <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-emblem-favorite.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> in <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref= "
"\"Icon-flag-green.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"gumbov poleg besedila lahko dodate trenutno pesem svojim priljubljenim "
"skladbam na <ulink url=\"http://www.last.fm/\">last.fm</ulink> ali dodajte "
"oznako položaja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right is the volume-control button. A blue circle around the button "
"shows the current volume. The volume is 0 at the bottom and increases "
"clockwise. Change volume by clicking on the volume circle or by using the "
"scroll wheel while the mouse hovers the button. The sound can also be "
"completely muted by clicking on the speaker in the center."
msgstr ""
"Na desni je gumb za nadzor glasnosti. Modri krog okoli gumba prikazuje "
"trenutno glasnost. Glasnost je na dnu 0 in se povečuje v smeri urinega "
"kazalca. Glasnost spremenite s klikom na krog za glasnost ali z uporabo "
"kolesca za pomikanje, medtem ko miška lebdi nad gumbom. Zvok lahko tudi "
"popolnoma utišamo s klikom na zvočnik v sredini."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Slim Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vitka orodna vrstica</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Slim Toolbar</emphasis> has the same functionality as the "
"<emphasis>Main Toolbar</emphasis>, but is more compact. Additionally the "
"<emphasis>Slim Toolbar</emphasis> has a <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-stop.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button to stop playing so the current song "
"will be restarted when you press <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> again. All buttons concerning the current "
"track are on the left and only the volume control on the right side. Here "
"the volume is controlled by clicking on the button and dragging the slider "
"or using the scroll wheel while the mouse is hovering the button."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Vitka orodna vrstica</emphasis> ima enako funkcionalnost kot "
"<emphasis>Glavna orodna vrstica</emphasis>, vendar je bolj kompaktna. Poleg "
"tega ima <emphasis>Vitka orodna vrstica</emphasis> gumb <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-stop.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> za ustavitev predvajanja, tako "
"da se bo trenutna pesem znova zagnala, ko ponovno pritisnete "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-"
"start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>. Vsi gumbi, "
"ki zadevajo trenutno skladbo, so na levi strani, na desni strani pa le gumb "
"za nastavitev glasnosti. Tukaj je glasnost nadzorovana s klikom na gumb in "
"vlečenjem drsnika ali uporabo kolesca za pomikanje, medtem ko miška lebdi "
"nad gumbom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Media Sources</emphasis> pane on the left by default is where "
"you access your local collection as well as other services: <emphasis>Local "
"Music</emphasis> on top, which is the primary interface to your local "
"collection and connected media such as mp3 players and CDs."
msgstr ""
"V podoknu <emphasis>Medijski viri</emphasis> na levi privzeto dostopate do "
"svoje lokalne zbirke in drugih storitev: <emphasis>Lokalna glasba</emphasis> "
"na vrhu, ki je primarni vmesnik do vaše lokalne zbirke in povezani mediji, "
"kot so predvajalniki mp3 in CD-ji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a section for all <emphasis>Internet Services</emphasis> that you "
"have enabled. Here, you can browse listings of radio stations and podcasts; "
"listen and/or subscribe to them, interact with your <ulink url=\"http://www."
"last.fm\">last.fm</ulink> account, purchase music from online stores such as "
"our new Amazon mp3 store, <ulink url=\"http://www.magnatune.com/"
"\">Magnatune</ulink> and download independent artists' music from <ulink url="
"\"http://www.jamendo.com/\">Jamendo</ulink> and more."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja razdelek za vse <emphasis>Internetne storitve</emphasis>, ki ste jih "
"omogočili. Tukaj lahko brskate po seznamih radijskih postaj in podcastov; "
"jih poslušajte in/ali se naročite nanje, komunicirajte s svojim računom "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.last.fm\">last.fm</ulink>, kupujte glasbo v spletnih "
"trgovinah, kot je naša nova Amazon mp3 trgovina, <ulink url=\"http://www."
"magnatune.com/\">Magnatune</ulink> in prenesite glasbo neodvisnih izvajalcev "
"iz <ulink url=\"http://www.jamendo.com/\">Jamendo</ulink> in več."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Playlists</emphasis> section allows you to create and manage "
"<emphasis>Dynamic Playlists</emphasis>, access your <emphasis>Saved "
"Playlists</emphasis> as well as the <emphasis>Automatic Playlist Generator</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <emphasis>Seznami predvajanja</emphasis> vam omogoča ustvarjanje in "
"upravljanje <emphasis>dinamičnih seznamov predvajanja</emphasis>, dostop do "
"<emphasis>shranjenih seznamov predvajanja</emphasis> ter "
"<emphasis>samodejnega generatorja seznamov predvajanja</emphasis> >."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Files</emphasis> section displays an integrated file browser "
"and the <emphasis>Podcasts</emphasis> section offers you access to your "
"podcast subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <emphasis>Datoteke</emphasis> je prikazan vgrajen brskalnik "
"datotek, razdelek <emphasis>Podcasti</emphasis> pa vam ponuja dostop do "
"vaših naročnin na podcaste."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation Menu"
msgstr "Navigacijski meni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Navigation menu</emphasis> consists of the <emphasis>Filter "
"bar</emphasis>, <emphasis>Bookmark button</emphasis> and "
"<emphasis>Breadcrumbs navigation bar</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Navigacijski meni</emphasis> je sestavljen iz <emphasis>Vrstice "
"filtrov</emphasis>, <emphasis>Gumba za zaznamke</emphasis> in "
"<emphasis>Navigacijske vrstice Drobtinice</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Filter Bar"
msgstr "Vrstica filtrov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Filter Bar</emphasis> filters the content according to the "
"text in the box."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Vrstica filtrov</emphasis> filtrira vsebino glede na besedilo v "
"polju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To access this feature, click on the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-bookmark-new-list.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> icon above the <emphasis>Filter bar</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do te funkcije kliknite ikono <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-bookmark-new-list.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> nad <emphasis> Filtrirna vrstica</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1262 index.docbook:1370 index.docbook:1451 index.docbook:1537
#: index.docbook:1625 index.docbook:3543 index.docbook:4533 index.docbook:5019
#: index.docbook:5105 index.docbook:6973 index.docbook:7259 index.docbook:7518
#: index.docbook:7595 index.docbook:7720 index.docbook:7821
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Item"
msgstr "Element menija"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1263 index.docbook:1371 index.docbook:1452 index.docbook:1538
#: index.docbook:1626 index.docbook:3095 index.docbook:3160 index.docbook:3268
#: index.docbook:3544 index.docbook:3942 index.docbook:4534 index.docbook:4713
#: index.docbook:5020 index.docbook:5106 index.docbook:5264 index.docbook:5451
#: index.docbook:5699 index.docbook:6891 index.docbook:6974 index.docbook:7260
#: index.docbook:7519 index.docbook:7596 index.docbook:7721 index.docbook:7822
#: index.docbook:8345
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Description</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Opis</entry>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark Media Sources View"
msgstr "Zaznamek Pogled virov medijev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds the current <emphasis>Media Sources</emphasis> view configuration to "
"the bookmark list."
msgstr ""
"Doda trenutno konfiguracijo pogleda <emphasis>Medijski viri</emphasis> na "
"seznam zaznamkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy Current View Bookmark to Clipboard"
msgstr "Kopiraj zaznamek trenutnega pogleda v odložišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copies bookmark to the system clipboard."
msgstr "Kopira zaznamek v sistemsko odložišče."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1285 index.docbook:7525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Bookmark Manager</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Upravljalnik zaznamkov</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a list of all available bookmarks in a new window, with options to "
"edit them."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže seznam vseh razpoložljivih zaznamkov v novem oknu z možnostmi za "
"njihovo urejanje."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark List"
msgstr "Seznam zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists all your bookmarks for faster selection."
msgstr "Navede vse vaše zaznamke za hitrejšo izbiro."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Local Music</title>"
msgstr "<title>Lokalna glasba</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the music from your default collection folder, sorted as specified. "
"Both the regular (non-merged) view and <emphasis>Merged</emphasis> view of "
"the same collection are shown, with the same sorting. Click the icon "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-view-list-tree."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> to toggle between "
"views."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže glasbo iz privzete mape zbirke, razvrščeno, kot je določeno. "
"Prikazana sta običajni (nespojeni) pogled in <emphasis>Spojen</emphasis> "
"pogled iste zbirke z enakim razvrščanjem. Kliknite ikono <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-view-list-tree.png\" format=\"PNG\"/"
"> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> za preklapljanje med pogledi."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Regular non-merged view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Navadni nespojeni pogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Regular non-merged view</para>"
msgstr "<para>Navadni nespojeni pogled</para>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Merged view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Združeni pogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Merged view</para>"
msgstr "<para>Združeni pogled</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the icon <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"preferences-other.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"to change the sorting criteria, using the following menu:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"preferences-other.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>, da spremenite kriterije razvrščanja z uporabo "
"naslednjega menija:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Artist/Album"
msgstr "Izvajalec/album"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the collection sorted by artists and album names. If two entries have "
"the same artist they will be sorted by album."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže zbirko, razvrščeno po izvajalcih in imenih albumov. Če imata dva "
"vnosa istega izvajalca, bosta razvrščena po albumu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Album/Artist"
msgstr "Album/Izvajalec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the collection sorted by album and artist names."
msgstr "Prikaže zbirko, razvrščeno po albumih in imenih izvajalcev."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Genre/Artist"
msgstr "Žanr/Izvajalec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the collection sorted by genre and artist. If two entries have the "
"same genre they will be sorted by artist."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže zbirko, razvrščeno po zvrsti in izvajalcu. Če imata dva vnosa isti "
"žanr, bosta razvrščena po izvajalcu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Genre/Artist/Album"
msgstr "Žanr/Izvajalec/Album"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the collection sorted by genre, artist and album. If two entries have "
"the same artist they will be sorted by album."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže zbirko, razvrščeno po žanru, izvajalcu in albumu. Če imata dva vnosa "
"istega izvajalca, bosta razvrščena po albumu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Levels"
msgstr "Ravni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Designate the window cascade order of your elements."
msgstr "Določite kaskadni vrstni red oken vaših elementov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Years"
msgstr "Prikaži leta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1420
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check if you want years to be displayed."
msgstr "Označite, če želite, da so prikazana leta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Track Numbers"
msgstr "Pokaži številke skladb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check if you want track numbers to be displayed."
msgstr "Označite, ali želite, da se prikažejo številke skladb."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Cover Art"
msgstr "Prikaz naslovnice Art"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check if you want cover art to be displayed."
msgstr "Označite, ali želite, da se prikaže naslovnica."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Internet</title>"
msgstr "<title>Internet</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows your internet collection, added and configured in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Plugins</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. More <link "
"linkend=\"internet-services\">about configuring Internet Services</link>. "
"There are some scripts which add Internet Services; see <link linkend="
"\"scripts\">Scripts</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje vašo internetno zbirko, dodano in konfigurirano v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok ..."
"</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vtičniki</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Več <link "
"linkend=\"internet-services\">o konfiguraciji internetnih storitev</link>. "
"Obstaja nekaj skriptov, ki dodajajo internetne storitve; za več informacij "
"si oglejte <link linkend=\"scripts\">Skripte</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cool Streams"
msgstr "Kul tokovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists quality radio streams."
msgstr "Navaja kakovostne radijske tokove."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1466 index.docbook:3189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jamendo"
msgstr "Jamendo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connects with <guilabel>Jamendo</guilabel>, a growing free music database."
msgstr ""
"Povezuje se z <guilabel>Jamendo</guilabel>, rastočo brezplačno glasbeno "
"zbirko podatkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1474 index.docbook:3200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last.fm"
msgstr "Last.fm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connects with <guilabel>Last.fm</guilabel>; embedding the site experience in "
"&amarok;."
msgstr ""
"Povezuje se z <guilabel>Last.fm</guilabel>; vdelava izkušnje spletnega mesta "
"v &amarok;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Librivox.org"
msgstr "Librivox.org"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connects with <guilabel>Librivox</guilabel>, an extensive collection of free "
"audio books."
msgstr ""
"Povezuje se z <guilabel>Librivox</guilabel>, obsežno zbirko brezplačnih "
"zvočnih knjig."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Magnatune.com"
msgstr "Magnatune.com"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connects with <guilabel>Magnatune</guilabel>, a great online music store."
msgstr ""
"Povezuje se z <guilabel>Magnatune</guilabel>, odlično spletno glasbeno "
"trgovino."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1498 index.docbook:3222
#, no-c-format
msgid "MP3 Music Store"
msgstr "Trgovina z glasbo MP3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connects with <guilabel>Amazon MP3 Store</guilabel>, an online music store."
msgstr ""
"Povezuje se s <guilabel>Amazon MP3 Store</guilabel>, spletno glasbeno "
"trgovino."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1506 index.docbook:3244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Podcast Directory"
msgstr "Imenik podcastov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a large list of podcasts. If you choose to subscribe, the podcast menu "
"will be automatically updated."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže velik seznam podcastov. Če se odločite, da se naročite, bo meni "
"podcasta samodejno posodobljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1517
#, no-c-format
msgid "Media Sources Playlists menu:"
msgstr "Predstavnostni viri Meni seznamov predvajanja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Dynamic Playlists</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Dinamični seznami predvajanja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dynamically updating parameter-based playlist; more on this <link linkend="
"\"dynamic-playlists\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dinamično posodabljanje seznama predvajanja na podlagi parametrov; več o tem "
"<link linkend=\"dynamic-playlists\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1552
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Saved Playlists</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Shranjeni seznami predvajanja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saved and imported playlists; more on this <link linkend=\"saved-playlists"
"\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Shranjeni in uvoženi seznami predvajanja; več o tem <link linkend=\"saved-"
"playlists\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automated Playlist Generator"
msgstr "Avtomatski generator seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates playlists by specific criteria; more on this <link linkend="
"\"automatic-playlist-generator\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari sezname predvajanja po določenih kriterijih; več o tem <link linkend="
"\"automatic-playlist-generator\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Files</title>"
msgstr "<title>Datoteke</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &amarok; <emphasis>file browser</emphasis> helps you add music to your "
"collection, or simply play tracks from your hard drive."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; <emphasis>Brskalnik datotek</emphasis> vam pomaga dodati glasbo v "
"svojo zbirko ali preprosto predvajati skladbe s trdega diska."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate through your files using the icon buttons: <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-previous.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> (previous), <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> (next), <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-up.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> (up), <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-go-home.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> (home), or <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-folder-remote.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> (places), very similar to a web browser menu; or click on "
"anywhere in the <emphasis>breadcrumbs</emphasis> to go directly to that "
"level."
msgstr ""
"Po svojih datotekah se pomikajte z gumbi z ikonami: <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-previous.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> (prejšnja), <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> (naslednji), <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-up.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> (gor), <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-home.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> (domača stran) ali <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-folder-remote.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> (mesta), zelo podoben meniju spletnega "
"brskalnika; ali kliknite kjer koli v <emphasis>drobtinicah</emphasis>, da "
"greste neposredno na to raven."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would rather search or filter for something rather than navigating to "
"it, use the <emphasis>filter field</emphasis> to find the desired content. "
"Partially type the name of the file and it will be displayed as in this "
"example."
msgstr ""
"Če bi raje iskali ali filtrirali nekaj, namesto da bi se pomaknili do tega, "
"uporabite <emphasis>polje filtra</emphasis>, da poiščete želeno vsebino. "
"Delno vnesite ime datoteke in prikazana bo kot v tem primeru."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1604
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Podcasts</title>"
msgstr "<title>Podcasti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lists your subscribed podcasts; from here you can listen, organize, add, "
"import or unsubscribe podcasts."
msgstr ""
"Seznam vaših naročenih podcastov; od tu lahko poslušate, organizirate, "
"dodajate, uvozite ali odjavite podcaste."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1632
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Podcast"
msgstr "Dodaj podcast"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a podcast URL: <emphasis>RSS 1.0/2.0</emphasis> or <emphasis>Atom feed</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte URL podcasta: <emphasis>RSS 1.0/2.0</emphasis> ali <emphasis>Atom "
"vir</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1643
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a folder to the podcast navigation menu."
msgstr "Dodajte mapo v navigacijski meni podcasta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Visible Sources"
msgstr "Vidni viri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1651
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects what category of podcasts you can view."
msgstr "Izbere kategorijo podcastov, ki si jih lahko ogledate."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1656
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merged View"
msgstr "Združeni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the podcasts in a merged or unmerged view."
msgstr "Prikaže podcaste v združenem ali nespojenem pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checks all podcasts for updates and downloads any available."
msgstr "Preveri vse podcaste za posodobitve in prenese vse razpoložljive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1675
#, no-c-format
msgid "Imports an OPML file from your hard drive."
msgstr "Uvozi datoteko OPML z vašega trdega diska."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1683
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Context pane"
msgstr "Kontekstno podokno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane is a panel to which you can add "
"various applets which offer information and media on the current music. A "
"connection to the Internet is required for the most useful use of these "
"little applications, which will fetch lyrics, information, photos, and even "
"guitar or bass tabs, depending on which applets you choose to display."
msgstr ""
"Podokno <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> je plošča, v katero lahko dodate "
"različne programčke, ki ponujajo informacije in medije o trenutni glasbi. "
"Povezava z internetom je potrebna za najbolj uporabno uporabo teh majhnih "
"aplikacij, ki bodo pridobile besedila, informacije, fotografije in celo "
"kitarske ali basovske tabulatorje, odvisno od tega, katere programčke "
"izberete za prikaz."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1686
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Context pane"
msgstr "Uporaba kontekstnega podokna"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1695
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Context pane when not playing</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kontekstno podokno, ko se ne predvaja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1698
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Context pane when not playing</para>"
msgstr "<para>Kontekstno podokno, ko se ne predvaja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pictured is the <emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane when no track is playing. "
"If it is hidden, use <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Context</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to display it. The "
"pane is divided in two parts:"
msgstr ""
"Na sliki je podokno <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis>, ko se ne predvaja nobena "
"skladba. Če je skrit, uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kontekst</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da ga prikažete. "
"Podokno je razdeljeno na dva dela:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The applet panel itself, where you can interact with some of the applets, "
"such as editing lyrics or changing settings."
msgstr ""
"Sama plošča programčkov, kjer lahko komunicirate z nekaterimi programčki, "
"kot je urejanje besedil ali spreminjanje nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lower portion of the panel, where you can expand and collapse applets "
"and manipulate them in various ways once you click the <emphasis>Configure "
"Applets</emphasis> icon <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."
msgstr ""
"Spodnji del plošče, kjer lahko razširite in strnete programčke in z njimi "
"manipulirate na različne načine, ko kliknete ikono <emphasis>Konfiguriraj "
"programčke</emphasis> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Applets"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje programčkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you click <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> in the "
"lower portion of the <emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane changes slightly; "
"each applet tab gets an <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-application-exit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> icon that you can click to remove it, and a list of "
"applets appear. To add new applet, simply click on the applet, and it will "
"appear in the pane, ready to be used. To change the applet display order, "
"click the tabs and drag them around the bar."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v "
"spodnjem delu podokna <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> rahlo spremeni; vsak "
"zavihek programčka dobi ikono <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-application-exit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>, ki jo lahko kliknete, da jo odstranite, in prikaže se "
"seznam programčkov. Če želite dodati nov programček, preprosto kliknite "
"programček in prikazal se bo v podoknu, pripravljen za uporabo. Če želite "
"spremeniti vrstni red prikaza programčkov, kliknite zavihke in jih povlecite "
"po vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applets"
msgstr "Programčki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several applets available to dock in your <emphasis>Context</"
"emphasis> pane; below is a description of each."
msgstr ""
"V vašem podoknu <emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> je na voljo več programčkov; "
"spodaj je opis vsakega."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applet"
msgstr "Programček"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1739
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Icon</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Ikona</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1742
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Description</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Opis</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current Track"
msgstr "Trenutna skladba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information about the current track. You may rate it by clicking on the "
"stars, add a position marker, or edit track metadata. When not playing, the "
"applet displays collection information and <emphasis>Recently Played Tracks</"
"emphasis>, which allows you to view the tracks and add them to the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Informacije o trenutni skladbi. Ocenite jo lahko s klikom na zvezdice, "
"dodate oznako položaja ali uredite metapodatke skladbe. Ko se ne predvaja, "
"programček prikaže informacije o zbirki in <emphasis>Nedavno predvajane "
"skladbe</emphasis>, kar vam omogoča ogled skladb in njihovo dodajanje na "
"seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Similar Artists"
msgstr "Podobni izvajalci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fetches artists similar to the currently playing one, with a short "
"description and options to find them in your collection, or on "
"<emphasis>Last.fm</emphasis>, and add to your current playlist."
msgstr ""
"Pridobi izvajalce, podobne izvajalcu, ki se trenutno predvaja, s kratkim "
"opisom in možnostmi, da jih poiščete v svoji zbirki ali na <emphasis>Last."
"fm</emphasis> in dodate na svoj trenutni seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1791
#, no-c-format
msgid "Upcoming Events"
msgstr "Prihajajoči dogodki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays upcoming events that involve the current artist or group. You can "
"set a venue locale to be watched by entering the applet settings and "
"narrowing it down under the Favorites section."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže prihajajoče dogodke, ki vključujejo trenutnega izvajalca ali "
"skupino. Lokalne nastavitve prizorišča lahko nastavite tako, da vnesete "
"nastavitve programčka in jih zožite v razdelku Priljubljene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1813
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wikipedia"
msgstr "Wikipedia"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Wikipedia</emphasis> page for the track or artist. Also browse "
"other <emphasis>Wikipedia</emphasis> links, and use the back button to go "
"back to the starting page."
msgstr ""
"Stran <emphasis>Wikipedije</emphasis> za skladbo ali izvajalca. Prebrskajte "
"tudi po drugih povezavah <emphasis>Wikipedije</emphasis> in uporabite gumb "
"za nazaj, da se vrnete na začetno stran."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1824
#, no-c-format
msgid "Labels"
msgstr "Oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"View, add and edit Labels for the current song. To add a Label just type it "
"in the text box and press &Enter;. Suggested Labels are user-contributed "
"tags from <emphasis>Last.fm</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si, dodajte in uredite oznake za trenutno pesem. Če želite dodati "
"oznako, jo vnesite v besedilno polje in pritisnite &Enter;. Predlagane "
"oznake so oznake, ki jih prispevajo uporabniki iz <emphasis>Last.fm</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabs"
msgstr "Zavihki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1863
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fetches and displays guitar and bass tabs (if available). Not editable."
msgstr ""
"Pridobi in prikaže zavihke za kitaro in bas (če so na voljo). Ni mogoče "
"urejati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1868
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lyrics"
msgstr "Besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the lyrics of the song that is currently playing. Add or change "
"lyrics scripts in the <link linkend=\"scripts\">Script Manager</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže besedilo pesmi, ki se trenutno predvaja. Dodajte ali spremenite "
"skripte besedil v <link linkend=\"scripts\">Upravljalniku skriptov</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1890 index.docbook:5278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Albums"
msgstr "Albumi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"View albums from the current artist or band that are available in your local "
"Collection."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si albume trenutnega izvajalca ali skupine, ki so na voljo v vaši "
"lokalni zbirki."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1912
#, no-c-format
msgid "Photos"
msgstr "Fotografije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This applet queries <emphasis>Flickr.com</emphasis> for pictures of the band "
"you're listening to. Open the settings to add more keywords to your query "
"(&eg;: live in tokyo).&gt;"
msgstr ""
"Ta programček išče <emphasis>Flickr.com</emphasis> slike skupine, ki jo "
"poslušate. Odprite nastavitve, da svoji poizvedbi dodate več ključnih besed "
"(&gt;: živeti v Tokiu).&gt;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Analyzer"
msgstr "Analizator"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a new applet in version 2.8. It provides basic audio visualizations. "
"A right click on it allows to configure the applet settings."
msgstr ""
"To je nov programček v različici 2.8. Zagotavlja osnovne zvočne "
"vizualizacije. Z desnim klikom nanj lahko konfigurirate nastavitve "
"programčka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1956
#, no-c-format
msgid "Info"
msgstr "Informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information about the current media source. Allows you to navigate through "
"internet services such as <emphasis>Librivox.org</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Informacije o trenutnem medijskem viru. Omogoča vam krmarjenje po "
"internetnih storitvah, kot je <emphasis>Librivox.org</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; offers excellent playlist management for all of your songs and "
"other audio files. Here you see a short playlist, sorted by album."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; ponuja odlično upravljanje seznamov predvajanja za vse vaše pesmi "
"in druge zvočne datoteke. Tukaj vidite kratek seznam predvajanja, razvrščen "
"po albumu."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1992
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&amarok; Playlist pane</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&amarok; Podokno seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1995
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&amarok; Playlist pane</para>"
msgstr "<para>&amarok; Podokno seznama predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2000
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic Playlist Manipulation"
msgstr "Osnovna manipulacija seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2009
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist Pop Up Dropper menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pojavna kapalka seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2012
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist Pop Up Dropper menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pojavna kapalka seznama predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding music to your playlist is a simple drag-and-drop, right-click or "
"double-click operation."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje glasbe na vaš seznam predvajanja je preprost postopek povleci in "
"spusti, desni klik ali dvoklik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two playlist-related options will be shown in the <emphasis>Context</"
"emphasis> pane in the center (the <emphasis>Pop-Up Dropper</emphasis>, or "
"<emphasis>PUD</emphasis>) when performing a drag-and-drop operation to add "
"music to your current playlist. You can either use <guilabel>Add to "
"Playlist</guilabel>, which will append the songs you have selected, or "
"<guilabel>Replace Playlist</guilabel>, which will replace all the contents "
"of the playlist with your selection."
msgstr ""
"Dve možnosti, povezani s seznamom predvajanja, bosta prikazani v podoknu "
"<emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> na sredini (<emphasis>Pojavna kapalka</"
"emphasis> ali <emphasis>PUD</emphasis>), ko izvajate vlečenje -in-spusti za "
"dodajanje glasbe na vaš trenutni seznam predvajanja. Lahko uporabite "
"<guilabel>Dodaj na seznam predvajanja</guilabel>, ki bo dodal skladbe, ki "
"ste jih izbrali, ali <guilabel>Zamenjaj seznam predvajanja</guilabel>, ki bo "
"zamenjal vso vsebino seznama predvajanja z vašim izborom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, dragging-and-dropping your selection into a position in the "
"<emphasis>Playlist</emphasis> pane also works."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da svoj izbor povlečete in spustite na položaj v podoknu "
"<emphasis>Seznam predvajanja</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-clicking on a track, album, or selected group will bring up a context "
"menu from which you can <guilabel>Add to Playlist</guilabel>, or "
"<guilabel>Replace Playlist</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Z desnim klikom na skladbo, album ali izbrano skupino se prikaže kontekstni "
"meni, v katerem lahko <guilabel>Dodaj na seznam predvajanja</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Zamenjaš seznam predvajanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-clicking a selection or pressing &Enter; while a track is selected in "
"the <emphasis>Media Sources</emphasis> pane will perform the same as "
"<guilabel>Add to Playlist</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Dvoklik na izbor ali pritisk &Enter; medtem ko je skladba izbrana v podoknu "
"<emphasis>Medijski viri</emphasis>, bo delovala enako kot <guilabel>Dodaj na "
"seznam predvajanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Middle-clicking an item will append it to the playlist and begin playing "
"from the start of the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Če s srednjo tipko kliknete element, ga dodate na seznam predvajanja in "
"začnete predvajati od začetka seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you tell the file browser to open a supported multimedia file, &amarok; "
"will append the selected file to the current playlist. Some multimedia files "
"contain playlists themselves or may have playlist files associated by name "
"(&eg; <emphasis>wav</emphasis> with <emphasis>cue</emphasis>). If &amarok; "
"detects such an association, it may add several items to the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Če brskalniku datotek naročite, naj odpre podprto večpredstavnostno "
"datoteko, &amarok; bo dodal izbrano datoteko na trenutni seznam predvajanja. "
"Nekatere večpredstavnostne datoteke same vsebujejo sezname predvajanja ali "
"imajo lahko datoteke seznamov predvajanja, povezane z imenom (&eg; "
"<emphasis>wav</emphasis> z <emphasis>cue</emphasis>). Če &amarok; zazna "
"takšno povezavo, lahko na seznam predvajanja doda več elementov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2032
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menu"
msgstr "Kontekstni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-clicking on any song or album in the playlist will bring up the "
"<emphasis>Playlist</emphasis> context menu."
msgstr ""
"Z desnim klikom na katero koli skladbo ali album na seznamu predvajanja se "
"prikaže kontekstni meni <emphasis>Seznam predvajanja</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2048
#, no-c-format
msgid "Queue/Dequeue Track"
msgstr "Čakalna vrsta/odstranitev sledi iz čakalne vrste"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2049
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Queuing a track will temporarily modify the play order without modifying the "
"actual playlist order by setting the user-selected track as the next track."
msgstr ""
"Če skladbo postavite v čakalno vrsto, boste začasno spremenili vrstni red "
"predvajanja, ne da bi spremenili dejanski vrstni red seznama predvajanja, "
"tako da skladbo, ki jo izbere uporabnik, nastavite kot naslednjo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As many tracks as required can be queued, and the order of queuing is "
"indicated by a green circle with the determined order. Choose the tracks by "
"<keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>Click</keycap></keycombo> for a block of tracks, or "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Click</keycap></keycombo> for individual tracks. The "
"order in which the tracks are selected is the determined order."
msgstr ""
"V čakalno vrsto lahko postavite poljubno število skladb, vrstni red pa je "
"označen z zelenim krogom z določenim vrstnim redom. Izberite skladbe s "
"<keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>Klikom</keycap></keycombo> za blok skladb ali "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Klikom</keycap></keycombo> za posamezne skladbe. "
"Vrstni red, v katerem so izbrane skladbe, je določen vrstni red."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tracks can be dequeued by opening the context menu and selecting the "
"<guilabel>Dequeue Track</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Skladbe lahko odstranite iz čakalne vrste tako, da odprete kontekstni meni "
"in izberete možnost <guilabel>Odstrani skladbo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2055
#, no-c-format
msgid "More about the <link linkend=\"queue-manager\">Queue Manager</link>."
msgstr ""
"Več o <link linkend=\"queue-manager\">Upravljalniku čakalnih vrst</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop Playing After This Track"
msgstr "Ustavite predvajanje po tej skladbi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choosing this option allows a track to finish, after which &amarok; will "
"stop playing . It will be indicated by the stop icon in place of the track "
"number. Selecting this option on a track already marked will unmark it. Only "
"one track in the playlist may be so marked."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, se skladba zaključi, po tem pa &amarok; bo prenehal "
"igrati. Označena bo z ikono za zaustavitev namesto številke skladbe. Če "
"izberete to možnost na že označeni skladbi, jo boste odstranili. Samo ena "
"skladba na seznamu predvajanja je lahko tako označena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2062
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove From Playlist"
msgstr "Odstrani s seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2063
#, no-c-format
msgid "This removes the selected track from the current playlist."
msgstr "S tem odstranite izbrano skladbo s trenutnega seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2066
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Position Marker"
msgstr "Dodajte oznako položaja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding a position marker is only available for the currently playing track. "
"This will add a bookmark in the seek bar at the top of the &amarok; "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje oznake položaja je na voljo samo za skladbo, ki se trenutno "
"predvaja. To bo dodalo zaznamek v iskalno vrstico na vrhu &amarok; vmesnik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show in Media Sources"
msgstr "Pokaži v medijskih virih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This displays the track selected in the <link linkend=\"the-media-sources-"
"pane\">Media Sources</link> pane, which is on the left by default."
msgstr ""
"To prikaže skladbo, izbrano v podoknu <link linkend=\"the-media-sources-pane"
"\">Medijski viri</link>, ki je privzeto na levi strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2074
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Album</title>"
msgstr "<title>Album</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2083
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist album menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni albuma seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2086
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist album menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni albuma seznama predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are per-album options which will affect the entire album the track "
"belongs to, rather than the track itself. The options are largely the same "
"as the album menu in the <link linkend=\"the-media-sources-pane\">Media "
"Sources</link> pane."
msgstr ""
"To so možnosti za posamezen album, ki bodo vplivale na celoten album, ki mu "
"skladba pripada, in ne na samo skladbo. Možnosti so večinoma enake kot meni "
"albuma v podoknu <link linkend=\"the-media-sources-pane\">Viri "
"predstavnosti</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2094
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Track Details"
msgstr "Uredi podrobnosti skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option brings up the <link linkend=\"tag-editor\">Edit Track Details</"
"link> dialog for the selected tracks."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost odpre pogovorno okno <link linkend=\"tag-editor\">Urejanje "
"podrobnosti skladbe</link> za izbrane skladbe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2099
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching the Playlist"
msgstr "Iskanje po seznamu predvajanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist searching options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti iskanja po seznamu predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist searching options</para>"
msgstr "<para>Možnosti iskanja po seznamu predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; offers powerful searching capabilities for playlists. Simply enter "
"your query for a song into the text box labelled <guilabel>Search playlist</"
"guilabel> and it will match your keywords up against the match criteria you "
"specify in the options menu &mdash; for instance, you can choose to search "
"only by <guilabel>Albums</guilabel> and not <guilabel>Artists</guilabel>, or "
"choose to match both of them."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; ponuja zmogljive zmožnosti iskanja seznamov predvajanja. Preprosto "
"vnesite svojo poizvedbo za pesem v besedilno polje z oznako <guilabel>Išči "
"po seznamu predvajanja</guilabel> in ujemala se bo z vašimi ključnimi "
"besedami glede na merila ujemanja, ki jih določite v meniju z možnostmi "
"&mdash; na primer, lahko izberete iskanje samo po <guilabel>Albumih</"
"guilabel> in ne po <guilabel>Izvajalcih</guilabel> ali pa izberete iskanje "
"po obeh."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist search bar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Iskalna vrstica seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2129
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist search bar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Iskalna vrstica seznama predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-"
"up.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> icon moves the "
"selection to the previous search result, and <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> moves to the next result, all without "
"losing focus on the search input box."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete ikono <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-go-up.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, "
"premaknete izbor na prejšnji rezultat iskanja in <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> premakne na naslednji rezultat, vse brez "
"izgube fokusa na polje za vnos iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-clear-"
"locationbar-rtl.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"icon in the search field will clear your query."
msgstr ""
"Ikona <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-clear-"
"locationbar-rtl.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v "
"iskalnem polju bo počistila vašo poizvedbo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabling <guilabel>Show only matches</guilabel> from the menu will cause "
"your playlist to display only the tracks matching the query."
msgstr ""
"Če v meniju omogočite <guilabel>Prikaži samo ujemanja</guilabel>, bo vaš "
"seznam predvajanja prikazal samo skladbe, ki se ujemajo s poizvedbo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More about <link linkend=\"playlist-filtering\">Playlist filtering here</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Več o <link linkend=\"playlist-filtering\">filtriranju seznamov predvajanja "
"tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting Levels and Bookmarking"
msgstr "Razvrščanje ravni in zaznamki"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist sorting and bookmarking toolbar</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Orodna vrstica za razvrščanje seznamov predvajanja in zaznamke</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2155
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist sorting and bookmarking toolbar</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Orodna vrstica za razvrščanje seznamov predvajanja in zaznamke</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting Levels"
msgstr "Ravni razvrščanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Menu for adding a sorting level</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni za dodajanje ravni razvrščanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Menu for adding a sorting level</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni za dodajanje ravni razvrščanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok;'s robust sorting abilities offer the ability to sort not only by "
"one field of a track, but by many combined in a series of levels."
msgstr ""
"Robustne zmožnosti razvrščanja &amarok; ponujajo možnost razvrščanja ne le "
"po enem polju skladbe, temveč po več združenih v nizu ravni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many different modes by which a sorting level can act. For "
"instance, songs can be sorted by their <guilabel>Genre</guilabel> and then "
"their <guilabel>Album</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja veliko različnih načinov, po katerih lahko deluje raven razvrščanja. "
"Pesmi lahko na primer razvrstite po <guilabel>Zvrsti</guilabel> in nato po "
"<guilabel>Albumu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A sorting level can be added by clicking the right-pointing triangle, which "
"will bring up the menu for adding another sorting level."
msgstr ""
"Raven razvrščanja lahko dodate s klikom na desno usmerjen trikotnik, kar bo "
"prikazalo meni za dodajanje druge ravni razvrščanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the small triangle on the right of the sorting level's name will "
"cause items in the playlist to switch between ascending and descending "
"order, which is indicated by the direction in which the triangle is pointing "
"&mdash; up or down, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete majhen trikotnik na desni strani imena ravni razvrščanja, bodo "
"elementi na seznamu predvajanja preklopili med naraščajočim in padajočim "
"vrstnim redom, kar je označeno s smerjo, v katero kaže trikotnik &mdash; "
"navzgor ali navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a sorting level, click the name of the sorting level that precedes "
"the one you wish to remove. Multiple sorting levels can be removed &mdash; "
"provided that they are all lower in the hierarchy &mdash; by clicking on the "
"ancestor of all of them. If you wish to clear all sorting levels, you can "
"click the playlist icon to the left of the first right-pointing arrow."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti raven razvrščanja, kliknite ime ravni razvrščanja, ki "
"je pred tisto, ki jo želite odstraniti. Več ravni razvrščanja je mogoče "
"odstraniti &mdash; pod pogojem, da so vsi nižje v hierarhiji &mdash; s "
"klikom na prednika vseh. Če želite počistiti vse ravni razvrščanja, lahko "
"kliknete ikono seznama predvajanja levo od prve puščice, ki kaže desno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarking"
msgstr "Dodajanje med zaznamke"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2197
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bookmarking menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni zaznamkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2200
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Bookmarking menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni zaznamkov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bookmarking menu provides options to save your <link linkend=\"changing-"
"the-playlist-layout\">current playlist layout</link>. Clicking "
"<guilabel>Bookmark Playlist Setup</guilabel> will add your playlist layout "
"to the layout bookmarks, which can be viewed in <link linkend=\"bookmark-"
"manager\">Bookmark Manager</link>."
msgstr ""
"Meni zaznamkov ponuja možnosti za shranjevanje vaše <link linkend=\"changing-"
"the-playlist-layout\">trenutne postavitve seznama predvajanja</link>. Če "
"kliknete <guilabel>Nastavitev seznama predvajanja med zaznamki</guilabel>, "
"boste dodali postavitev seznama predvajanja med zaznamke postavitve, ki si "
"jih lahko ogledate v <link linkend=\"bookmark-manager\">Upravljalniku "
"zaznamkov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Copy Current View Bookmark to Clipboard</guilabel> copies an "
"&amarok; playlist layout URL to the clipboard, which can be used for backing "
"up your playlist layout."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kopiraj zaznamek trenutnega pogleda v odložišče</guilabel> kopira "
"&amarok; URL postavitve seznama predvajanja v odložišče, ki ga lahko "
"uporabite za varnostno kopiranje postavitve seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist Functions"
msgstr "Funkcije seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2220
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist bottom bar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Spodnja vrstica seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2223
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist bottom bar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Spodnja vrstica seznama predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bottom bar of the <emphasis>Playlist</emphasis> pane provides various "
"additional options for manipulation of your playlist."
msgstr ""
"Spodnja vrstica podokna <emphasis>Seznam predvajanja</emphasis> ponuja "
"različne dodatne možnosti za upravljanje vašega seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Empty playlist of all playlists, albums and tracks."
msgstr ""
"Prazen seznam predvajanja vseh seznamov predvajanja, albumov in skladb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save your playlist. Right-click to rename it, default is the date as a name. "
"Left-click to bring up the <emphasis>Save Playlist</emphasis> menu, to save "
"your playlist file onto the hard drive instead of the database."
msgstr ""
"Shranite svoj seznam predvajanja. Z desnim klikom ga preimenujete, privzeto "
"je datum kot ime. Z levim klikom prikličete meni <emphasis>Shrani seznam "
"predvajanja</emphasis>, da datoteko seznama predvajanja shranite na trdi "
"disk namesto v bazo podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls playlist to the track which is currently playing and highlights it "
"&mdash; useful for a large playlist."
msgstr ""
"Pomakne seznam predvajanja do skladbe, ki se trenutno predvaja, in jo označi "
"&mdash; uporabno za velik seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the playlist queue; tracks played first before the playlist resumes. "
"More about the <link linkend=\"queue-manager\">Queue Manager</link>."
msgstr ""
"Uredite čakalno vrsto seznama predvajanja; predvajane skladbe, preden se "
"seznam predvajanja nadaljuje. Več o <link linkend=\"queue-manager"
"\">Upravljalniku čakalnih vrst</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Playlist menu"
msgstr "Meni Shrani seznam predvajanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Save playlist menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni za shranjevanje seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2390
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Save playlist menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni za shranjevanje seznama predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Left-click <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"document-save.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> to "
"bring up the <guilabel>Save Playlist</guilabel> menu, to save your playlist "
"file onto the hard drive instead of the database."
msgstr ""
"Levi klik <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"document-save.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, da "
"prikažete <guilabel>Shrani seznam predvajanja</guilabel> meni, da datoteko s "
"seznamom predvajanja shranite na trdi disk namesto v bazo podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track Progression"
msgstr "Sledite napredovanju"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2407
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Track progression menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni za sledenje napredovanju</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2410
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Track progression menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni za napredovanje sledi</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Track Progression</guilabel> menu enables you to modify the "
"order in which &amarok; progresses through the tracks in your playlist."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guilabel>Sledenje napredovanju</guilabel> vam omogoča spreminjanje "
"vrstnega reda, v katerem &amarok; napreduje po skladbah na vašem seznamu "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top half of the menu specifies repeat options &mdash; whether songs "
"should be repeated by track, by album or by playlist; whereas the bottom "
"half specifies the order in which the tracks play in &mdash; in random order "
"or by favor. Only one type of progression may be selected, &eg; you cannot "
"select both random track and repeat playlist."
msgstr ""
"Zgornja polovica menija določa možnosti ponovitve &mdash; ali naj se pesmi "
"ponavljajo po skladbi, albumu ali seznamu predvajanja; medtem ko spodnja "
"polovica določa vrstni red predvajanja skladb v &mdash; po naključnem "
"vrstnem redu ali naklonjeno. Izberete lahko samo eno vrsto napredovanja, "
"npr. ne morete izbrati tako naključne skladbe kot ponavljajočega se seznama "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Favor"
msgstr "Uslugo"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2428
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist favor menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni priljubljenih seznamov predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2431
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist favor menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni priljubljenih seznamov predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Favor is an innovative method to determine the next track to be played when "
"using the random selection mode. The next track to be played can be "
"determined depending on their score (a measure of how often they are "
"played), their user-given rating, or if they have not been recently played."
msgstr ""
"Favor je inovativna metoda za določanje naslednje skladbe za predvajanje pri "
"uporabi načina naključne izbire. Naslednjo skladbo, ki jo je treba "
"predvajati, je mogoče določiti glede na njihov rezultat (merilo, kako "
"pogosto se predvajajo), njihovo oceno, ki jo je dal uporabnik, ali če niso "
"bili nedavno predvajani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Amarok"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje Amaroka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On first start, some basic configuration is done; see also <link linkend="
"\"getting-started\">Quick Start Guide: Getting Started</link>. But there is "
"more under the hood."
msgstr ""
"Ob prvem zagonu je narejenih nekaj osnovnih konfiguracij; glejte tudi <link "
"linkend=\"getting-started\">Vodnik za hiter začetek: Kako začeti</link>. "
"Toda pod pokrovom je še več."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To access the <emphasis>Configuration Menu</emphasis>, go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Amarok...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and see the following dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do <emphasis>konfiguracijskega menija</emphasis> pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Amarok ..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in si oglejte naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2456
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>General configuration options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošne konfiguracijske možnosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2459
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>General configuration options</para>"
msgstr "<para>Možnosti splošne konfiguracije</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2464
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the screenshot above, see some <emphasis>General Options</emphasis> you "
"can set. Depending on the distribution, the default settings can vary. When "
"hovering over the options with the mouse pointer, a tooltip will show to "
"explain the individual settings."
msgstr ""
"Na zgornjem posnetku zaslona si oglejte nekaj <emphasis>Splošnih možnosti</"
"emphasis>, ki jih lahko nastavite. Privzete nastavitve se lahko razlikujejo "
"glede na distribucijo. Ko se s kazalcem miške pomaknete nad možnosti, se "
"prikaže opis orodja, ki pojasnjuje posamezne nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2467
#, no-c-format
msgid "General options:"
msgstr "Splošne možnosti:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2474 index.docbook:2559 index.docbook:2641 index.docbook:2683
#: index.docbook:2757 index.docbook:2899 index.docbook:3008
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option"
msgstr "Možnost"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2475 index.docbook:2560 index.docbook:2642 index.docbook:2684
#: index.docbook:2758 index.docbook:2900 index.docbook:3009
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tooltip"
msgstr "Opis orodja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show tray icon"
msgstr "Pokaži ikono pladnja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to enable the &amarok; system tray icon."
msgstr "Označite, da omogočite &amarok; ikona sistemske vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2489
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically retrieve cover art"
msgstr "Samodejno pridobi naslovnico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2492
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to enable the automatic retrieval of cover art from the internet."
msgstr "Označite, da omogočite samodejno pridobivanje naslovnic iz interneta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable context applets collapse animations"
msgstr "Omogoči animacije strnjevanja kontekstnih programčkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2500
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to enable animations when context applets collapse."
msgstr ""
"Označite, če želite omogočiti animacije, ko se kontekstni programčki zrušijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2505
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically scroll playlist to current track"
msgstr "Samodejno pomikanje po seznamu predvajanja do trenutne skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check to make the playlist scroll so the current track is always visible."
msgstr ""
"Označite, da se seznam predvajanja premika, tako da je trenutna skladba "
"vedno vidna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2513
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Moodbar in progress slider"
msgstr "Pokaži drsnik Moodbar v teku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Moodbar</emphasis> makes it possible to navigate in your music "
"visually. Please note that this feature requires the <link linkend=\"the-"
"moodbar\">external Moodbar Generator tool</link>, or a script."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Moodbar</emphasis> omogoča vizualno krmarjenje po glasbi. "
"Upoštevajte, da ta funkcija zahteva <link linkend=\"the-moodbar\">zunanje "
"orodje Moodbar Generator</link> ali skript."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2521
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moodbar style"
msgstr "Stil vrstice razpoloženja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the mood display style."
msgstr "Izberite slog prikaza razpoloženja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you enable the <emphasis>Moodbar</emphasis>, be aware of the following "
"requirements: the Moodbar will only display if your tracks have been tagged "
"with moods. For more about the Moodbar, refer to: <link linkend=\"the-moodbar"
"\">Moodbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko omogočite <emphasis>vrstico razpoloženja</emphasis>, bodite pozorni na "
"naslednje zahteve: vrstica razpoloženja bo prikazana le, če so vaše skladbe "
"označene z razpoloženji. Za več informacij o vrstici razpoloženja glejte: "
"<link linkend=\"the-moodbar\">Vrstica razpoloženja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local Collection"
msgstr "Lokalna zbirka"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2542
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Local Collection configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija lokalne zbirke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Local Collection configuration</para>"
msgstr "<para>Konfiguracija lokalne zbirke</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog shows your file system in a tree structure, called "
"<emphasis>Collection Folders</emphasis>. Selecting a folder always includes "
"its subfolders. These folders will be scanned for media to make up your "
"collection. You can right-click on a folder to individually rescan it, if it "
"was previously selected."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno prikazuje vaš datotečni sistem v drevesni strukturi, "
"imenovani <emphasis>Mape zbirk</emphasis>. Izbira mape vedno vključuje njene "
"podmape. Te mape bodo skenirane za medije, da sestavijo vašo zbirko. Z desno "
"miškino tipko lahko kliknete mapo, da jo posamično znova pregledate, če je "
"bila prej izbrana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection options:"
msgstr "Možnosti zbiranja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2566
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fully Rescan Entire Collection"
msgstr "Popolnoma ponovno skenirajte celotno zbirko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rescan your entire collection. This will <emphasis>not</emphasis> delete any "
"statistics."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno skenirajte celotno zbirko. S tem <emphasis>ne</emphasis> boste "
"izbrisali nobene statistike."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import"
msgstr "Uvozi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Imports ratings and/or statistics from older &amarok; versions, the batch "
"scanner, or media players."
msgstr ""
"Uvozi ocene in/ali statistiko iz starejših &amarok; različice, paketni "
"skener ali predstavnostni predvajalniki."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scan folders recursively (requires full rescan if newly checked)"
msgstr ""
"Rekurzivno skeniranje map (zahteva popolno ponovno skeniranje, če je na novo "
"označeno)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2585
#, no-c-format
msgid "If selected, &amarok; will read all subfolders."
msgstr "Če je izbrano, &amarok; bo prebral vse podmape."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Watch folders for changes"
msgstr "Opazujte mape za spremembe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, the collection folders will be watched for changes. The watcher "
"will not notice changes behind symbolic links."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete, bodo mape zbirke opazovane za spremembe. Opazovalec ne bo "
"opazil sprememb za simbolnimi povezavami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2598
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Music: Transcode tracks"
msgstr "Uvažanje glasbe: Prekodiraj skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether &amarok; should transcode tracks when they are copied or moved to "
"<emphasis>Local Collection</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Ali &amarok; mora prekodirati skladbe, ko so kopirane ali premaknjene v "
"<emphasis>Lokalno zbirko</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import Statistics"
msgstr "Statistika uvoza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to import statistics, &eg; ratings and scores from "
"either"
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča uvoz statističnih podatkov, npr. ocene in ocene bodisi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"an older &amarok; 1.4.x version (from <guilabel>SQLite</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> or <guilabel>PostgreSQL</guilabel> databases)"
msgstr ""
"starejši &amarok; Različica 1.4.x (iz baz podatkov <guilabel>SQLite</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> ali <guilabel>PostgreSQL</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2612
#, no-c-format
msgid "from <guilabel>iTunes</guilabel>"
msgstr "iz <guilabel>iTunes</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It does <emphasis>not</emphasis> import statistics from an &amarok; 2.x "
"database, so if you want to merge an older 2.x database version, you will "
"need to do this by hand."
msgstr ""
"Statistike <emphasis>ne</emphasis> uvaža iz datoteke &amarok; baze podatkov "
"2.x, tako da če želite združiti starejšo različico baze podatkov 2.x, boste "
"morali to narediti ročno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Metadata"
msgstr "Metapodatki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog will allow you to configure the settings for metadata handling. "
"This is a separate page starting with Amarok 2.7"
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno vam bo omogočilo, da konfigurirate nastavitve za ravnanje "
"z metapodatki. To je ločena stran, ki se začne z Amarokom 2.7"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2634
#, no-c-format
msgid "Metadata options:"
msgstr "Možnosti metapodatkov:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Write statistics to file"
msgstr "Zapišite statistiko v datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check to write play-changing statistics as tags back to the audio files."
msgstr ""
"Označite, če želite zapisati statistiko spreminjanja predvajanja kot oznake "
"nazaj v zvočne datoteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2656
#, no-c-format
msgid "Write covers to file, maximum size..."
msgstr "Zapišite naslovnice v datoteko, največja velikost ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check to write changed covers back to the audio files. This will replace "
"existing embedded covers. Select a value from the drop-down list to set the "
"maximum size of the cover."
msgstr ""
"Označite, če želite spremenjene naslovnice zapisati nazaj v zvočne datoteke. "
"To bo nadomestilo obstoječe vdelane pokrove. Na spustnem seznamu izberite "
"vrednost, da nastavite največjo velikost pokrova."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2664
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable character set detection in ID3 tags"
msgstr "Omogoči zaznavanje nabora znakov v oznakah ID3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, Amarok will use Mozilla's Character Set Detector to attempt to "
"automatically guess the character sets used in ID3 tags. If your tags are "
"correct, it is more safe to leave this option turned off."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo Amarok uporabil Mozillin detektor nabora znakov, da bo "
"poskušal samodejno uganiti nabore znakov, uporabljene v oznakah ID3. Če so "
"vaše oznake pravilne, je bolj varno, če to možnost pustite izklopljeno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2673
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statistics Synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija statistike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog will allow you to <link linkend=\"statistics-synchronization"
"\">keep statistics of your collections synchronized</link>. Make sure to "
"only check collections between which you want to synchronize metadata."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno vam bo omogočilo, da <link linkend=\"statistics-"
"synchronization\">vodite statistiko svojih zbirk sinhronizirano</link>. "
"Preverite samo zbirke, med katerimi želite sinhronizirati metapodatke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2676
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statistics Synchronization options:"
msgstr "Možnosti sinhronizacije statistike:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Rating"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj oceno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2693
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to synchronize ratings between collections."
msgstr "Označite za sinhronizacijo ocen med zbirkami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize First Played"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj prvo predvajano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2701
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to synchronize first played dates between collections."
msgstr ""
"Označite, če želite sinhronizirati datume prvega predvajanja med zbirkami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2706
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Last Played"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj nazadnje predvajano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to synchronize last played dates between collections."
msgstr "Označite za sinhronizacijo datumov zadnjega predvajanja med zbirkami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Playcount"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj Playcount"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to synchronize playcounts between collections."
msgstr "Označite za sinhronizacijo števila predvajanj med zbirkami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2722
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Labels"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2725
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to synchronize labels between collections."
msgstr "Označite, če želite sinhronizirati oznake med zbirkami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playback"
msgstr "Predvajanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2742
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playback configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2745
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playback configuration dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the playback options, as well as the KDE multimedia framework "
"&phonon;."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte možnosti predvajanja in multimedijsko ogrodje KDE &phonon;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2764
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fadeout on stop"
msgstr "Zatemnitev ob ustavitvi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &amarok; will slowly fade the volume of the playing track on "
"stop or at the end of the playlist, or stop playback immediately."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, &amarok; bo počasi zmanjšal glasnost predvajane skladbe, ko "
"se ustavi ali na koncu seznama predvajanja, ali takoj ustavi predvajanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2772
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fadeout on pause"
msgstr "Zatemnitev ob premoru"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &amarok; will slowly fade the volume of the playing track on "
"pausing the current track."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, &amarok; bo počasi zmanjševal glasnost predvajane skladbe, "
"ko začasno ustavi trenutno skladbo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2780
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fadeout duration"
msgstr "Trajanje zatemnitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2783
#, no-c-format
msgid "The length of the fadeout, in milliseconds."
msgstr "Dolžina zatemnitve v milisekundah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2788
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inhibit automatic suspend if playing"
msgstr "Prepreči samodejno prekinitev med predvajanjem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &amarok; will prevent the computer from being suspended will a "
"track is playing."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, &amarok; prepreči začasno zaustavitev računalnika, ko se "
"skladba predvaja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pause playback on suspend"
msgstr "Začasna ustavitev predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &amarok; will pause playing of the current track when the "
"computer is about to suspend."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, &amarok; bo začasno ustavil predvajanje trenutne skladbe, ko "
"bo računalnik prekinil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2804
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resume playback on start"
msgstr "Nadaljevanje predvajanja ob začetku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &amarok; will resume playback where you left it the last session "
"-- just like a tape-player."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, &amarok; bo nadaljeval predvajanje tam, kjer ste ga pustili "
"v zadnji seji -- tako kot kasetofon."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2813
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Phonon"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje Phonona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&phonon; is the multimedia framework used by &amarok;. It was created to "
"allow KDE 4 to be independent of any single multimedia framework such as "
"<guilabel>GStreamer</guilabel> or <guilabel>VLC</guilabel> and to provide a "
"stable API for KDE 4's lifetime. As an added bonus, it simplifies "
"development by providing a simple API that works across different platforms "
"such as <guilabel>Windows</guilabel> and <guilabel>OS X</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&phonon; je multimedijsko ogrodje, ki ga uporablja &amarok;. Ustvarjen je "
"bil, da omogoči KDE 4 neodvisnost od katerega koli posameznega "
"multimedijskega ogrodja, kot je <guilabel>GStreamer</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>VLC</guilabel>, in da zagotovi stabilen API za življenjsko dobo "
"KDE 4. Kot dodaten bonus poenostavlja razvoj z zagotavljanjem preprostega "
"API-ja, ki deluje na različnih platformah, kot sta <guilabel>Windows</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>OS X</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2816
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result of all this for you, the user, is that you can choose the "
"multimedia framework that works best for you. This is usually pre-configured "
"by your distribution."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat vsega tega za vas, uporabnika, je, da lahko izberete multimedijsko "
"ogrodje, ki vam najbolj ustreza. To običajno vnaprej konfigurira vaša "
"distribucija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Playback problems in &amarok; are typically not &amarok; issues, but rather "
"&phonon; issues, as &amarok; doesn't handle sound directly anymore."
msgstr ""
"Težave s predvajanjem v &amarok; običajno niso &amarok; vprašanja, temveč "
"&phonon; vprašanja, kot &amarok; zvoka ne obravnava več neposredno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2820
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device Preference tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Nastavitve naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on your OS and distribution, you may need to use <guilabel>ALSA</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>OSS</guilabel>, <guilabel>PulseAudio</guilabel>, or "
"something else as your default playback device. Find one that works for you "
"with the <guilabel>Test</guilabel> button and apply to all types of output. "
"If you would like different types of output to go with different devices, "
"this is possible as well."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od vašega operacijskega sistema in distribucije boste morda morali "
"uporabiti <guilabel>ALSA</guilabel>, <guilabel>OSS</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>PulseAudio</guilabel> ali kaj drugega kot privzeto napravo za "
"predvajanje. Z gumbom <guilabel>Preizkusi</guilabel> poiščite tistega, ki "
"vam ustreza, in ga uporabite za vse vrste izpisa. Če želite, da različne "
"vrste izhoda delujejo z različnimi napravami, je tudi to mogoče."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speaker Setup tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Nastavitev zvočnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should you wish to change the standard speaker setup, here is the place to "
"do it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti standardno nastavitev zvočnikov, je tukaj kraj, kjer "
"lahko to storite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2854
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backend tab"
msgstr "Zadnji zavihek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on your operating system you may see options such as "
"<emphasis>Gstreamer</emphasis>, <emphasis>VLC</emphasis>, or <emphasis>DS9</"
"emphasis> (Windows) here. The recommended phonon-backend for &Linux; users "
"is <emphasis>VLC</emphasis> or <emphasis>Gstreamer</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od operacijskega sistema boste tukaj morda videli možnosti, kot so "
"<emphasis>Gstreamer</emphasis>, <emphasis>VLC</emphasis> ali <emphasis>DS9</"
"emphasis> (Windows). Priporočeno zaledje phonon za &Linux; uporabnikov je "
"<emphasis>VLC</emphasis> ali <emphasis>Gstreamer</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't see <emphasis>VLC</emphasis> or <emphasis>Gstreamer</emphasis>, "
"install the package for it. For most distributions the package for "
"<emphasis>VLC</emphasis>, for example, would be <guilabel>phonon-backend-"
"vlc</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če ne vidite <emphasis>VLC</emphasis> ali <emphasis>Gstreamer</emphasis>, "
"namestite paket zanj. Za večino distribucij bi bil paket za <emphasis>VLC</"
"emphasis> na primer <guilabel>phonon-backend-vlc</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each backend comes with its own codecs, so depending on the backend you "
"choose you will need to also download the codecs, as most distributions "
"don't ship them for legal reasons."
msgstr ""
"Vsako zaledje ima svoje kodeke, tako da boste morali glede na izbrano "
"zaledje prenesti tudi kodeke, saj jih večina distribucij ne pošilja iz "
"pravnih razlogov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2877
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "Obvestila"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2886
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Notifications configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo obvestil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2889
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Notifications configuration dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo obvestil</para>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use On-Screen Display"
msgstr "Uporabite zaslonski prikaz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check to enable the <emphasis>On-Screen Display</emphasis>. The "
"<emphasis>OSD</emphasis> briefly displays track data when a new track is "
"played. Once checked, the OSD will be visible on your screen and you can "
"drag it to the location you prefer."
msgstr ""
"Označite, da omogočite <emphasis>zaslonski prikaz</emphasis>. <emphasis>OSD</"
"emphasis> na kratko prikaže podatke o skladbi, ko se predvaja nova skladba. "
"Ko potrdite, bo zaslonski meni viden na vašem zaslonu in ga lahko povlečete "
"na želeno mesto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2914
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duration"
msgstr "Trajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time in milliseconds for which to show the OSD. The value must be "
"between 500 ms and 10000 ms."
msgstr ""
"Čas v milisekundah za prikaz OSD. Vrednost mora biti med 500 ms in 10000 ms."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2922
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screen"
msgstr "Zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to choose the screen that should display the OSD if you have a "
"multiscreen setup. Default is 0."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam izbiro zaslona, ki naj prikaže OSD, če imate nastavitev več "
"zaslonov. Privzeto je 0."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translucent"
msgstr "Prosojno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2933
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to enable translucency if supported by your desktop system."
msgstr "Označite, da omogočite prosojnost, če jo vaš namizni sistem podpira."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2938
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font scale"
msgstr "Merilo pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2941
#, no-c-format
msgid "(choose the size of the font in the OSD)"
msgstr "(izberite velikost pisave v OSD)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2946
#, no-c-format
msgid "Don't show when a fullscreen application is active"
msgstr "Ne prikaži, ko je aktivna celozaslonska aplikacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not show On-Screen Display if another application is focused and running "
"in fullscreen mode."
msgstr ""
"Ne prikaži zaslonskega prikaza, če je druga aplikacija fokusirana in deluje "
"v celozaslonskem načinu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2954
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use custom colors"
msgstr "Uporabite barve po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check to enable custom colors for the <emphasis>On-Screen Display</emphasis> "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Označite, da omogočite barve po meri za besedilo <emphasis>Prikaz na "
"zaslonu</emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2962
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text color"
msgstr "Barva besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2965
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click to select the color of the <emphasis>OSD</emphasis> text."
msgstr "Kliknite, da izberete barvo besedila <emphasis>OSD</emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2970
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use system notifications"
msgstr "Uporabite sistemska obvestila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check to use the system notification. This can vary depending on your "
"desktop system and/or distribution."
msgstr ""
"Označite, če želite uporabiti sistemsko obvestilo. To se lahko razlikuje "
"glede na vaš namizni sistem in/ali distribucijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2980
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Database</title>"
msgstr "<title>Baza podatkov</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2989
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>External Database configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo zunanje baze podatkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2992
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>External Database configuration dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo zunanje baze podatkov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default database is already set to use embedded <guilabel>MySQL</"
"guilabel>. For most users there is no need to configure an external "
"database, as there is no change in performance. If you want to share your "
"database or use it remotely, you can configure an external <guilabel>MySQL</"
"guilabel> database."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta zbirka podatkov je že nastavljena za uporabo vdelanega "
"<guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>. Za večino uporabnikov ni potrebe po "
"konfiguraciji zunanje baze podatkov, saj ni sprememb v zmogljivosti. Če "
"želite deliti svojo zbirko podatkov ali jo uporabljati na daljavo, lahko "
"konfigurirate zunanjo zbirko podatkov <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2999
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; expects the external database and user account to already exist. "
"The user also requires full access to the database. You MUST restart "
"&amarok; after changing these settings."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; pričakuje, da zunanja zbirka podatkov in uporabniški račun že "
"obstajata. Uporabnik potrebuje tudi popoln dostop do baze podatkov. MORATE "
"znova zagnati &amarok; po spremembi teh nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your database is not already set up, you can use the SQL commands in the "
"field at the bottom to do so, after replacing the password with the correct "
"one."
msgstr ""
"Če vaša zbirka podatkov še ni nastavljena, lahko za to uporabite ukaze SQL v "
"polju na dnu, potem ko zamenjate geslo s pravilnim."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3015
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use external MySQL Database"
msgstr "Uporabite zunanjo bazo podatkov MySQL"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3018
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to enable the use of an external database."
msgstr "Označite, če želite omogočiti uporabo zunanje baze podatkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3023
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Server</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Strežnik</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3026
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the name of the existing <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> server."
msgstr "Vnesite ime obstoječega strežnika <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3031
#, no-c-format
msgid "Port"
msgstr "Pristanišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the port number to access the server. Default is port 3306."
msgstr "Vnesite številko vrat za dostop do strežnika. Privzeto so vrata 3306."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Username"
msgstr "Uporabniško ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the username to access the database with full access privileges."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite uporabniško ime za dostop do zbirke podatkov s polnimi pravicami "
"dostopa."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3047
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password"
msgstr "Geslo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3050
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the password for the default user."
msgstr "Vnesite geslo za privzetega uporabnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3055
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Database</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Baza podatkov</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the name of the database. Default preset is amarokdb."
msgstr "Vnesite ime baze podatkov. Privzeta prednastavitev je amarokdb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find more information about the External Database <link linkend="
"\"external-database\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Več informacij o zunanji zbirki podatkov najdete <link linkend=\"external-"
"database\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3067
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Vtičniki"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3076
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Plugins configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo vtičnikov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3079
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Plugins configuration dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo vtičnikov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plugins configuration controls <guilabel>Collections</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Internet Services</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Local Collection "
"Backends</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija vtičnikov nadzoruje <guilabel>Zbirke</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Internetne storitve</guilabel> in <guilabel>Zaledja lokalnih "
"zbirk</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3086
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collections"
msgstr "Zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; offers you access to the following Collections, if they are "
"available:"
msgstr "&amarok; vam ponuja dostop do naslednjih zbirk, če so na voljo:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3094
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Collection</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Zbirka</entry>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3101
#, no-c-format
msgid "AudioCD Collection"
msgstr "Zbirka avdio CD-jev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3104
#, no-c-format
msgid "AudioCD collection plugin for &amarok;"
msgstr "Vtičnik za zbirko zvočnih CD-jev za &amarok;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3109
#, no-c-format
msgid "DAAP Collection"
msgstr "Zbirka DAAP"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3112
#, no-c-format
msgid "DAAP collection plugin for &amarok;"
msgstr "Vtičnik zbiranja DAAP za &amarok;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3117
#, no-c-format
msgid "iPod, iPad &amp; iPhone Collection"
msgstr "iPod, iPad &amp; Zbirka iPhone"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugin to use iPod-like devices as collections in &amarok;"
msgstr "Vtičnik za uporabo iPod podobnih naprav kot zbirk v &amarok;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3125
#, no-c-format
msgid "MTP Collection"
msgstr "Zbirka MTP"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3128
#, no-c-format
msgid "MTP collection plugin for &amarok;"
msgstr "Vtičnik za zbiranje MTP za &amarok;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Universal Mass Storage Collection"
msgstr "Univerzalna zbirka za masovno shranjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3136
#, no-c-format
msgid "UMS/USB collection plugin for &amarok;"
msgstr "Zbirni vtičnik UMS/USB za &amarok;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3141
#, no-c-format
msgid "UPnP Collection"
msgstr "Zbirka UPnP"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3144
#, no-c-format
msgid "UPnP collection plugin for &amarok;"
msgstr "Vtičnik zbiranja UPnP za &amarok;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Internet Services"
msgstr "Internetne storitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3152
#, no-c-format
msgid "&amarok; offers by default the following Internet services:"
msgstr "&amarok; privzeto ponuja naslednje internetne storitve:"

#. Tag: entry
