#, no-c-format
msgid "gpodder.net"
msgstr "gpodder.net"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Podcast service. See also <ulink url=\"http://www.gpodder.net\">gpodder.net</"
"ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Storitev podcast. Glejte tudi <ulink url=\"http://www.gpodder.net\">gpodder."
"net</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3184 index.docbook:3195 index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>No</para>"
msgstr "<para>Ne</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Listen to free music published under Creative Common licenses. See also "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.jamendo.com/en/about\">Jamendo.com</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Poslušajte brezplačno glasbo, objavljeno pod licencami Creative Common. Glej "
"tudi <ulink url=\"http://www.jamendo.com/en/about\">Jamendo.com</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A popular internet radio service, streaming only for subscribers. See also "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.last.fm/about\">Last.fm</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Priljubljena internetna radijska storitev, pretakanje samo za naročnike. "
"Glej tudi <ulink url=\"http://www.last.fm/about\">Last.fm</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, personal information to <link linkend=\"scrobble\">scrobble</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "Da, osebni podatki za <link linkend=\"scrobble\">scrobble</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Magnatune Store"
msgstr "Trgovina Magnatune"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Preview and buy music from a non-evil record label. See also <ulink url="
"\"http://magnatune.com/info/whynotevil\">Magnatunes.com</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Predoglejte si in kupite glasbo pri založbi, ki ni zlobna. Glej tudi <ulink "
"url=\"http://magnatune.com/info/whynotevil\">Magnatunes.com</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only for downloads"
msgstr "Samo za prenose"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access the Amazon MP3 Store directly from Amarok"
msgstr "Do Amazon MP3 Store dostopajte neposredno iz Amaroka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3228 index.docbook:3239
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Yes</para>"
msgstr "<para>Da</para>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid "mp3tunes"
msgstr "mp3tunes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A personal mp3 locker. See also <ulink url=\"http://www.mp3tunes.com/cb/"
"about/\">mp3tunes.com</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Osebna omarica za mp3. Glej tudi <ulink url=\"http://www.mp3tunes.com/cb/"
"about/\">mp3tunes.com</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse and subscribe to a huge choice of podcasts"
msgstr "Prebrskajte in se naročite na ogromno izbiro podcastov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other service are available through scripts."
msgstr "Druge storitve so na voljo prek skriptov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local Collection Backends"
msgstr "Zaledja lokalne zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; offers you access to the following Local Collection Backends, if "
"they are available:"
msgstr ""
"&amarok; vam ponuja dostop do naslednjih ozadij lokalne zbirke, če so na "
"voljo:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Devices"
msgstr "Naprave"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local Files &amp; USB Mass Storage Backend"
msgstr "Lokalne datoteke &amp; Zaledje za masovno shranjevanje USB"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local Collection folders on local and pluggable disks"
msgstr "Lokalne zbirke map na lokalnih in priključnih diskih"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3282
#, no-c-format
msgid "NFS Share Backend"
msgstr "NFS Share End"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local Collection folders on remote NFS shares (Network File System)"
msgstr ""
"Lokalne zbirke map v oddaljenih skupnih rabah NFS (omrežni datotečni sistem)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3290
#, no-c-format
msgid "SMB (Windows) Share Backend"
msgstr "SMB (Windows) Share Backend"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local Collection folders on remote Samba (Windows) shares"
msgstr "Lokalne zbirke map v oddaljenih skupnih rabah Samba (Windows)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3300
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ampache configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija Ampache"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have access to a remote <guilabel>Ampache</guilabel> music server, "
"click <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> and enter the "
"necessary information. You can configure access to more than one "
"<guilabel>Ampache</guilabel> server. For more information see the <link "
"linkend=\"ampache\">Ampache</link> section in what follows."
msgstr ""
"Če imate dostop do oddaljenega glasbenega strežnika <guilabel>Ampache</"
"guilabel>, kliknite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject > "
"in vnesite potrebne podatke. Konfigurirate lahko dostop do več kot enega "
"strežnika <guilabel>Ampache</guilabel>. Za več informacij glejte razdelek "
"<link linkend=\"ampache\">Ampache</link> v nadaljevanju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3304
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last.fm configuration"
msgstr "Last.fm konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While streaming is free with Last.fm's own online player for residents of "
"the US, the UK and Germany, it only works in &amarok; for paid subscribers. "
"Scrobbling is free, however, provided you enter your Last.fm username and "
"password by clicking <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>. "
"&amarok; allows you to store the password in the secure <guilabel>KDE "
"Wallet</guilabel>. If you decline the use of <guilabel>Kwallet</guilabel>, "
"your password will be stored in clear text instead."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je pretakanje brezplačno z lastnim spletnim predvajalnikom Last.fm za "
"prebivalce ZDA, Združenega kraljestva in Nemčije, deluje samo v &amarok; za "
"plačljive naročnike. Drsenje je brezplačno, če vnesete svoje uporabniško ime "
"in geslo za Last.fm s klikom na <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> . &amarok; omogoča shranjevanje gesla v varno "
"<guilabel>KDE Wallet</guilabel>. Če zavrnete uporabo <guilabel>Kwallet</"
"guilabel>, bo vaše geslo namesto tega shranjeno v čistem besedilu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Magnatune Store configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija Magnatune Store"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Listen to the music offered by Magnatune for free and buy it directly "
"through &amarok;. Click <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"to add your membership credentials if you are a member and/or add your email "
"address to re-download music you previously have downloaded from Magnatune."
msgstr ""
"Brezplačno poslušajte glasbo, ki jo ponuja Magnatune, in jo kupite "
"neposredno prek &amarok;. Kliknite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>, da dodate poverilnice za članstvo, če ste član, in/ali "
"dodate svoj e-poštni naslov za ponoven prenos glasbe, ki ste jo prej "
"prenesli iz Magnatune."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To download, you then go to the <emphasis>Media Sources</emphasis> pane, "
"select the Internet section and click on the Magnatune Store. It will then "
"download the catalog where you can search and select the music you want to "
"buy."
msgstr ""
"Za prenos nato pojdite v podokno <emphasis>Medijski viri</emphasis>, "
"izberite razdelek Internet in kliknite Magnatune Store. Nato bo prenesel "
"katalog, kjer lahko iščete in izberete glasbo, ki jo želite kupiti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3314
#, no-c-format
msgid "MP3 Store configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija MP3 Store"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access the Amazon MP3 Store directly from &amarok;."
msgstr "Do Amazon MP3 Store dostopajte neposredno iz &amarok;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Amazon MP3 Store needs to know what country you are located in because "
"it offers different items depending on your location. The following "
"countries are allowed:"
msgstr ""
"Trgovina Amazon MP3 mora vedeti, v kateri državi se nahajate, ker ponuja "
"različne predmete glede na vašo lokacijo. Dovoljene so naslednje države:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3320
#, no-c-format
msgid "France"
msgstr "Francija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Austria, Germany, Switzerland"
msgstr "Avstrija, Nemčija, Švica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Japan"
msgstr "Japonska"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3323
#, no-c-format
msgid "United Kingdom"
msgstr "Združeno kraljestvo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3324
#, no-c-format
msgid "United States (default)"
msgstr "Združene države (privzeto)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"NOTE: Changing the country invalidates your shopping cart. If your country "
"is not in the list, you cannot use the Amazon MP3 Store because it is not "
"supported by Amazon."
msgstr ""
"OPOMBA: Če spremenite državo, vaš nakupovalni voziček postane neveljaven. Če "
"vaše države ni na seznamu, ne morete uporabljati Amazon MP3 Store, ker je "
"Amazon ne podpira."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3329
#, no-c-format
msgid "mp3tunes configuration"
msgstr "konfiguracija mp3tunes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a personal mp3tunes locker, click <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> and enter your username and password. You "
"will then be able to access your online locker."
msgstr ""
"Če imate osebno omarico za mp3tunes, kliknite <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> ter vnesite svoje uporabniško ime in "
"geslo. Nato boste lahko dostopali do svoje spletne omarice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripts"
msgstr "Skripte"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3343
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scripts configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo skriptov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3346
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Scripts configuration dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo skriptov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Script Configuration in &amarok; covers <guilabel>Generic</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Lyrics</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Scriptable Service</guilabel> "
"scripts. Scripts are added in the <guilabel>Manage Scripts</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija skripta v &amarok; zajema skripte <guilabel>Generic</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Lyrics</guilabel> in <guilabel>Scriptable Service</"
"guilabel>. Skripti so dodani v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Upravljanje "
"skriptov</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic scripts"
msgstr "Generični skripti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generic scripts add functionality to &amarok;. The <emphasis>Amarok Script "
"Console</emphasis> is available by default; other scripts which add CD "
"burning, cover image storage, games, and many other choices are available. "
"If installed, these scripts will show up in the <emphasis>Tools</emphasis> "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"Generični skripti dodajo funkcionalnost v &amarok;. <emphasis>Amarok Script "
"Console</emphasis> je privzeto na voljo; na voljo so drugi skripti, ki "
"dodajo zapisovanje CD-jev, shranjevanje slik pokrovov, igre in številne "
"druge možnosti. Če so nameščeni, bodo ti skripti prikazani v meniju "
"<emphasis>Orodja</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lyrics scripts"
msgstr "Skripte za besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A variety of lyrics scripts are available; <emphasis>Ultimate Lyrics</"
"emphasis> is provided by default. Your chosen lyrics scripts will provide "
"the lyrics shown in the <emphasis>Lyrics applet</emphasis> in the "
"<emphasis>Context</emphasis> pane."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so različni scenariji besedil; <emphasis>Ultimate Lyrics</emphasis> "
"je privzeto na voljo. Vaši izbrani skripti besedil bodo zagotovili besedila, "
"prikazana v <emphasis>apletu besedila</emphasis> v podoknu "
"<emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scriptable Services scripts"
msgstr "Skripte storitev Scriptable Services"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scriptable services, if enabled, will show up in the <emphasis>Internet "
"Services</emphasis> in the <emphasis>Collections</emphasis> pane. Many "
"collections of streams are available, in many languages, and from many "
"sources."
msgstr ""
"Storitve, ki jih je mogoče skriptirati, bodo, če so omogočene, prikazane v "
"<emphasis>Internetnih storitvah</emphasis> v podoknu <emphasis>Zbirke</"
"emphasis>. Na voljo je veliko zbirk tokov v številnih jezikih in iz "
"številnih virov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manage Scripts"
msgstr "Upravljanje skriptov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3366
#, no-c-format
msgid "At bottom of the configuration dialog are two options:"
msgstr "Na dnu konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna sta dve možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically update built-in scripts"
msgstr "Samodejno posodobi vgrajene skripte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically download and install updates for the built-in scripts from the "
"&amarok; website if available. Enable if you usually have a working Internet "
"connections, and want your scripts automatically updated. This will not "
"update user-supplied scripts from KDE-apps.org."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno prenesite in namestite posodobitve za vgrajene skripte iz datoteke "
"&amarok; spletno mesto, če je na voljo. Omogočite, če imate običajno "
"delujoče internetne povezave in želite, da se vaši skripti samodejno "
"posodabljajo. To ne bo posodobilo uporabniško posredovanih skriptov s KDE-"
"apps.org."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3374
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Manage Scripts</guilabel> button"
msgstr "Gumb <guilabel>Upravljanje skriptov</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Browse, install and uninstall user-supplied scripts; also search, sort and "
"rate the scripts in the <emphasis>Amarok Add-on Installer</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Prebrskajte, namestite in odstranite skripte, ki jih zagotovi uporabnik; "
"tudi poiščite, razvrstite in ocenite skripte v <emphasis>Amarokovem "
"namestitvenem programu</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add-on Installer"
msgstr "Namestitveni program dodatkov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Amarok Script Manager</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Amarok Script Manager</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3390
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Amarok Script Manager</para>"
msgstr "<para>Amarok Script Manager</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <emphasis>Add-on Installer</emphasis>, one can install the latest "
"user-contributed &amarok; scripts. There are also options to search, sort "
"and rate the scripts."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo <emphasis>Namestitvenega programa za dodatke</emphasis> lahko "
"namestite najnovejši &amarok; skripte. Obstajajo tudi možnosti za iskanje, "
"razvrščanje in ocenjevanje skriptov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Install Scripts</guilabel> and <guilabel>Uninstall</guilabel> "
"buttons can be used to manage scripts. One can install script packages of "
"type amarokscript.tar, amarokscript.tar.bz2, amarokscript.tar.gz"
msgstr ""
"Gumba <guilabel>Namesti skripte</guilabel> in <guilabel>Odstrani</guilabel> "
"lahko uporabite za upravljanje skriptov. Namestite lahko pakete skriptov "
"tipa amarokscript.tar, amarokscript.tar.bz2, amarokscript.tar.gz"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Information"
msgstr "Informacije o skriptu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Learn more about a script using the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button."
msgstr ""
"Izvedite več o skriptu z uporabo gumba <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A script can also be executed directly in the Amarok Script Console. This is "
"activated by selecting the Script Console and confirm the selection by "
"hitting either the <guilabel>OK</guilabel> or the <guilabel>Apply</guilabel> "
"button. To deactivate the Script Console deselect it and confirm again."
msgstr ""
"Skript je mogoče izvesti tudi neposredno v skriptni konzoli Amarok. To "
"aktivirate tako, da izberete skriptno konzolo in potrdite izbiro s pritiskom "
"na gumb <guilabel>V redu</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Uporabi</guilabel>. Če "
"želite deaktivirati skriptno konzolo, jo počistite in znova potrdite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Layouts"
msgstr "Spreminjanje postavitev"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the Amarok Window Layout"
msgstr "Spreminjanje postavitve okna Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The visibility of each of the three &amarok; panes is indicated in the "
"<guilabel>View</guilabel> menu (part of the top-level menu). If you unlock "
"the layout, each of the three panes will show two clickable boxes. These two "
"boxes allow you to rearrange or customize the layout of your &amarok; "
"window. Clicking the <guilabel>X</guilabel> closes that particular pane. "
"Having been closed, a pane can be activated again by checking the "
"appropriate box in the <guilabel>View menu</guilabel>. Clicking "
"<guilabel>Reset Layout</guilabel> will of course reset the layout back to "
"the default look."
msgstr ""
"Vidnost vsakega od treh &amarok; podokna je označeno v meniju "
"<guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> (del menija na najvišji ravni). Če odklenete "
"postavitev, bosta v vsakem od treh podoknov prikazani dve polji, ki ju je "
"mogoče klikniti. Ti dve polji vam omogočata, da preuredite ali prilagodite "
"postavitev vašega &amarok; okno. S klikom na <guilabel>X</guilabel> se to "
"posebno podokno zapre. Ko je bilo podokno zaprto, ga lahko znova aktivirate "
"tako, da označite ustrezno polje v <guilabel>meniju Pogled</guilabel>. Če "
"kliknete <guilabel>Ponastavi postavitev</guilabel>, boste seveda ponastavili "
"postavitev nazaj na privzeti videz."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3438
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undocking Amarok panes"
msgstr "Odklop podokna Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the hollow symbol on the left of the cross causes that panel to be "
"undocked, so it will appear as a separate window on your desktop. Repeating "
"this action on the undocked pane will dock it again inside your &amarok; "
"window. You can drag the panes inside your &amarok; window to reorder them. "
"You may stack the panes, or even put one or two of them covering the others, "
"selectable by tabs."
msgstr ""
"Klik na prazen simbol na levi strani križa povzroči, da se ta plošča "
"odklopi, tako da bo prikazana kot ločeno okno na namizju. Ponavljanje tega "
"dejanja na nezasidranem podoknu bo znova zasidrano znotraj vašega &amarok; "
"okno. Podokna lahko povlečete v svoj &amarok; okno, da jih preuredite. "
"Podokna lahko zložite na kup ali celo postavite eno ali dve od njih, ki "
"prekrivata druge, izbirate jih lahko po zavihkih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3455
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lock and save Amarok window layout"
msgstr "Zakleni in shrani postavitev okna Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with the layout inside your &amarok; window, you can "
"lock this layout by clicking the appropriate item in the <guilabel>View</"
"guilabel> menu. Be aware that if you want to be sure your layout is "
"preserved when you shut down your session with &amarok; still open, quit "
"&amarok; first by either choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Amarok</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or by typing "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če ste zadovoljni s postavitvijo znotraj vašega &amarok; okno, lahko to "
"postavitev zaklenete s klikom na ustrezen element v meniju <guilabel>Pogled</"
"guilabel>. Zavedajte se, da če želite biti prepričani, da je vaša postavitev "
"ohranjena, ko prekinete sejo z &amarok; še odprto, zapri &amarok; najprej "
"bodisi z izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Amarok</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali z vnosom <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></"
"keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the Toolbar"
msgstr "Spreminjanje orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also choose between two layouts of the Toolbar by clicking the "
"appropriate item in the <guilabel>View</guilabel> menu:"
msgstr ""
"Izbirate lahko tudi med dvema postavitvama orodne vrstice, tako da kliknete "
"ustrezen element v meniju <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3485
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Main Toolbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavna orodna vrstica</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3506
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Slim Toolbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Orodna vrstica Slim</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3512
#, no-c-format
msgid "More about the Toolbar <link linkend=\"toolbar\">here</link>."
msgstr "Več o orodni vrstici <link linkend=\"toolbar\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the Playlist layout"
msgstr "Spreminjanje postavitve seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To access the <guilabel>Playlist Layout Editor</guilabel>, go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlist</guimenu><guisubmenu>Playlist Layouts</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Configure Playlist Layouts...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> and you will see the above editor window. On the left you can "
"see the preset layouts; clicking on those allows you to see how the "
"configuration is done on the right. Clicking on the <guilabel>Preview</"
"guilabel> button allows you to see the applied layout in the "
"<guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do <guilabel>urejevalnika postavitve seznama predvajanja</"
"guilabel> pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Postavitve seznama predvajanja</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj postavitve seznama predvajanja ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in videli boste zgornje okno urejevalnika. Na levi "
"strani lahko vidite prednastavljene postavitve; s klikom nanje lahko vidite, "
"kako je konfiguracija izvedena na desni. S klikom na gumb "
"<guilabel>Predogled</guilabel> si lahko ogledate uporabljeno postavitev v "
"podoknu <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3531
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifying a default layout"
msgstr "Spreminjanje privzete postavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To modify one of the default layouts, first make a new copy of it: simply "
"click on <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-"
"copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> and save it "
"under a new name. To generate a new layout, click on"
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti eno od privzetih postavitev, najprej naredite njeno "
"novo kopijo: preprosto kliknite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> in ga shranite pod novim imenom. Če želite ustvariti novo "
"postavitev, kliknite na"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A layout consists of 3 elements: the Album <emphasis>Head</emphasis>, the "
"Album <emphasis>Body</emphasis> (with a special album body for Various "
"Artist tracks) and the <emphasis>Single</emphasis> Tracks configuration, "
"selectable in the tabs in the middle of the editor. To add an item, simply "
"drag it from the selector on top and drop it in the layout tab elected "
"below. To show the album cover, just check the <guilabel>Cover</guilabel> "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev je sestavljena iz treh elementov: <emphasis>glave</emphasis> "
"albuma, <emphasis>tela</emphasis> albuma (s posebnim telesom albuma za "
"skladbe različnih izvajalcev) in <emphasis>posamezne</emphasis> skladbe "
"konfiguracijo, ki jo lahko izberete v zavihkih na sredini urejevalnika. Če "
"želite dodati element, ga preprosto povlecite iz izbirnika na vrhu in ga "
"spustite na zavihek postavitve, izbran spodaj. Če želite prikazati "
"naslovnico albuma, označite polje <guilabel>Oslovnica</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3536
#, no-c-format
msgid "In addition, you can also add:"
msgstr "Poleg tega lahko dodate tudi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3550
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show inline playback controls"
msgstr "Pokaži vgrajene kontrolnike za predvajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3553
#, no-c-format
msgid "playback controls will appear below the line of the playing track."
msgstr "kontrolniki za predvajanje bodo prikazani pod črto predvajane skladbe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show tooltips"
msgstr "Pokaži nasvete orodij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tooltips showing ID3 tag information will be shown on hovering over a track."
msgstr ""
"Namigi orodij, ki prikazujejo informacije o oznaki ID3, bodo prikazani, ko "
"miškin kazalec premaknete nad skladbo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3567
#, no-c-format
msgid "Item layout configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija postavitve predmeta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each of the added items can then have its own layout configured: hovering "
"over the item shows a wrench, clicking on this wrench will let you access a "
"configuration dialog for that item. The example below shows you the "
"configuration dialog for the <guilabel>Album</guilabel> item:"
msgstr ""
"Vsakemu od dodanih elementov je nato mogoče konfigurirati lastno postavitev: "
"če miškin kazalec premaknete nad element, se prikaže ključ, s klikom na ta "
"ključ boste imeli dostop do konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna za ta "
"element. Spodnji primer prikazuje konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno za element "
"<guilabel>Album</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then decide of the total width of the item (100% is the total width "
"of the line, so if you use a custom width and have more than one item on a "
"line, you need to reduce that width per item), its alignment, the font "
"weight and whether the tag should be shown with a prefix or suffix."
msgstr ""
"Nato se lahko odločite za skupno širino elementa (100 % je skupna širina "
"vrstice, tako da če uporabljate širino po meri in imate več kot en element v "
"vrstici, morate to širino zmanjšati na element), poravnavo, težo pisave in "
"ali naj bo oznaka prikazana s predpono ali pripono."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: single line layout"
msgstr "Primer: enovrstična postavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Example</emphasis>: to generate a single line layout without "
"grouping you only add items in the <guilabel>Single</guilabel> Track element."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Primer</emphasis>: če želite ustvariti postavitev ene same vrstice "
"brez združevanja v skupine, dodate samo elemente v elementu "
"<guilabel>Single</guilabel> Track."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist layout storage"
msgstr "Shranjevanje postavitve seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The playlist layouts will be stored in xml format in <filename>$HOME/.kde/"
"share/apps/amarok/playlist_layouts</filename> (might be <filename>$HOME/."
"kde4/share/apps/amarok/playlist-layouts</filename> for some distributions)."
msgstr ""
"Postavitve seznamov predvajanja bodo shranjene v formatu xml v <filename>"
"$HOME/.kde/share/apps/amarok/playlist_layouts</filename> (lahko <filename>"
"$HOME/.kde4/share/apps/amarok/playlist- postavitve</filename> za nekatere "
"distribucije)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3598
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organization"
msgstr "Organizacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Organizing your music makes it easier to find what you want. &amarok; offers "
"you several tools to assist."
msgstr ""
"Z organiziranjem glasbe boste lažje našli tisto, kar želite. &amarok; ponuja "
"več orodij za pomoč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3601
#, no-c-format
msgid "First, organize your collection of music, both local and remote:"
msgstr "Najprej organizirajte svojo zbirko glasbe, tako lokalno kot oddaljeno:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3604
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"collection\">Collection</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"collection\">Zbirka</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3605 index.docbook:3631
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"collection-scanning\">Collection Scanning</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"collection-scanning\">Skeniranje zbirke</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
