#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3612 index.docbook:3638 index.docbook:4173
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"samba\">Samba</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"samba\">Samba</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3613 index.docbook:3639 index.docbook:4174
#, no-c-format
msgid "UPnP"
msgstr "UPnP"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3616 index.docbook:3642
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"external-database\">External Database</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"external-database\">Zunanja zbirka podatkov</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3617 index.docbook:3643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"working-with-media-devices\">Working with Media Devices</"
"link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"working-with-media-devices\">Delo z medijskimi napravami</"
"link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Cover Manager</guilabel> organizes your album covers, the "
"<emphasis>Tag Editor</emphasis> helps &amarok; categorize your tracks, and "
"transcoding allows you to transfer tracks to your devices in encoding they "
"can play."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Upravljalnik naslovnic</guilabel> organizira vaše naslovnice "
"albumov, <emphasis>Urejevalnik oznak</emphasis> pomaga &amarok; "
"ukategorizirajte svoje skladbe, transkodiranje pa vam omogoča prenos skladb "
"v vaše naprave v kodiranju, ki ga lahko predvajajo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3623
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"cover-manager\">Cover Manager</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"cover-manager\">Upravljalnik naslovnic</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3624
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"tag-editor\">Tag Editor</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"tag-editor\">Urejevalnik oznak</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3625
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"transcoding\">Transcoding</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"transcoding\">Prekodiranje</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3628
#, no-c-format
msgid "&amarok; organizes your music in the <emphasis>Collection</emphasis>."
msgstr "&amarok; organizira vašo glasbo v <emphasis>Zbirki</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"statistics-synchronization\">Statistics Synchronization "
"Between Collections and with Last.fm</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"statistics-synchronization\">Sinhronizacija statistike med "
"zbirkami in z Last.fm</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection Scanning"
msgstr "Skeniranje zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every time &amarok; is displaying a collection the information about tracks "
"and albums needs to come from a source."
msgstr ""
"Vsakič, ko &amarok; prikazuje zbirko, informacije o skladbah in albumih "
"morajo priti iz vira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source can be an portable device, an Internet service or a database."
msgstr ""
"Vir je lahko prenosna naprava, internetna storitev ali zbirka podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For tracks that are in <guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel> folders "
"&amarok; is using a database to have fast access to the required meta-"
"information."
msgstr ""
"Za skladbe, ki so v mapah <guilabel>Lokalna zbirka</guilabel> &amarok; "
"uporablja bazo podatkov za hiter dostop do zahtevanih metainformacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At first this information needs to be loaded into the database which is "
"usually done by scanning the <guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel> "
"directories for audio files."
msgstr ""
"Najprej je treba te informacije naložiti v bazo podatkov, kar se običajno "
"naredi s pregledovanjem imenikov <guilabel>Lokalna zbirka</guilabel> za "
"zvočne datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3654
#, no-c-format
msgid "This process is called collection scanning."
msgstr "Ta postopek se imenuje skeniranje zbirke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is useful to understand the scanning process in order to work better with "
"&amarok;."
msgstr "Za boljše delo z &amarok;om je koristno razumeti postopek skeniranja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3658
#, no-c-format
msgid "Incremental Scan / Update Collection"
msgstr "Postopno skeniranje/zbirka posodobitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The so-called incremental scan will check the collection directories for "
"updates."
msgstr ""
"Tako imenovano inkrementalno skeniranje bo preverilo, ali so v imenikih "
"zbirk posodobitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is done every minute if <guilabel>Watch folders for changes</guilabel> "
"is enabled (on by default) but can also be triggered manually by selecting "
"<guilabel>Update Collection</guilabel> from the menu."
msgstr ""
"To se izvede vsako minuto, če je omogočeno <guilabel>Ogled map za spremembe</"
"guilabel> (privzeto vklopljeno), lahko pa se sproži tudi ročno, tako da v "
"meniju izberete <guilabel>Posodobi zbirko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The incremental scan will just check the modification date of every folder "
"in the collection against the last known modification time."
msgstr ""
"Postopno skeniranje bo samo preverilo datum spremembe vsake mape v zbirki "
"glede na zadnji znani čas spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3665
#, no-c-format
msgid "This has a couple of implications:"
msgstr "To ima nekaj posledic:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can trigger a rescan of one directory by modifying its time (such as "
"using <varname>touch /path/to/directory</varname> in the console)."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno skeniranje enega imenika lahko sprožite tako, da spremenite njegov "
"čas (na primer z uporabo <varname>dotaknite se /path/to/directory</varname> "
"v konzoli)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If files inside a directory are changed the scanner will not notice, because "
"changing a file updates its modification time but not the time of the parent "
"folder. On the other hand most programs that modify the files save them "
"atomically by using a temporary file which is then renamed. Such procedure "
"does update directory modification time and thus triggers directory rescan."
msgstr ""
"Če so datoteke znotraj imenika spremenjene, optični bralnik ne bo opazil, "
"ker sprememba datoteke posodobi njen čas spremembe, ne pa tudi časa "
"nadrejene mape. Po drugi strani večina programov, ki spreminjajo datoteke, "
"jih shrani atomsko z uporabo začasne datoteke, ki se nato preimenuje. Takšen "
"postopek posodobi čas spreminjanja imenika in tako sproži ponovno skeniranje "
"imenika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the collection folders are on a very slow partition the process of "
"checking all the modification times can take some time. Usually this "
"information is cached by the operating system but with large collections "
"that might not be possible. In such a case the scanner might appear to scan "
"continuously. With collections above thousands of directories or when "
"collections are stored on a network drive or an NTFS partition it is "
"recommended to switch off the <guilabel>Watch folders for change</guilabel> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Če so zbirne mape na zelo počasni particiji, lahko postopek preverjanja vseh "
"časov spreminjanja traja nekaj časa. Običajno te informacije predpomni "
"operacijski sistem, vendar z velikimi zbirkami, kar morda ni mogoče. V tem "
"primeru se lahko zdi, da optični bralnik neprekinjeno skenira. Pri zbirkah "
"nad tisoč imenikov ali ko so zbirke shranjene na omrežnem pogonu ali "
"particiji NTFS, priporočamo, da izklopite možnost <guilabel>Ogled map za "
"spremembe</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have problems with deleted tracks still appearing in the collection, "
"or you want to update album covers (which are not updated by a mere "
"<guilabel>Update collection</guilabel>) then you can use the <guilabel>Full "
"rescan</guilabel> option in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če imate težave z izbrisanimi skladbami, ki se še vedno pojavljajo v zbirki, "
"ali želite posodobiti naslovnice albumov (ki se ne posodobijo zgolj z "
"<guilabel>Posodobi zbirko</guilabel>), potem lahko uporabite "
"<guilabel>Popolno ponovno skeniranje</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Full rescan</guilabel> will not care about modification dates. It "
"will not delete statistics of existing files; it will, however, delete "
"statistics of tracks that disappeared from the currently mounted collection "
"folders. Because of that it is adviseable to perform the <guilabel>Full "
"rescan</guilabel> only with all <guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel> "
"folders mounted if you move the tracks between mounts. <guilabel>Full "
"rescan</guilabel> also updates play count if the one stored in file tags is "
"greater, rating if the song is unrated and file tags mention rating and "
"score (under the same circumstances)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Popolno ponovno skeniranje</guilabel> ne bo upoštevalo datumov "
"sprememb. Ne bo izbrisal statistike obstoječih datotek; vendar bo izbrisal "
"statistiko skladb, ki so izginile iz trenutno nameščenih map zbirk. Zaradi "
"tega je priporočljivo, da izvedete <guilabel>Popolno ponovno skeniranje</"
"guilabel> samo z vsemi nameščenimi mapami <guilabel>Lokalna zbirka</"
"guilabel>, če premikate skladbe med namestitvami. <guilabel>Popolno ponovno "
"skeniranje</guilabel> prav tako posodobi število predvajanj, če je tisto, "
"shranjeno v oznakah datotek, večje, oceno, če pesem ni ocenjena, in oznake "
"datotek omenjajo oceno in rezultat (v enakih okoliščinah)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3677
#, no-c-format
msgid "Progress bar / scanning time"
msgstr "Vrstica napredka/čas skeniranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3678
#, no-c-format
msgid "The progress bar will show the progress of the scanning."
msgstr "Vrstica napredka bo prikazovala potek skeniranja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Up to 50% the scanner will scan the file system and just buffer the result."
msgstr ""
"Do 50 % bo optični bralnik pregledal datotečni sistem in samo shranil "
"rezultat v medpomnilnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Times above 50% indicate that the scanner is committing the results to the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Časi nad 50 % pomenijo, da optični bralnik posreduje rezultate v bazo "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually the second step is much faster than the first so don't be surprised "
"if the progress bar seems to jump."
msgstr ""
"Običajno je drugi korak veliko hitrejši od prvega, zato ne bodite "
"presenečeni, če se zdi, da vrstica napredka poskoči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Up to 50% aborting the scan is possible. After 50%, the committing of the "
"files cannot be stopped."
msgstr ""
"Možna je do 50-odstotna prekinitev skeniranja. Po 50 % potrditve datotek ni "
"mogoče ustaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3688
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scanning time depends on your disk speed and other factors."
msgstr "Čas skeniranja je odvisen od hitrosti diska in drugih dejavnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually the first scan is a lot slower than subsequent scans where the files "
"are cached by the operating system."
msgstr ""
"Običajno je prvo skeniranje veliko počasnejše od naslednjih skeniranj, pri "
"katerih datoteke predpomni operacijski sistem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A scan of 10000 files should take around three minutes on a modern computer. "
"50000 files should be around 13 minutes. Of course with an SSD (solid state "
"drive) this will be much faster."
msgstr ""
"Skeniranje 10.000 datotek bi moralo na sodobnem računalniku trajati "
"približno tri minute. 50000 datotek bi moralo biti približno 13 minut. "
"Seveda bo s SSD (SSD) to veliko hitreje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3695
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup of collection"
msgstr "Varnostna kopija zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the default settings &amarok; is storing all the collection information "
"in a directory called <filename>~.kde/share/apps/amarok/mysqle/</filename> . "
"It can be a good idea to make a backup of this directory from time to time, "
"especially when you didn't enable the writing back of statistics information."
msgstr ""
"S privzetimi nastavitvami &amarok; shranjuje vse informacije o zbirki v "
"imeniku <filename>~.kde/share/apps/amarok/mysqle/</filename> . Priporočljivo "
"je, da občasno naredite varnostno kopijo tega imenika, zlasti če niste "
"omogočili zapisovanja statističnih podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3699
#, no-c-format
msgid "About unique ids"
msgstr "O edinstvenih ID-jih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; is tracking files by an id that is either stored in the audio track "
"or computed using file metadata, tag metadata and first few kilobytes of the "
"file."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; sledi datotekam po ID-ju, ki je shranjen v zvočnem posnetku ali "
"izračunan z uporabo metapodatkov datoteke, metapodatkov oznak in prvih nekaj "
"kilobajtov datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This id helps &amarok; to identify tracks that are moved to other locations "
"so that statistics information (rating, score, playcount, first &amp; last "
"played) are not lost."
msgstr ""
"Ta ID pomaga &amarok;u za prepoznavanje skladb, ki so premaknjene na druge "
"lokacije, tako da se statistični podatki (ocena, rezultat, število "
"predvajanj, prva in zadnja predvajana) ne izgubijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currently &amarok; will not import tracks with duplicate unique ids."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno &amarok; ne bo uvozil skladb s podvojenimi edinstvenimi ID-ji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This leads to the surprising behavior that copied tracks still appear only "
"once in &amarok;."
msgstr ""
"To vodi do presenetljivega vedenja, da se kopirane skladbe še vedno "
"prikažejo samo enkrat v &amarok;u."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some circumstances even different tracks can end up with the same unique "
"id. Such a problem can be seen by the debug output (start &amarok; with the "
"--debug option in a console) while scanning."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih okoliščinah imajo lahko celo različne skladbe isti edinstveni "
"ID. Takšno težavo lahko opazite v izhodu za odpravljanje napak (zaženite "
"&amarok; z možnostjo --debug v konzoli) med skeniranjem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3711
#, no-c-format
msgid "About Albums"
msgstr "O albumih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scanner can only read single tracks but &amarok; will display those "
"sorted by album and compilation (an album without one specific artist). "
"&amarok; can't rely on the directory in which the files are located, since "
"directory organizational schemes vary so widely."
msgstr ""
"Skener lahko bere samo posamezne skladbe, vendar &amarok; prikaže tiste, "
"razvrščene po albumu in kompilaciji (album brez enega določenega izvajalca). "
"&amarok; se ne more zanesti na imenik, v katerem so datoteke, saj se "
"organizacijske sheme imenikov zelo razlikujejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3714
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scanner is therefore doing the following:"
msgstr "Optični bralnik torej počne naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tracks without an album artist or an artist (or a composer in case of a "
"classical track) are placed in a compilation."
msgstr ""
"Skladbe brez izvajalca albuma ali izvajalca (ali skladatelja v primeru "
"klasične skladbe) so uvrščene v kompilacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tracks that have the compilation flag set or an album artist other than "
"<quote>various artists</quote> will be placed in an album."
msgstr ""
"Skladbe, ki imajo nastavljeno zastavico kompilacije ali izvajalca albuma, ki "
"ni <quote>različni izvajalci</quote>, bodo uvrščene v album."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tracks that have the compilation flag set to 0 are placed in a compilation."
msgstr ""
"Skladbe, ki imajo zastavico kompilacije nastavljeno na 0, so uvrščene v "
"kompilacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Albums called <quote>Best Of</quote>, <quote>Anthology</quote>, <quote>Hit "
"collection</quote>, <quote>Greatest Hits</quote>, <quote>All Time Greatest "
"Hits</quote> and <quote>Live</quote> are always regarded as an album."
msgstr ""
"Albumi, imenovani <quote>Best Of</quote>, <quote>Antologija</quote>, "
"<quote>Zbirka uspešnic</quote>, <quote>Greatest Hits</quote>, <quote>All "
"Time Greatest Hits</quote> in <quote>V živo</quote> se vedno obravnavata kot "
"album."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If we end up having tracks with several different artists left over they are "
"placed inside a compilation, or else we make one album out of them."
msgstr ""
"Če nam na koncu ostanejo skladbe z več različnimi izvajalci, jih damo v "
"kompilacijo ali pa iz njih naredimo en album."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This process is quite complicated. However usually the outputs of the "
"scanner can help in figuring out why the tracks are sorted as they are."
msgstr ""
"Ta postopek je precej zapleten. Vendar pa lahko rezultati skenerja običajno "
"pomagajo ugotoviti, zakaj so skladbe razvrščene tako, kot so."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In such a case try executing (on a command line) "
"<userinput>amarokcollectionscanner -r <replaceable>~/your/music/directory</"
"replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"V takem primeru poskusite izvesti (v ukazni vrstici) "
"<userinput>amarokcollectionscanner -r <replaceable>~/your/music/directory</"
"replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Look for <quote>compilation</quote> tags and tracks with different "
"<quote>artist</quote> and <quote>albumartist</quote> tags."
msgstr ""
"Poiščite oznake <quote>kompilacije</quote> in skladbe z različnimi oznakami "
"<quote>izvajalec</quote> in <quote>izvajalec albuma</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can remove the <emphasis>compilation</emphasis> tag from mp3 files with "
"the following command: <userinput>id3v2 -r TCMP <replaceable>your filename "
"here</replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Oznako <emphasis>kompilacija</emphasis> lahko odstranite iz datotek mp3 z "
"naslednjim ukazom: <userinput>id3v2 -r TCMP <replaceable>vaše ime datoteke "
"tukaj</replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in Collection"
msgstr "Iskanje v zbirki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Search Collection</emphasis> lets you specify complex filters to "
"search for specific tracks in your collection. Use the edit box in the "
"<emphasis>Media Sources</emphasis> pane or click the <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-properties.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button right next to the edit "
"box. Alternatively you can simply press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> to activate the search bar."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Iskanje v zbirki</emphasis> vam omogoča, da določite kompleksne "
"filtre za iskanje določenih skladb v vaši zbirki. Uporabite polje za "
"urejanje v podoknu <emphasis>Medijski viri</emphasis> ali kliknite "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-"
"properties.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> tik "
"poleg polja za urejanje. Lahko pa preprosto pritisnete <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>, da aktivirate iskalno vrstico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3749 index.docbook:5220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Box"
msgstr "Polje za urejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you type in the input field, &amarok; will search for the text in all "
"available tags such as artist, album and title. Your view of the collection "
"will update automatically to display only the matches of the search."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete v polje za vnos, &amarok; bo iskal besedilo v vseh razpoložljivih "
"oznakah, kot so izvajalec, album in naslov. Vaš pogled zbirke se bo "
"samodejno posodobil in prikazal samo ujemanja iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing &Enter; after searching will populate your playlist with all of the "
"found search items and clear the search box. This is a great way to quickly "
"add hundreds or thousands of tracks to a playlist instantly!"
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom &Enter; po iskanju bo vaš seznam predvajanja zapolnil z vsemi "
"najdenimi iskalnimi elementi in počistil iskalno polje. To je odličen način "
"za hitro in takojšnje dodajanje več sto ali tisoč skladb na seznam "
"predvajanja!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To search in a specific tag, type <varname>tag:value</varname> into the "
"search bar. Operators like <quote>&gt;</quote> and <quote>&lt;</quote> can "
"be used to create more general conditions. Several conditions can be used "
"together by separating them by a space character. For time conditions, use "
"the following abbreviations: d=day, w=week, m=month, y=year."
msgstr ""
"Če želite iskati v določeni oznaki, v iskalno vrstico vnesite <varname>tag:"
"value</varname>. Operatorje, kot sta <quote>&gt;</quote> in <quote>&lt;</"
"quote>, lahko uporabite za ustvarjanje bolj splošnih pogojev. Več pogojev "
"lahko uporabite skupaj, tako da jih ločite s presledkom. Za časovne pogoje "
"uporabite naslednje okrajšave: d=dan, w=teden, m=mesec, y=leto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3758
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following tags can be searched:"
msgstr "Iščete lahko po naslednjih oznakah:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3761
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Album</para>"
msgstr "<para>Album</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3762
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Artist</para>"
msgstr "<para>Umetnik</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3763
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bitrate"
msgstr "Bitna hitrost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3764
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Composer</para>"
msgstr "<para>Skladatelj</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3765
#, no-c-format
msgid "AlbumArtist"
msgstr "AlbumArtist"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3766
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Genre</para>"
msgstr "<para>Zvrst</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playcount"
msgstr "Playcount"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3768
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Rating</para>"
msgstr "<para>Ocena</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sample Rate"
msgstr "Stopnja vzorčenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3770
#, no-c-format
msgid "Score"
msgstr "Rezultat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3771
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Title</para>"
msgstr "<para>Naslov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3772
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Track</para>"
msgstr "<para>Skladba</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Year</para>"
msgstr "<para>Leto</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3774
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>BPM</para>"
msgstr "<para>BPM</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3777
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional searchable fields"
msgstr "Dodatna polja za iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3778
#, no-c-format
msgid "Along with tags, the following can also be searched:"
msgstr "Poleg oznak je mogoče iskati tudi naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3781
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Comment</para>"
msgstr "<para>Komentar</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3782
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename"
msgstr "Ime datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3783
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disc number"
msgstr "Številka diska"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Length"
msgstr "Dolžina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3785
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filesize"
msgstr "Velikost datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3786
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format"
msgstr "Oblika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3787
#, no-c-format
msgid "Added (to Collection)"
msgstr "Dodano (v zbirko)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3788
#, no-c-format
msgid "First played"
msgstr "Prvo predvajano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3789
#, no-c-format
msgid "Label"
msgstr "Oznaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3790
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last modified"
msgstr "Nazadnje spremenjeno"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3793
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operators"
msgstr "Operaterji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3794
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numerical tags can use the following operators to create a condition:"
msgstr ""
"Številske oznake lahko za ustvarjanje pogoja uporabljajo naslednje "
"operatorje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3797
#, no-c-format
msgid "Equal: <quote>:</quote>"
msgstr "Enako: <quote>:</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Less than: <quote>&lt;</quote>"
msgstr "Manj kot: <quote>&lt;</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Larger than: <quote>&gt;</quote>"
msgstr "Večje od: <quote>&gt;</quote>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3802 index.docbook:5223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "Primeri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you search without specifying a tag, &amarok; will search in all "
"important text tags:"
msgstr ""
"Če iščete brez podajanja oznake, &amarok; bo iskal v vseh pomembnih "
"besedilnih oznakah:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3818
#, no-c-format
msgid "More complex patterns can be used to get better results:"
msgstr "Za boljše rezultate je mogoče uporabiti bolj zapletene vzorce:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Filter Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za urejanje filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you prefer to build your searches more programatically, drag down the "
"icons for the search terms you want, and drag to change search-term order. "
"You may search by: <guilabel>Simple text</guilabel>, <guilabel>Title</"
"guilabel>,"
msgstr ""
"Če želite iskanja oblikovati bolj programsko, povlecite navzdol ikone za "
"želene iskalne izraze in jih povlecite, da spremenite vrstni red iskalnih "
"izrazov. Iščete lahko po: <guilabel>Preprosto besedilo</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Naslov</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Artist name</guilabel>, <guilabel>Album Artist Name</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Album Name</guilabel>, <guilabel>Genre</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Composer</guilabel>, <guilabel>Comment</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Filename</guilabel>,"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime izvajalca</guilabel>, <guilabel>Ime izvajalca albuma</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Ime albuma</guilabel>, <guilabel>Zvrst</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel>, <guilabel>Komentar</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Ime datoteke</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Year</guilabel>, <guilabel>Track Number</guilabel>, <guilabel>Disc "
"Number</guilabel>, <guilabel>BPM</guilabel>,"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Leto</guilabel>, <guilabel>Številka skladbe</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Številka diska</guilabel>, <guilabel>BPM</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Length</guilabel>, <guilabel>Bit Rate</guilabel>, <guilabel>Sample "
"Rate</guilabel>, <guilabel>File Size</guilabel>,"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dolžina</guilabel>, <guilabel>Bitna hitrost</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Hitrost vzorčenja</guilabel>, <guilabel>Velikost datoteke</"
"guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Format</guilabel>, <guilabel>Added to Collection</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Score</guilabel>, <guilabel>Rating</guilabel>,"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Oblika</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dodano v zbirko</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Ocena</guilabel>, <guilabel>Ocena</guilabel>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>First Played</guilabel>, <guilabel>Playcount</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Label</guilabel>, <guilabel>Last Modified</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prvič predvajano</guilabel>, <guilabel>Število predvajanj</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Oznaka</guilabel>, <guilabel>Nazadnje spremenjeno</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also add <guilabel>OR</guilabel> and <guilabel>AND</guilabel> here."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko dodate tudi <guilabel>ALI</guilabel> in <guilabel>IN</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a term and check <guilabel>Invert condition</guilabel> to exclude "
"items matching this term from the results. Choose <guilabel>AND</guilabel> "
"or <guilabel>OR</guilabel> for all terms in this search. If you choose "
"<guilabel>AND</guilabel>, all search-terms must be present."
msgstr ""
"Izberite izraz in označite <guilabel>Obrni pogoj</guilabel>, da iz "
"rezultatov izključite elemente, ki se ujemajo s tem izrazom. Izberite "
"<guilabel>IN</guilabel> ali <guilabel>ALI</guilabel> za vse izraze v tem "
"iskanju. Če izberete <guilabel>IN</guilabel>, morajo biti prisotni vsi "
"iskalni izrazi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3852
#, no-c-format
msgid "If <guilabel>OR</guilabel>, any matches will show up."
msgstr "Če <guilabel>ALI</guilabel>, bodo prikazana vsa ujemanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3854
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course, clicking <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-edit-clear-locationbar-rtl.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> removes your selections."
msgstr ""
"Seveda s klikom na <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-edit-clear-locationbar-rtl.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> odstranite svoje izbire."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3870
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organize Collection"
msgstr "Organizirajte zbiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While organizing your collection in &amarok; is a straight-forward task, you "
"will be manipulating the actual files on your hard drive. Please be sure you "
"have a backup of your files before you begin."
msgstr ""
"Med organiziranjem svoje zbirke v &amarok; preprosta naloga, boste "
"manipulirali z dejanskimi datotekami na vašem trdem disku. Preden začnete, "
"poskrbite, da imate varnostno kopijo svojih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guilabel>Organize Files</guilabel> dialog of &amarok; you can "
"easily manage the media files on your hard drive. When you change the naming "
"scheme of media files, you will organize them, which is very powerful. To "
"access the <guilabel>Organize Files</guilabel> dialog, right-click "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Local Collection</guimenu><guimenuitem>Organize Files</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane and "
"the menu interface will pop-up."
msgstr ""
"S pogovornim oknom <guilabel>Organiziraj datoteke</guilabel> programa "
"&amarok; enostavno lahko upravljate medijske datoteke na trdem disku. Ko "
"spremenite shemo poimenovanja predstavnostnih datotek, jih boste "
"organizirali, kar je zelo zmogljivo. Za dostop do pogovornega okna "
"<guilabel>Organiziraj datoteke</guilabel> z desno miškino tipko kliknite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Lokalna zbirka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Organiziraj "
"datoteke</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v podokno <guilabel>Medijski viri</"
"guilabel> in menijski vmesnik se bosta pojavila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using this option will move the files to a new location, so you not only "
"need appropriate rights for both the origin and the destination location, "
"but also enough space, usually the double of the total file size to have the "
"action perform smoothly. If you are unsure, do NOT use this option."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabite to možnost, boste datoteke premaknili na novo lokacijo, tako da "
"ne potrebujete le ustreznih pravic za izvorno in ciljno lokacijo, temveč "
"tudi dovolj prostora, običajno dvakratnik skupne velikosti datoteke, da se "
"dejanje izvede gladko. Če niste prepričani, NE uporabite te možnosti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3885
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Context menu to Organize Collection dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kontekstni meni za pogovorno okno Organiziraj zbirko</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3888
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Context menu to Organize Collection dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Kontekstni meni za pogovorno okno Organiziraj zbirko</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the option <guilabel>Organize Files</guilabel> does not appear, you may "
"have Merged View on (toggled by <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-view-list-tree.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>). In order to safely organize your files, you need to see "
"your collections separated, not merged."
msgstr ""
"Če se možnost <guilabel>Organiziraj datoteke</guilabel> ne prikaže, ste "
"morda vklopili združeni pogled (preklopi ga <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-view-list-tree.png\" format=\"PNG\"/"
"> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>). Če želite varno organizirati svoje "
"datoteke, morate svoje zbirke videti ločene, ne združene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3895
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organizing Files Interface"
msgstr "Vmesnik za organiziranje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After selecting the option <guilabel>Organize Files</guilabel> you will "
"first see an additional option that allows you to move the files to a new "
"location, as well as transcode them at the same time. Depending on the "
"codecs you have installed on the system, some format options might not be "
"available and will be grayed out:"
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete možnost <guilabel>Organiziraj datoteke</guilabel>, boste najprej "
"videli dodatno možnost, ki vam omogoča, da datoteke premaknete na novo "
"lokacijo in jih istočasno prekodirate. Odvisno od kodekov, ki ste jih "
"namestili v sistem, nekatere možnosti formata morda ne bodo na voljo in bodo "
"zatemnjene:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3906
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>First screen when choosing the Organize Files option</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prvi zaslon pri izbiri možnosti Organiziraj datoteke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3909
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>First screen when choosing the Organize Files option</para>"
msgstr "<para>Prvi zaslon pri izbiri možnosti Organiziraj datoteke</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about Transcoding, please see the <link linkend="
"\"transcoding\">Transcoding</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o transkodiranju si oglejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"transcoding\">Transkodiranje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After clicking on the <guilabel>Move</guilabel> button on top of the screen, "
"the following interface will show:"
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na gumb <guilabel>Premakni</guilabel> na vrhu zaslona se prikaže "
"naslednji vmesnik:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3926
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Organize Tracks dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za organiziranje sledi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3929
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Organize Tracks dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za organiziranje skladb</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3935 index.docbook:6951
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "Vsebina"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3941
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Item"
msgstr "Element vmesnika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3948
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection Folder"
msgstr "Zbirna mapa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default collection folder. Set multiple folders in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Amarok</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta mapa zbirke. Nastavite več map v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Amarok</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3956
#, no-c-format
msgid "Token Bar"
msgstr "Token Bar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag and drop multiple tokens here to change the naming scheme of your media "
"files. Only available in <guilabel>Basic</guilabel> view."
msgstr ""
"Sem povlecite in spustite več žetonov, da spremenite shemo poimenovanja "
"svojih medijskih datotek. Na voljo samo v <guilabel>Osnovnem</guilabel> "
"pogledu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3964
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format Presets"
msgstr "Prednastavitve formatov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have created your naming scheme, save it as a preset by clicking "
"<guilabel>Save Preset</guilabel>. Remove presets by clicking "
"<guilabel>Remove Preset</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite shemo poimenovanja, jo shranite kot prednastavitev s klikom na "
"<guilabel>Shrani prednastavitev</guilabel>. Odstranite prednastavitve s "
"klikom na <guilabel>Odstrani prednastavitev</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3972
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace Spaces With Underscores"
msgstr "Presledke zamenjajte s podčrtaji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3975
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked, converts spaces in filenames to underscores."
msgstr "Če je označeno, pretvori presledke v imenih datotek v podčrtaje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore 'The' in Artist names"
msgstr "Prezrite 'The' v imenih izvajalcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, artists' names starting with 'The' will instead be styled ', "
"The'."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bodo imena umetnikov, ki se začnejo z 'The', namesto tega "
"označena z ', The'."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3988
#, no-c-format
msgid "VFAT Safe Names"
msgstr "Varna imena VFAT"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, replaces characters that are incompatible with <emphasis>MS-DOS</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>VFAT</emphasis> file systems with underscores. Most "
"people can leave this option enabled."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, zamenja znake, ki niso združljivi z datotečnim sistemom "
"<emphasis>MS-DOS</emphasis> ali <emphasis>VFAT</emphasis>, s podčrtaji. "
"Večina ljudi lahko pusti to možnost omogočeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:3996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restrict to ASCII"
msgstr "Omeji na ASCII"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3999
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, all non-ASCII characters will be replaced with underscores. "
"<emphasis>Do not check this option if you have non-English characters in "
"your tags</emphasis>. Most people can leave this option unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bodo vsi znaki, ki niso ASCII, zamenjani s podčrtaji. "
"<emphasis>Ne označite te možnosti, če imate v oznakah neangleške znake</"
"emphasis>. Večina ljudi lahko to možnost pusti neoznačeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4004
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Character Replacement"
msgstr "Zamenjava znakov po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replace the tag expressions you write under the <guilabel>Replace</guilabel> "
"box with character strings you write in the <guilabel>With</guilabel> box. "
"Useful if there are mis-spellings in CDDB."
msgstr ""
"Zamenjajte izraze oznak, ki jih napišete pod polje <guilabel>Zamenjaj</"
"guilabel>, z nizi znakov, ki jih napišete v polje <guilabel>Z</guilabel>. "
"Uporabno, če so v CDDB napačno črkovane."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4012
#, no-c-format
msgid "Destination Preview"
msgstr "Predogled cilja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the original naming scheme of your media files and how they will look "
"after the changes are applied (not available since ver. 2.4.2)."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje izvirno shemo poimenovanja vaših medijskih datotek in kako bodo "
"videti po uveljavitvi sprememb (ni na voljo od različice 2.4.2)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4020
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overwrite Destination"
msgstr "Prepiši cilj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, overwrites files of the same name without asking for further "
"confirmation (not available since ver. 2.4.2)."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, prepiše datoteke z istim imenom, ne da bi zahteval nadaljnjo "
"potrditev (ni na voljo od različice 2.4.2)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Contents"
msgstr "Napredne vsebine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4031
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The code version of the <guilabel>Token Bar</guilabel>, which allows you to "
"code the name format of media files. Activate it by pressing "
"<guilabel>Advanced...</guilabel> in the interface menu. To change back click "
"<guilabel>Basic...</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Različica kode <guilabel>Vrstica žetonov</guilabel>, ki vam omogoča "
"kodiranje zapisa imena medijskih datotek. Aktivirajte ga s pritiskom na "
"<guilabel>Napredno...</guilabel> v meniju vmesnika. Za spremembo nazaj "
"kliknite <guilabel>Osnovno...</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enclose conditional inclusion arguments such as CD number in braces, like "
"this:"
msgstr ""
"Argumente pogojne vključitve, kot je številka CD-ja, priložite v oklepajih, "
"kot je ta:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4035
#, no-c-format
msgid "%artist%/%album%{/Disc %discnumber%}/%track% %title%"
msgstr "%artist%/%album%{/Disc %discnumber%}/%track% %title%"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4037
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: formerly, the coding was <varname>%token</varname>, as of 2.4 it is "
"<varname>%token%</varname>."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: prej je bilo kodiranje <varname>%token</varname>, od 2.4 pa je "
"<varname>%token%</varname>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4054
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statistics Synchronization Between Collections and with Last.fm"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija statistike med zbirkami in z Last.fm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4055
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Beginning with version 2.7, &amarok; allows syncing the play-related "
"metadata and statistics of the tracks (such as rating or play count) between "
"any of your collections which show up in <menuchoice><guimenu>Media Sources</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Local Music</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and with the "
"Last.fm web service, if you choose to use Last.fm."
msgstr ""
"Začenši z različico 2.7, &amarok; omogoča sinhronizacijo metapodatkov, "
"povezanih s predvajanjem, in statistike skladb (kot je ocena ali število "
"predvajanj) med katero koli od vaših zbirk, ki so prikazane v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Medijski viri</guimenu><guimenuitem>Lokalna glasba</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in s spletno storitvijo Last.fm, če se odločite "
"za uporabo Last.fm."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4057
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manual Syncing"
msgstr "Ročna sinhronizacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At any time, you can start manual synchronization from "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Synchronize Statistics...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Kadar koli lahko začnete ročno sinhronizacijo iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sinhroniziraj "
"statistiko ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4073
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From here, you can start a synchronization between the collections you "
"select here, which will default to what you have configured in the &amarok; "
"<link linkend=\"metadata\">Metadata</link> configuration."
msgstr ""
"Od tu lahko začnete sinhronizacijo med zbirkami, ki jih izberete tukaj, ki "
"bo privzeto tisto, kar ste konfigurirali v &amarok; Konfiguracija <link "
"linkend=\"metadata\">metapodatkov</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4075
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conflicts and Syncing Statistics Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za spore in statistiko sinhronizacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When syncing, &amarok; will show a dialog window which states the conflicts "
"and statistics of the syncing that has recently been in progress. In this "
"window you will be able to see three tabs: <guilabel>Matched Tracks</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Unique Tracks</guilabel> and <guilabel>Excluded Tracks</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Pri sinhronizaciji &amarok; prikaže pogovorno okno, ki navaja spore in "
"statistiko sinhronizacije, ki je nedavno potekala. V tem oknu boste lahko "
"videli tri zavihke: <guilabel>Ujemajoče se sledi</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Edinstvene sledi</guilabel> in <guilabel>Izključene sledi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:4092
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matched Tracks"
msgstr "Ujemajoče se skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab will show all the tracks that &amarok; has found in more than one "
"collection, and reflects conflicts. When tracks are grouped, you can see two "
"types of background: light green, and light red. A light green background "
"indicates the new or updated field, whilst a light red background will "
"indicate the old/overwritten field. You do not need to solve all conflicts "
"listed here; the particular field of the listed tracks are not going to be "
"synced if you do not resolve the conflict."
msgstr ""
"Na tem zavihku bodo prikazane vse skladbe, ki jih &amarok; je našel v več "
"kot eni zbirki in odraža konflikte. Ko so skladbe združene, lahko vidite dve "
"vrsti ozadja: svetlo zeleno in svetlo rdeče. Svetlo zeleno ozadje označuje "
"novo ali posodobljeno polje, medtem ko bo svetlo rdeče ozadje označevalo "
"staro/prepisano polje. Ni vam treba rešiti vseh tukaj navedenih sporov; "
"določeno polje navedenih skladb ne bo sinhronizirano, če ne razrešite spora."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:4097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unique Tracks"
msgstr "Edinstvene skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are tracks found in only one collection. You can use it as a "
"<emphasis>difference view</emphasis>. Track dragging is supported here."
msgstr ""
"To so skladbe v samo eni zbirki. Uporabite ga lahko kot <emphasis>pogled "
"razlike</emphasis>. Tu je podprto vlečenje sledi."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:4102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Excluded Tracks"
msgstr "Izključene skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are tracks that are not synced because of different reasons, such as "
"identical metadata, so as not cause to disorder in the database."
msgstr ""
"To so skladbe, ki niso sinhronizirane zaradi različnih razlogov, kot so "
"enaki metapodatki, da ne povzročijo nereda v bazi podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronizing with Last.fm"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija z Last.fm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have the Last.fm plugin enabled and configured correctly with your "
"Last.fm account, you can choose to also synchronize your &amarok; play "
"counts, ratings and labels with your Last.fm Library. The sync takes some "
"time, but you may continue using &amarok; while it is syncing. Please note "
"that Unattended Synchronization (which will be explained later on) is not "
"possible with Last.fm, and synchronization from Last.fm to &amarok; needs to "
"be initiated manually."
msgstr ""
"Če imate vtičnik Last.fm omogočen in pravilno konfiguriran z vašim računom "
"Last.fm, lahko izberete tudi sinhronizacijo &amarok; število predvajanj, "
"ocene in oznake z vašo knjižnico Last.fm. Sinhronizacija traja nekaj časa, "
"vendar lahko še naprej uporabljate &amarok; med sinhronizacijo. Upoštevajte, "
"da nenadzorovana sinhronizacija (ki bo razložena kasneje) ni mogoča z Last."
"fm, sinhronizacija iz Last.fm v &amarok; je treba sprožiti ročno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spelling Auto-Correction"
msgstr "Samodejni popravek črkovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Last.fm enables by default a feature that will auto-correct common "
"misspelling during the sync. It can happen that even if you scrobble many "
"track plays, it does not show up in Matched Tracks as Last.fm knows the "
"track under a slightly different name."
msgstr ""
"Last.fm privzeto omogoča funkcijo, ki med sinhronizacijo samodejno popravi "
"pogosto napačno črkovanje. Lahko se zgodi, da tudi če pobrskate po številnih "
"predvajanjih skladbe, se ta ne prikaže v ujemajočih se skladbah, saj Last.fm "
"pozna skladbo pod nekoliko drugačnim imenom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can disable this feature on the Last.fm site, and changes will be "
"applied also to your past scrobbles. You have two options:"
msgstr ""
"To funkcijo lahko onemogočite na spletnem mestu Last.fm in spremembe bodo "
"uporabljene tudi pri vaših preteklih drskih. Imate dve možnosti:"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:4132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Off</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>Izklopljeno</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tracks are matched properly, but if you change your tags after some time, "
"your play-count will be split in two tracks."
msgstr ""
"Skladbe se pravilno ujemajo, vendar če čez nekaj časa spremenite oznake, bo "
"vaše število predvajanj razdeljeno na dve skladbi."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:4137
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>On</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>Vklopljeno</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can play-count the tracks even if tags are changed after some time, but "
"you will have to use Last.fm preferred spelling."
msgstr ""
"Skladbe lahko predvajate, tudi če se oznake čez nekaj časa spremenijo, "
"vendar boste morali uporabiti prednostno črkovanje Last.fm."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unattended Syncing"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija brez nadzora"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Please note the dialog will only appear in the case of iPods."
msgstr "Upoštevajte, da se pogovorno okno prikaže samo v primeru iPodov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you connect a device that is able to sync with your collections, a pop-"
"up like this will appear."
msgstr ""
"Ko povežete napravo, ki se lahko sinhronizira z vašimi zbirkami, se prikaže "
"pojavno okno, kot je to."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For unattended syncing to start, you only need to click <guilabel>Yes</"
"guilabel> in the pop-up. &amarok; will work in the background, so the "
"metadata in your device including ratings, first/last played times, play "
"counts and labels will be synced with other collections <link linkend="
"\"metadata\">configured to participate in the synchronization</link>, and "
"tracks recently played on the device will be scrobbled to Last.fm, if it is "
"enabled. The process will not ask for user interaction unless any conflict "
"is found in the middle."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek nenadzorovane sinhronizacije morate samo klikniti <guilabel>Da</"
"guilabel> v pojavnem oknu. &amarok; bodo delovali v ozadju, tako da bodo "
"metapodatki v vaši napravi, vključno z ocenami, časi prvega/zadnjega "
"igranja, štetjem predvajanj in oznakami, sinhronizirani z drugimi zbirkami "
"<link linkend=\"metadata\">konfiguriranimi za sodelovanje pri "
"sinhronizaciji</link>, in skladbe, ki so bile nedavno predvajane v napravi, "
"bodo pomaknjene na Last.fm, če je ta omogočen. Postopek ne bo zahteval "
"interakcije uporabnika, razen če se na sredini pojavi kakršen koli konflikt."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remote Collections"
msgstr "Oddaljene zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Often it is very useful to share your media files across the network, "
"especially if you want to use it on different computers. This can be done in "
"different ways:"
msgstr ""
"Pogosto je zelo koristno deliti predstavnostne datoteke po omrežju, še "
"posebej, če jih želite uporabljati v različnih računalnikih. To je mogoče "
"storiti na različne načine:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Ampache</title>"
msgstr "<title>Ampache</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; is able to play music from an <guilabel>Ampache</guilabel> media "
"server. If you want to install a server, see <ulink url=\"https://github.com/"
"ampache/ampache/wiki/Installation\">here</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; lahko predvaja glasbo iz medijskega strežnika <guilabel>Ampache</"
"guilabel>. Če želite namestiti strežnik, glejte <ulink url=\"https://github."
"com/ampache/ampache/wiki/Installation\">tukaj</ulink> za več informacij."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ampache Client"
msgstr "Odjemalec Ampache"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activate the <guilabel>Ampache</guilabel> service using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Plugins</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> icon to open the "
"configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Aktivirajte storitev <guilabel>Ampache</guilabel> z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vtičniki</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Kliknite ikono "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, da odprete "
"konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select <guilabel>Add Server</guilabel>:"
msgstr "Izberite <guilabel>Dodaj strežnik</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure the service with the data entered on the server:"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte storitev s podatki, vnesenimi na strežniku:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now the <guilabel>Ampache</guilabel> service should appear in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Media Sources</guimenu><guimenuitem>Internet</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj bi se morala storitev <guilabel>Ampache</guilabel> pojaviti v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Medijski viri</guimenu><guimenuitem>Internet</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Digital Audio Access Protocol (DAAP)"
msgstr "Protokol za dostop do digitalnega zvoka (DAAP)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"DAAP is a protocol to share media over a network. It was first used for the "
"<guilabel>iTunes</guilabel> music player, but is used widely now. The "
"current state is that the DAAP-plugin won't work with a recent iTunes, the "
"Firefly media server is known to work."
msgstr ""
"DAAP je protokol za skupno rabo predstavnosti prek omrežja. Najprej je bil "
"uporabljen za glasbeni predvajalnik <guilabel>iTunes</guilabel>, zdaj pa se "
"pogosto uporablja. Trenutno stanje je, da vtičnik DAAP ne bo deloval z "
"nedavnim iTunesom, znano je, da medijski strežnik Firefly deluje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4246 index.docbook:4267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Client"
msgstr "Stranka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; will show the tracks from the server in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Media Sources</guimenu><guimenuitem>Local Music</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> pane if you enable the DAAP Collection in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Configure Plugins</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Collections</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If the "
"collection is not showing up, click the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-view-list-tree.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> icon to be sure you are not in Merged View."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; bo prikazal skladbe s strežnika v podoknu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Medijski viri</guimenu><guimenuitem>Lokalna glasba</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, če omogočite zbirko DAAP v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj vtičnike</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Zbirke</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če se zbirka ne "
"prikaže, kliknite ikono <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-view-list-tree.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>, da se prepričate niste v združenem pogledu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Samba"
msgstr "Samba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Samba</guilabel> is a free implementation of the <emphasis>SMB/"
"CIFS</emphasis> protocol which is used to share files and printers in a "
"network. Most modern file managers like &dolphin; and <guilabel>Nautilus</"
"guilabel> support this protocol."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samba</guilabel> je brezplačna izvedba protokola <emphasis>SMB/"
"CIFS</emphasis>, ki se uporablja za skupno rabo datotek in tiskalnikov v "
"omrežju. Večina sodobnih upraviteljev datotek, kot je &dolphin; in "
"<guilabel>Nautilus</guilabel> podpirata ta protokol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to mount the share to use it in &amarok;. To do this, you need to "
"install the package <emphasis>smbfs</emphasis>. Use the command"
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo v &amarok;u morate skupno rabo namestiti. Če želite to narediti, "
"morate namestiti paket <emphasis>smbfs</emphasis>. Uporabite ukaz"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"sudo mount -t cifs //<guilabel>host</guilabel>/<guilabel>share</guilabel> "
"<guilabel>/mount-point/</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"sudo mount -t cifs //<guilabel>gostitelj</guilabel>/<guilabel>deljenje</"
"guilabel> <guilabel>/mount-point/</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"to mount the share. After that you can use it like a local folder and add it "
"to your local collection."
msgstr ""
"za namestitev deleža. Po tem ga lahko uporabite kot lokalno mapo in dodate v "
"svojo lokalno zbirko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4275
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Server</title>"
msgstr "<title>Strežnik</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way is to use your file manager. On <guilabel>Debian</guilabel>-"
"based distributions like &ubuntu; you can install a &dolphin; extension to "
"manage shares using"
msgstr ""
"Najlažji način je uporaba upravljalnika datotek. V distribucijah, ki "
"temeljijo na <guilabel>Debian</guilabel>, kot je &ubuntu; lahko namestite "
"&dolphin; razširitev za upravljanje skupnih rab z uporabo"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4278
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo apt-get install kdenetwork-filesharing"
msgstr "sudo apt-get namestite kdenetwork-filesharing"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the properties of a folder in &dolphin; and switch to the "
"<guilabel>Share</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Odprite lastnosti mape v &dolphin; in preklopite na zavihek <guilabel>Skupna "
"raba</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To share the folder, just check the <guilabel>Share with Samba (Microsoft "
"Windows)</guilabel> field and set the share name under the <guilabel>Name</"
"guilabel> field. Check the <guilabel>Allow Guests</guilabel> checkbox to "
"allow anonymous users access to the folder."
msgstr ""
"Za skupno rabo mape preprosto označite polje <guilabel>Skupna raba s Sambo "
"(Microsoft Windows)</guilabel> in nastavite ime za skupno rabo pod poljem "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel>. Označite potrditveno polje <guilabel>Dovoli "
"gostom</guilabel>, da dovolite anonimnim uporabnikom dostop do mape."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folder should now be accessible to the network. Please see the <link "
"linkend=\"client\">Client section</link> for details on how to use it in "
"&amarok;."
msgstr ""
"Mapa bi morala biti zdaj dostopna omrežju. Oglejte si <link linkend=\"client"
"\">razdelek o odjemalcih</link> za podrobnosti o uporabi v &amarok;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Universal Plug and Play (UPnP) / DLNA"
msgstr "Univerzalni Plug and Play (UPnP) / DLNA"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>UPnP</emphasis> is a set of protocols to share media on the "
"network. It is also supported by a wide range of residential gateways and "
"Network Attached Storage devices. UPnP support is now commonly marketed as "
"<ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DLNA\">DLNA</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>UPnP</emphasis> je nabor protokolov za skupno rabo predstavnosti v "
"omrežju. Podpira ga tudi širok nabor stanovanjskih prehodov in omrežnih "
"naprav za shranjevanje. Podpora za UPnP se zdaj pogosto trži kot <ulink url="
"\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DLNA\">DLNA</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; has a built-in UPnP media share client so it can play tracks shared "
"on the network. To enable it, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Plugins</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Collections</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and check "
"the box by the <guilabel>UPnP Collection</guilabel> plugin."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; ima vgrajen odjemalec za skupno rabo medijev UPnP, tako da lahko "
"predvaja skladbe, ki so v skupni rabi v omrežju. Če ga želite omogočiti, "
"uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj "
"Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vtičnike</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Zbirke</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in potrdite polje z vtičnik <guilabel>UPnP "
"Collection</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a media share is discovered it will be shown in <guilabel>Local Music</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je medijska skupna raba odkrita, bo prikazana v <guilabel>Lokalni glasbi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The UPnP feature depends on <guilabel>KDE's</guilabel> UPnP media server "
"support. As of now (2015) there is no working UPnP kio-slave available."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija UPnP je odvisna od <guilabel>KDE</guilabel> podpore za medijski "
"strežnik UPnP. Od zdaj (2015) ni na voljo nobenega delujočega kio-slave UPnP."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4350
#, no-c-format
msgid "External Database"
msgstr "Zunanja baza podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; 2.2 and above support an external <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> "
"database as a backend."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; 2.2 in višje podpirajo zunanjo bazo podatkov <guilabel>MySQL</"
"guilabel> kot zaledje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Install MySQL-Server"
msgstr "Namestite MySQL-Server"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First you need to install an <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> server. On Debian-"
"based distributions like Ubuntu you can use"
msgstr ""
"Najprej morate namestiti strežnik <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>. V "
"distribucijah, ki temeljijo na Debianu, kot je Ubuntu, lahko uporabite"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4361
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client"
msgstr "sudo apt-get namestite mysql-strežnik mysql-odjemalec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"to install it. You will be asked to specify a password for the root-account "
"for the database. The <emphasis>mysql-client</emphasis> package is needed in "
"order to execute some of the commands in this document, but it's not "
"fundamental to the use of &amarok;."
msgstr ""
"da ga namestite. Zahtevani boste, da določite geslo za korenski račun za "
"bazo podatkov. Paket <emphasis>mysql-client</emphasis> je potreben za "
"izvajanje nekaterih ukazov v tem dokumentu, vendar ni bistvenega pomena za "
"uporabo &amarok;a."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Database"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte bazo podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connect to the local database using"
msgstr "Povežite se z lokalno bazo podatkov z uporabo"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4369
#, no-c-format
msgid "mysql -u root -p"
msgstr "mysql -u root -p"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will be prompted for the password for <guilabel>MySQL's</guilabel> "
"<emphasis>root</emphasis> user. You will get the <screen>mysql&gt;</screen> "
"prompt."
msgstr ""
"Pozvani boste k vnosu gesla za <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> <emphasis>root</"
"emphasis> uporabnika. Dobili boste poziv <screen>mysql&gt;</screen>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new user <replaceable>amarokuser</replaceable> with the password "
"<replaceable>amarokpass</replaceable> using the"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite novega uporabnika <replaceable>amarokuser</replaceable> z geslom "
"<replaceable>amarokpass</replaceable> z uporabo"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"CREATE USER <guilabel>'amarokuser'</guilabel>@<guilabel>'localhost'</"
"guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY <guilabel>'amarokpass'</guilabel>;"
msgstr ""
"CREATE USER <guilabel>'amarokuser'</guilabel>@<guilabel>'localhost'</"
"guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY <guilabel>'amarokpass'</guilabel>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4377
#, no-c-format
msgid "command. Amarok needs its own database, which is created with"
msgstr "ukaz. Amarok potrebuje svojo bazo podatkov, ki je ustvarjena z"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4379
#, no-c-format
msgid "CREATE DATABASE <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>;"
msgstr "CREATE DATABASE <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Give the new user access to the database by entering the"
msgstr "Novemu uporabniku omogočite dostop do baze podatkov z vnosom"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GRANT ALL ON <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>.* TO <guilabel>'amarokuser'</"
"guilabel>@<guilabel>'%'</guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY <guilabel>'amarokpass'</"
"guilabel>;"
msgstr ""
"GRANT ALL ON <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>.* TO <guilabel>'amarokuser'</"
"guilabel>@<guilabel>'%'</guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY <guilabel>'amarokpass'</"
"guilabel>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"command, where <emphasis>%</emphasis> is a wildcard to allow all hosts to "
"connect to the database. Now use the"
msgstr ""
"ukaz, kjer je <emphasis>%</emphasis> nadomestni znak, ki vsem gostiteljem "
"omogoča povezavo z bazo podatkov. Zdaj uporabite"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4387
#, no-c-format
msgid "FLUSH PRIVILEGES;"
msgstr "FLUSH PRIVILEGES;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement to reload various internal caches used by <guilabel>MySQL</"
"guilabel>. Finally"
msgstr ""
"stavek za ponovno nalaganje različnih notranjih predpomnilnikov, ki jih "
"uporablja <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>. Končno"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4391
#, no-c-format
msgid "exit"
msgstr "izhod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4393
#, no-c-format
msgid "closes the <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> prompt."
msgstr "zapre poziv <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the server can only be accessed by the local host. To change this "
"you need to edit the file <filename>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</filename> and adjust "
"the address near <emphasis>bind-address</emphasis> to the one your server "
"listens on the network. <guilabel>0.0.0.0</guilabel> listens on all "
"interfaces. After that you need to restart the server using"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto lahko do strežnika dostopa samo lokalni gostitelj. Če želite to "
"spremeniti, morate urediti datoteko <filename>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</filename> "
"in prilagoditi naslov blizu <emphasis>bind-address</emphasis> tistemu, ki ga "
"vaš strežnik posluša v omrežju. <guilabel>0.0.0.0</guilabel> posluša na vseh "
"vmesnikih. Po tem morate znova zagnati strežnik z uporabo"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4397
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo service mysql restart"
msgstr "ponovni zagon storitve sudo mysql"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Client"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte odjemalca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the configuration dialog by clicking <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Database</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Enable the checkbox and enter the user data."
msgstr ""
"Odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno s klikom na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Baza podatkov</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Omogočite "
"potrditveno polje in vnesite uporabniške podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4416
#, no-c-format
msgid "You need to restart &amarok; so that the changes take effect."
msgstr "Ponovno morate zagnati &amarok; tako da bodo spremembe začele veljati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Migrating from MySQL Embedded to MySQL Server"
msgstr "Selitev z MySQL Embedded na MySQL Server"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to maintain the statistics, &etc; that you have in the embedded "
"<guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> database from before &amarok; 2.2, you can do the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite vzdrževati statistiko itd. ki jih imate v vdelani zbirki podatkov "
"<guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> pred &amarok; 2.2, lahko storite naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, start &amarok; 2.2+ at least once to give the database a chance to "
"update to the latest schema version."
msgstr ""
"Najprej zaženite &amarok; 2.2+ vsaj enkrat, da se baza podatkov lahko "
"posodobi na najnovejšo različico sheme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next, kill the running <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> service"
msgstr "Nato ukinite delujočo storitev <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4426
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo /etc/init.d/mysql stop"
msgstr "sudo /etc/init.d/mysql stop"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and start a <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> daemon from your <filename>~/.kde4/"
"share/apps/amarok</filename> directory (--defaults-file MUST be the first "
"option!):"
msgstr ""
"in zaženite demon <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> iz imenika <filename>~/.kde4/"
"share/apps/amarok</filename> (--defaults-file MORA biti prva možnost!):"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"/usr/sbin/mysqld --defaults-file=`pwd`/my.cnf --default-storage-"
"engine=MyISAM --datadir=`pwd`/mysqle --socket=`pwd`/sock --skip-grant-tables"
msgstr ""
"/usr/sbin/mysqld --defaults-file=`pwd`/my.cnf --default-storage-"
"engine=MyISAM --datadir=`pwd`/mysqle --socket=`pwd`/sock --skip- dotacijske "
"mize"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The skip-grant-tables means you can use any password or username to connect "
"to it. 'localhost' will not work, the <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> client will "
"try to use a <guilabel>&UNIX;</guilabel> socket. Using <guilabel>127.0.0.1</"
"guilabel> as the host makes it work. Some systems may restrict this access "
"through apparmor or SE&Linux;. They can be temporarily disabled with"
msgstr ""
"Tabele preskočenih dodelitev pomenijo, da lahko uporabite katero koli geslo "
"ali uporabniško ime za povezavo z njim. 'localhost' ne bo deloval, bo "
"odjemalec <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> poskusil uporabiti vtičnico "
"<guilabel>&UNIX;</guilabel>. Če uporabljate <guilabel>127.0.0.1</guilabel> "
"kot gostitelja, deluje. Nekateri sistemi lahko omejijo ta dostop prek "
"apparmorja ali SE&Linux;. Jih je mogoče začasno onemogočiti z"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4434
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo /etc/init.d/apparmor stop"
msgstr "sudo /etc/init.d/apparmor stop"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, run mysqldump, passing in the -S option to specify the local socket. "
"This will dump your old embedded DB out to a SQL file."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj zaženite mysqldump in podajte možnost -S, da določite lokalno vtičnico."
"S tem boste vašo staro vdelano bazo podatkov stresli v datoteko SQL."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4438
#, no-c-format
msgid "mysqldump -S sock amarok &gt; amarok.mysql"
msgstr "mysqldump -S sock amarok &gt; amarok.mysql"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then restart your <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> service and load this "
"SQL file into your <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> server. You'll have needed to "
"already run the GRANT statement above and create an &amarok; database "
"(<quote>CREATE DATABASE amarok;</quote>):"
msgstr ""
"Nato lahko znova zaženete svojo storitev <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> in "
"naložite to datoteko SQL v svoj strežnik <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>. Morali "
"boste že zagnati zgornji stavek GRANT in ustvariti &amarok; zbirko podatkov "
"(<quote>CREATE DATABASE amarok;</quote>):"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"sudo /etc/init.d/mysql stop mysql -u amarokuser -p amarok &lt; amarok.mysql"
msgstr ""
"sudo /etc/init.d/mysql stop mysql -u amarokuser -p amarok &lt; amarok.mysql"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may need to re-scan your collection in &amarok; after completing this."
msgstr ""
"Morda boste morali ponovno skenirati svojo zbirko v &amarok; po zaključku "
"tega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4449
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Media Devices"
msgstr "Delo z medijskimi napravami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use &amarok; to play music from media devices such as MTP devices, iPods, "
"and generic USB devices."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi &amarok; za predvajanje glasbe iz medijskih naprav, kot so naprave "
"MTP, iPodi in generične naprave USB."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connecting Media Devices"
msgstr "Povezovanje medijskih naprav"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connect your media device using the USB cable. The device notifier applet in "
"&kde; will automatically pop up with a list of all available media devices. "
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"emblem-mounted.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"icon to access your device."
msgstr ""
"Povežite predstavnostno napravo s kablom USB. Programček za obveščanje "
"naprave v &kde; se samodejno prikaže s seznamom vseh razpoložljivih "
"medijskih naprav. Za dostop do svoje naprave kliknite ikono "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-emblem-mounted."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Play Music from the Media Device"
msgstr "Predvajanje glasbe iz medijske naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Or just wait until your device shows up in &amarok;, which will take "
"anywhere from a few seconds to a minute or more, to scan the device for "
"music tracks. Until then the vfat volume will show 0 tracks."
msgstr ""
"Ali pa samo počakajte, da se vaša naprava prikaže v &amarok;, kar bo trajalo "
"od nekaj sekund do minute ali več, da poiščete glasbene skladbe v napravi. "
"Do takrat bo vsebina vfat prikazovala 0 sledi oz. skladb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the scan, &amarok; will display all the music tracks available in the "
"Media Device, which you can then move to the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> "
"to play them, or copy or move to your <guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Po skeniranju &amarok; bo prikazal vse skladbe, ki so na voljo v medijski "
"napravi, ki jih lahko nato premaknete na <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</"
"guilabel>, da jih predvajate, ali kopirate ali premaknete v svojo "
"<guilabel>Lokalno zbirko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing the Media"
msgstr "Upravljanje medijev"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add to playlist"
msgstr "Dodaj na seznam predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds all the selected tracks from the media device to the current &amarok; "
"playlist."
msgstr ""
"Doda vse izbrane skladbe iz predstavnostne naprave v trenutni &amarok; "
"seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4548
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace the playlist"
msgstr "Zamenja seznam predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clears the current &amarok; playlist and adds instead all the selected "
"tracks from the media device."
msgstr ""
"Počisti trenutni seznam predvajanja &amarok; in namesto tega doda vse "
"izbrane skladbe iz predstavnostne naprave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Device"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte napravo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4559
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a dialog box to edit configuration options for the device."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno za urejanje konfiguracijskih možnosti za napravo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4564
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disconnect Device"
msgstr "Odklopi napravo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4567
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disconnects the device from the computer."
msgstr "Prekine povezavo naprave z računalnikom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4572
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy to collection"
msgstr "Kopiraj v zbirko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy all the selected tracks to the Local collection or to any other media "
"devices connected."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte vse izbrane skladbe v lokalno zbirko ali v katero koli drugo "
"povezano predstavnostno napravo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move to collection"
msgstr "Premakni v zbirko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move all the selected tracks to the Local collection or to any other media "
"devices connected."
msgstr ""
"Premakni vse izbrane skladbe v lokalno zbirko ali v katero koli drugo "
"povezano predstavnostno napravo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4588
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move to trash"
msgstr "Premakni v koš"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4591
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves all the selected tracks from the media device to the trash."
msgstr "Premakne vse izbrane skladbe iz predstavnostne naprave v koš."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4596
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete tracks"
msgstr "Izbriši skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4599
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes all the selected tracks from the media device."
msgstr "Izbriše vse izbrane skladbe iz predstavnostne naprave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organize Files"
msgstr "Organiziraj datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organizes tracks based on the configuration for the device."
msgstr "Organizira skladbe glede na konfiguracijo naprave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4612
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit track details"
msgstr "Uredi podrobnosti skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog box to edit details of the selected tracks from the media "
"device."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno za urejanje podrobnosti izbranih skladb iz "
"predstavnostne naprave."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Troubleshooting Media Device support"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav s podporo za medijske naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4623
#, no-c-format
msgid "As of Amarok 2.8, the following devices should work with Amarok:"
msgstr "Od Amaroka 2.8 naj bi naslednje naprave delovale z Amarokom:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic Media Players connected through the UMS protocol."
msgstr "Generični medijski predvajalniki, povezani prek protokola UMS."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"iPods/iPhones, depending on their support by the libgpod library. The status "
"depends on the version of this library installed on your system, please "
"refer to <ulink url=\"http://www.gtkpod.org/wiki/Home\">the libgpod support "
"listing</ulink> on their homepage."
msgstr ""
"iPod/iPhone, odvisno od podpore knjižnice libgpod. Stanje je odvisno od "
"različice te knjižnice, ki je nameščena v vašem sistemu, glejte <ulink url="
"\"http://www.gtkpod.org/wiki/Home\">seznam podpore za libgpod</ulink> na "
"njihovi domači strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"limited support for devices using the MTP protocol, the support for new "
"Android devices is currently implemented for the next Amarok version."
msgstr ""
"omejena podpora za naprave, ki uporabljajo protokol MTP, podpora za nove "
"naprave Android je trenutno implementirana za naslednjo različico Amaroka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4633 index.docbook:7636
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Cover Manager</title>"
msgstr "<title>Upravljalnik naslovnic</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Cover Manager</guilabel> is a tool to manage the cover art "
"images of your collection. It allows you to change covers easily, fetch all "
"missing covers and browse them. You can find <guilabel>Cover Manager</"
"guilabel> in <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cover Manager</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Upravljalnik naslovnic</guilabel> je orodje za upravljanje slik "
"naslovnic vaše zbirke. Omogoča enostavno menjavo naslovnic, pridobivanje "
"vseh manjkajočih naslovnic in brskanje po njih. <guilabel>Upravljalnik "
"naslovnic</guilabel> najdete v <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljalnik naslovnic</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When scanning the local music library, &amarok; tries to find corresponding "
"covers for albums. At this point, &amarok; only searches them from the file "
"system, not from the Internet. If none are found in your files, &amarok; "
"uses a placeholder image like this for the album cover:"
msgstr ""
"Ko skenirate lokalno glasbeno knjižnico, poskuša &amarok; najti ustrezne "
"naslovnice za albume. Na tej točki &amarok; išče jih samo iz datotečnega "
"sistema ne tudi iz interneta. Če v vaših datotekah ni nobene, &amarok; za "
"naslovnico albuma uporablja sliko nadomestnega znaka, kot je ta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an album is missing a cover or the current one is incorrect, you can "
"fetch one from the Internet with <guilabel>Cover Manager</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če albumu manjka ovitek ali je trenutni nepravilen, ga lahko pridobite iz "
"interneta z <guilabel>Upravljalnik naslovnic</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4664
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing Covers"
msgstr "Brskanje po naslovnicah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With <guilabel>Cover Manager</guilabel>, browsing covers is easy. You can "
"view covers for any artist by selecting from list on left, or use the search "
"box to find the right album. On the status bar, you can see how many covers "
"are currently listed and how many albums are missing covers. You can also "
"set the <guilabel>Cover Manager</guilabel> to only show albums with or "
"without covers. By right-clicking on cover art and selecting "
"<guilabel>Display Cover</guilabel> you can view the cover image at the "
"original size."
msgstr ""
"Z <guilabel>Upravljalnik naslovnic</guilabel> je brskanje po naslovnicah "
"enostavno. Naslovnice za katerega koli izvajalca si lahko ogledate tako, da "
"izberete s seznama na levi ali uporabite iskalno polje, da poiščete pravi "
"album. V vrstici stanja lahko vidite, koliko naslovnic je trenutno navedenih "
"in koliko albumov nima naslovnic. Prav tako lahko nastavite "
"<guilabel>Upravljalnik naslovnic</guilabel>, da prikaže samo albume z ali "
"brez naslovnic. Z desnim klikom na naslovnico in izbiro <guilabel>Prikaži "
"naslovnico</guilabel> si lahko ogledate sliko naslovnice v izvirni velikosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4668
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fetching Missing Covers"
msgstr "Pridobivanje manjkajočih naslovnic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are albums with missing covers, you can try to automatically fetch "
"them all from the Internet. Just select <guilabel>Fetch Missing Covers</"
"guilabel> from the top of the window and <emphasis>Cover Manager</emphasis> "
"will try to find covers. If there are many albums missing covers, the "
"process may take some time."
msgstr ""
"Če obstajajo albumi z manjkajočimi naslovnicami, jih lahko poskusite "
"samodejno pridobiti vse iz interneta. Samo izberite <guilabel>Pridobi "
"manjkajoče naslovnice</guilabel> na vrhu okna in <emphasis>Upravljalnik "
"naslovnic</emphasis> bo poskušal najti naslovnice. Če veliko albumov nima "
"naslovnic, lahko postopek traja nekaj časa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4672
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Cover Art"
msgstr "Spremenljiva prevleka Art"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is an album with an incorrect cover, you can fetch new one from the "
"Internet. Right-click on the cover and select <guilabel>Fetch Cover</"
"guilabel>. A dialog window for finding a new cover will open. &amarok; "
"automatically tries find the correct album art by searching with the artist "
"name and album name. Usually this works very well, as with the example, and "
"you will most likely see a correct cover on results as in the example. If no "
"correct cover is found, you can try to enter a custom search phrase or "
"change the source of images by clicking on <guilabel>Configure...</guilabel> "
"You can select where to search, including Last.fm, Google Images, Yahoo! "
"Image Search or Discogs. After finding a cover for album, just click "
"<guilabel>OK</guilabel> and the changes will be applied."
msgstr ""
"Če obstaja album z napačno naslovnico, lahko poiščete novo z interneta. Z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknite naslovnico in izberite <guilabel>Pridobi "
"naslovnico</guilabel>. Odpre se pogovorno okno za iskanje nove naslovnice. "
"&amarok; samodejno poskuša najti pravo sliko albuma z iskanjem po imenu "
"izvajalca in imenu albuma. Običajno to deluje zelo dobro, kot pri primeru, "
"in najverjetneje boste videli pravilno naslovnico na rezultatih, kot je v "
"primeru. Če ne najdete pravilne naslovnice, lahko poskusite vnesti iskalni "
"izraz po meri ali spremenite vir slik s klikom na <guilabel>Konfiguriraj...</"
"guilabel> Izberete lahko, kje želite iskati, vključno z Last.fm, Google "
"Images , Yahoo! Iskanje slik ali Discogs. Ko najdete naslovnico za album, "
"samo kliknite <guilabel>V redu</guilabel> in spremembe bodo uporabljene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use a image from your hard drive as an album cover. If you want "
"to store the image in the Album folder, name it <filename>cover.jpg</"
"filename> or <filename>cover.png</filename> for best results. As before, "
"right-click on the incorrect image and click on <guilabel>Set Custom Cover</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Sliko s trdega diska lahko uporabite tudi kot naslovnico albuma. Če želite "
"sliko shraniti v mapo Album, jo poimenujte <filename>cover.jpg</filename> "
"ali <filename>cover.png</filename> za najboljše rezultate. Kot prej, z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknite napačno sliko in kliknite <guilabel>Nastavi "
"naslovnico po meri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't like the cover art at all, you can unset it by right-clicking "
"on the image and selecting <guilabel>Unset Cover</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če vam naslovnica sploh ni všeč, jo lahko počistite tako, da z desno miškino "
"tipko kliknete sliko in izberete <guilabel>Odstrani naslovnico</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find this menu without <guilabel>Cover Manager</guilabel> too. Just "
"right-click on the album or song from your playlist or collection and hover "
"the <guilabel>Album</guilabel> item."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni lahko najdete tudi brez <guilabel>Upravljalnik naslovnic</guilabel>. "
"Preprosto z desno miškino tipko kliknite album ali pesem s svojega seznama "
"predvajanja ali zbirke in premaknite miškin kazalec na element "
"<guilabel>Album</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4696
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tag Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik oznak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The built-in <emphasis>Tag Editor</emphasis> allows to show and change meta "
"data of music files. To open the editor just right-click on one or more "
"selected songs, albums, or genres, in either your collection or your "
"playlist, click on <guilabel>Edit Track Details</guilabel> and choose the "
"<guilabel>Tags</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Vgrajeni <emphasis>Urejevalnik oznak</emphasis> omogoča prikazovanje in "
"spreminjanje metapodatkov glasbenih datotek. Če želite odpreti urejevalnik, "
"z desno miškino tipko kliknite eno ali več izbranih pesmi, albumov ali "
"žanrov v vaši zbirki ali na seznamu predvajanja, kliknite <guilabel>Uredi "
"podrobnosti o skladbi</guilabel> in izberite <guilabel>Oznake</guilabel > "
"zavihek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4699
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Tags Manually"
msgstr "Ročno uredi oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the proper line to the required value and click <guilabel>Save &amp; "
"Close</guilabel>. Clicking <guilabel>Cancel</guilabel> discards all unsaved "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Spremeni ustrezno vrstico na zahtevano vrednost in kliknite <guilabel>Shrani "
"&amp; Zapri</guilabel>. Če kliknete <guilabel>Prekliči</guilabel>, zavržete "
"vse neshranjene spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tags are metadata such as the track number or the artist of the track "
"contained in the file. A very common kind of tag is the <emphasis>ID3 tag</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Oznake so metapodatki, kot je številka skladbe ali izvajalec skladbe v "
"datoteki. Zelo pogosta vrsta oznake je <emphasis>oznaka ID3</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4705
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a list of tags supported by &amarok;:"
msgstr "Tukaj je seznam oznak, ki jih podpira &amarok;:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4712
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Tag</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Oznaka</entry>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4719
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Title</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Naslov</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4722
#, no-c-format
msgid "The title of the track."
msgstr "Naslov skladbe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4727
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Artist</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Umetnik</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4730
#, no-c-format
msgid "The artist or band of the track."
msgstr "Izvajalec ali skupina skladbe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4735
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Composer</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4738
#, no-c-format
msgid "The composer of the track."
msgstr "Skladatelj skladbe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Album Artist"
msgstr "Izvajalec albuma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4746
#, no-c-format
msgid "The artist or band of the album."
msgstr "Izvajalec ali skupina albuma."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4751
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Album</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Album</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4754
#, no-c-format
msgid "The album title."
msgstr "Naslov albuma."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disc Number"
msgstr "Številka diska"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4762
#, no-c-format
msgid "The disc number of the album; important in a multi-CD album."
msgstr "Številka plošče albuma; pomembna v albumu z več CD-ji."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4767 index.docbook:5294
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Genre</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Zvrst</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The genre of the track. This can be a custom genre, but usually one of the "
"predefined ones is used."
msgstr ""
"Žanr skladbe. To je lahko žanr po meri, vendar se običajno uporabi eden od "
"vnaprej določenih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4775
#, no-c-format
msgid "Beats Per Minute"
msgstr "Utripov na minuto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4778
#, no-c-format
msgid "The tempo of the track."
msgstr "Tempo skladbe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4783
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Track</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Skladba</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4786
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of the track on the album."
msgstr "Številka skladbe na albumu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4791
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Year</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Leto</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4794
#, no-c-format
msgid "The year in which the track or album was published."
msgstr "Leto, v katerem je bila skladba ali album objavljen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:4799
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Comment</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Komentar</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4802
#, no-c-format
msgid "A text comment for the track."
msgstr "Besedilni komentar za skladbo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4809
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Single Track"
msgstr "Uredi eno skladbo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4810
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this mode you can change all supported tags of the chosen file."
msgstr "V tem načinu lahko spremenite vse podprte oznake izbrane datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Several Tracks"
msgstr "Uredi več skladb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several tracks can be selected by clicking on the artist, album, or genre in "
"the your collection or by selecting several tracks in the playlist using the "
"&Ctrl; (non-sequential) or &Shift; (sequential) key."
msgstr ""
"Več skladb lahko izberete s klikom na izvajalca, album ali zvrst v vaši "
"zbirki ali z izbiro več skladb na seznamu predvajanja z &Ctrl; (nezaporedno) "
"ali &Shift; (zaporedni) ključ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4830
#, no-c-format
msgid "All At Once"
msgstr "Vse naenkrat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4831
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More general tags can be set for a group of tags at once. It works just like "
"the single-track-mode, but the title and track number tags are locked."
msgstr ""
"Bolj splošne oznake lahko nastavite za skupino oznak hkrati. Deluje tako kot "
"način z eno skladbo, vendar sta oznaki naslova in številke skladbe "
"zaklenjeni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4847
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track By Track"
msgstr "Track By Track"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode is pretty similar to the single-track-mode, except for the ability "
"to switch between the selected tracks using the <guilabel>Next</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Previous</guilabel> buttons. It is activated by clicking on "
"the checkbox <guilabel>Per Track</guilabel> on the bottom of the window."
msgstr ""
"Ta način je precej podoben načinu z eno skladbo, razen možnosti "
"preklapljanja med izbranimi skladbami z uporabo gumbov <guilabel>Naprej</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Prejšnja</guilabel>. Aktivira se s klikom na "
"potrditveno polje <guilabel>Na skladbo</guilabel> na dnu okna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Get Tags from MusicBrainz"
msgstr "Pridobite oznake od MusicBrainz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; 2.8 has the ability to guess tags from the <guilabel>MusicBrainz</"
"guilabel> database. Click the <guilabel>Get Tags from MusicBrainz</"
"guilabel>, wait a moment for the database to be searched for matches, and "
"then <guilabel>Update Tags</guilabel>, or <guilabel>Cancel</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; 2.8 ima možnost ugibanja oznak iz baze podatkov "
"<guilabel>MusicBrainz</guilabel>. Kliknite <guilabel>Pridobi oznake iz "
"MusicBrainz</guilabel>, počakajte trenutek, da se v zbirki podatkov poiščejo "
"ujemanja, nato pa <guilabel>Posodobi oznake</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Prekliči</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have the packages <emphasis>libofa</emphasis> and <emphasis>ffmpeg</"
"emphasis> installed, and &amarok; is compiled with them, "
"<guilabel>Musicbrainz</guilabel> will be able to use <quote>fingerprinting</"
"quote> (the <emphasis>MusicDNS</emphasis> service) to search for albums and "
"tracks without good filenames or existing tags."
msgstr ""
"Če imate nameščena paketa <emphasis>libofa</emphasis> in <emphasis>ffmpeg</"
"emphasis> ter &amarok; je sestavljen z njimi, bo <guilabel>Musicbrainz</"
"guilabel> lahko uporabljal <quote>prstne odtise</quote> (storitev "
"<emphasis>MusicDNS</emphasis>) za iskanje albumov in skladb brez dobrih imen "
"datotek ali obstoječih oznak ."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4878
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>MusicBrainz Tagger dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno MusicBrainz Tagger</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4881
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>MusicBrainz Tagger dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno za označevanje MusicBrainz</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Guess Tags From Filename"
msgstr "Ugani oznake iz imena datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also possible to tag tracks using information in the filename. This is "
"a very convenient feature when dealing with lots of files with a consistent "
"naming scheme."
msgstr ""
"Možno je tudi označiti skladbe z uporabo informacij v imenu datoteke. To je "
"zelo priročna funkcija, ko imate opravka z veliko datotekami z dosledno "
"shemo poimenovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some tracks need to be edited manually, because special characters like "
"single quotes are omitted in file names. A preview helps to create the "
"correct pattern."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere skladbe je treba urediti ročno, ker so v imenih datotek izpuščeni "
"posebni znaki, kot so enojni narekovaji. Predogled pomaga ustvariti pravilen "
"vzorec."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also several options to format the result. These are self-"
"explanatory."
msgstr "Obstaja tudi več možnosti za oblikovanje rezultata. Te so samoumevne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4909
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic"
msgstr "Osnovno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the basic view you get a drag-and-drop menu to create the pattern in the "
"filename."
msgstr ""
"V osnovnem pogledu dobite meni povleci in spusti za ustvarjanje vzorca v "
"imenu datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4926 index.docbook:4966 index.docbook:5361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Primer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4927 index.docbook:4967
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename: 01-The Beatles-Hey Jude.mp3"
msgstr "Ime datoteke: 01-The Beatles-Hey Jude.mp3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4929 index.docbook:4969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tracknumber: 01"
msgstr "Številka skladbe: 01"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4931 index.docbook:4971
#, no-c-format
msgid "Artist: The Beatles"
msgstr "Izvajalec: The Beatles"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4933 index.docbook:4973
#, no-c-format
msgid "Title: Hey Jude"
msgstr "Naslov: Hej Jude"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4949
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the advanced view you can create a pattern using markers in a string."
msgstr ""
"V naprednem pogledu lahko ustvarite vzorec z uporabo označevalcev v nizu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4991
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcoding"
msgstr "Prekodiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4992
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Transcoding</guilabel> allows you to encode media files to a "
"variety of formats while copying or moving them to a collection "
"(<guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel>, USB <guilabel>Universal Mass Storage "
"Collection</guilabel> and <guilabel>iPod, iPad &amp; iPhone Collection</"
"guilabel> support transcoding as of &amarok; 2.8). A word of warning: be "
"careful when you use this feature, as you are working with actual files on "
"your hard drive. Have a backup!"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prekodiranje</guilabel> vam omogoča kodiranje medijskih datotek v "
"različne formate, medtem ko jih kopirate ali premikate v zbirko "
"(<guilabel>Lokalna zbirka</guilabel>, USB <guilabel>Univerzalna zbirka "
"masovnega shranjevanja</guilabel> in <guilabel>Zbirka iPod, iPad &amp; "
"iPhone</guilabel> podpirata prekodiranje od &amarok; 2.8). Opozorilo: pri "
"uporabi te funkcije bodite previdni, saj delate z dejanskimi datotekami na "
"trdem disku. Imejte varnostno kopijo!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4994
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface"
msgstr "Vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Transcoding</emphasis> dialog will appear whenever you copy or "
"move tracks to one of the collections that support transcoding. You can also "
"transcode tracks within the <emphasis>Local Collection</emphasis> by using "
"the <guilabel>Organize files</guilabel> functionality."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <emphasis>Transkodiranje</emphasis> se bo prikazalo vsakič, "
"ko boste kopirali ali premaknili skladbe v eno od zbirk, ki podpirajo "
"transkodiranje. Skladbe znotraj <emphasis>Lokalne zbirke</emphasis> lahko "
"tudi prekodirate s funkcijo <guilabel>Organiziraj datoteke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4998
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcode Tracks Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Transcode Tracks"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4999
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose to copy or move files to a supported collection, the following "
"dialog will pop up:"
msgstr ""
"Če se odločite kopirati ali premakniti datoteke v podprto zbirko, se prikaže "
"naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5026
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopirati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selected media files will be copied to your collection without re-encoding."
msgstr ""
"Izbrane medijske datoteke bodo kopirane v vašo zbirko brez ponovnega "
"kodiranja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoder list"
msgstr "Seznam kodirnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5037
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"List of all your installed codecs; choose among them to be able to "
"transcode. If this list is empty, you need to install <emphasis>FFmpeg</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Seznam vseh nameščenih kodekov; izberite med njimi, da boste lahko "
"prekodirali. Če je ta seznam prazen, morate namestiti <emphasis>FFmpeg</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcode all tracks"
msgstr "Prekodiraj vse skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcode every selected track to the chosen codec"
msgstr "Prekodirajte vsako izbrano skladbo v izbrani kodek"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5050
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcode only when needed for playability"
msgstr "Prekodirajte le, ko je to potrebno za predvajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only transcode tracks which need to be transcoded to play in the destination "
"system"
msgstr ""
"Prekodirajte samo skladbe, ki jih je treba prekodirati za predvajanje v "
"ciljnem sistemu"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcode only if source and destination formats are different"
msgstr "Prekodiraj samo, če sta izvorni in ciljni format različna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5061
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcode only if source and destination file formats are different"
msgstr "Prekodiraj samo, če sta izvorni in ciljni format datoteke različni"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5066
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remember this choice for the next time"
msgstr "Zapomnite si to izbiro za naslednjič"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the preference for the <guilabel>current destination collection</"
"guilabel>. This includes the copy/transcode preference and transcoding "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"Shranite nastavitve za <guilabel>trenutno ciljno zbirko</guilabel>. To "
"vključuje nastavitve kopiranja/prekodiranja in parametre za prekodiranje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5074 index.docbook:5120 index.docbook:8391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5077 index.docbook:5123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exits the <guilabel>Transcode Tracks</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr "Zapre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Prekodiraj sledi</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5084
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Encoding"
msgstr "Kodiranje po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5085
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to save space, to make your files readable by a portable music "
"player or a particular software program, &amarok; can handle it. Choose a "
"codec from the list and a custom setting and click <guilabel>Transcode</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali želite prihraniti prostor, narediti vaše datoteke "
"berljive s prenosnim predvajalnikom glasbe ali določenim programom, &amarok; "
"lahko prenese. Izberite kodek s seznama in nastavitev po meri ter kliknite "
"<guilabel>Prekodiraj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transcode"
msgstr "Prekodiraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Begins encoding with the selected codecs and parameters. In case of the "
"<guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel> the <guilabel>Organize tracks</"
"guilabel> dialog will pop up. <link linkend=\"contents\">More about Organize "
"tracks</link>."
msgstr ""
"Začne kodiranje z izbranimi kodeki in parametri. V primeru <guilabel>Lokalne "
"zbirke</guilabel> se prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Organiziraj skladbe</"
"guilabel>. <link linkend=\"contents\">Več o Organiziranju skladb</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Transcoding Preferences"
msgstr "Shranjevanje nastavitev transkodiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned in the <guilabel>Remember this choice for the next time</"
"guilabel> description, &amarok; can remember transcoding preference per each "
"of your collections. The preference can be changed any time in the "
"<guilabel>Configure Local Collection</guilabel> <guilabel>Configure Amarok</"
"guilabel> dialog page for the <guilabel>Local Collection</guilabel> and in "
"the configure dialogs of <guilabel>iPod, iPad &amp; iPhone</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Universal Mass Storage</guilabel> collections."
msgstr ""
"Kot je omenjeno v opisu <guilabel>Zapomni si to izbiro za naslednjič</"
"guilabel>, &amarok; si lahko zapomni nastavitev prekodiranja za vsako od "
"vaših zbirk. Nastavitve lahko kadar koli spremenite v pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj lokalno zbirko</guilabel> <guilabel>Konfiguriraj "
"Amarok</guilabel> za <guilabel>Lokalno zbirko</guilabel> in v pogovornih "
"oknih za konfiguracijo <guilabel> iPod, iPad &amp; Zbirki iPhone</guilabel> "
"in <guilabel>Universal Mass Storage</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pro Tip: Strip Audio out of Video Files"
msgstr "Profesionalni nasvet: Odstranite zvok iz video datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok;'s transcoding capabilities can be used to extract audio from video "
"files while copying or moving them into a collection. Just select video "
"file(s) in Amarok embedded file browser, right-click and choose "
"<guilabel>Copy to Collection</guilabel>. Standard <guilabel>Transcode "
"Tracks</guilabel> dialog will appear. Choose one of the encoders, hit "
"<guilabel>Transcode</guilabel> and transcoding will begin."
msgstr ""
"Zmožnosti prekodiranja &amarok; lahko uporabite za pridobivanje zvoka iz "
"video datotek med kopiranjem ali premikanjem v zbirko. Preprosto izberite "
"video datoteko(e) v vdelanem brskalniku datotek Amarok, kliknite z desno "
"miškino tipko in izberite <guilabel>Kopiraj v zbirko</guilabel>. Odprlo se "
"bo standardno pogovorno okno <guilabel>Prekodiranje sledi</guilabel>. "
"Izberite enega od kodirnikov, pritisnite <guilabel>Transcode</guilabel> in "
"transkodiranje se bo začelo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Manager"
msgstr "Script Manager"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Script Manager</guilabel> contains the options required to "
"extend the functionality of &amarok; through custom scripts. It is reached "
"from the <guilabel>Settings</guilabel> menu, <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure "
"Amarok</guimenu><guimenuitem>Scripts</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Scripts can "
"be installed from downloaded script packages, or from the <guilabel>Manage "
"Scripts</guilabel> button which can fetch and install the latest user-"
"contributed scripts from the Internet."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Script Manager</guilabel> vsebuje možnosti, potrebne za razširitev "
"funkcionalnosti &amarok; prek skriptov po meri. Dosežete ga v meniju "
"<guilabel>Nastavitve</guilabel>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Skripte</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Skripte je mogoče "
"namestiti iz prenesenih paketov skriptov ali z gumbom <guilabel>Upravljanje "
"skriptov</guilabel>, ki lahko pridobi in namesti najnovejše skripte, ki jih "
"prispevajo uporabniki iz interneta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please refer to <link linkend=\"scripts\">Configuring Amarok -&gt; Scripts</"
"link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"scripts\">Konfiguriranje Amaroka -&gt; Skripte</link> "
"za več informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Playlist</emphasis> is a powerful part of &amarok;. One can "
"drag in some tracks, but there is a lot more available."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Seznam predvajanja</emphasis> je močan del &amarok;a. Nekatere "
"skladbe lahko vlečete, vendar je na voljo veliko več."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5163
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"saved-playlists\">Saved Playlists</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"saved-playlists\">Shranjeni seznami predvajanja</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5164
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"playlist-filtering\">Playlist Filtering</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"playlist-filtering\">Filtriranje seznama predvajanja</"
"link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5165
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"queue-manager\">Queue Manager</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"queue-manager\">Upravljalnik čakalnih vrst</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5166
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"dynamic-playlists\">Dynamic Playlists</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"dynamic-playlists\">Dinamični seznami predvajanja</"
"link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"automatic-playlist-generator\">Automatic Playlist Generator</"
"link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"automatic-playlist-generator\">Samodejni generator seznamov "
"predvajanja</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Saved Playlists</title>"
msgstr "<title>Shranjeni seznami predvajanja</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Saved playlist</emphasis> is a traditional type of playlist. Saved "
"playlists work like &amarok;'s current playlist, saved in the &amarok; "
"database or your file system for later use. It can be fun to use them at "
"events when you have specific songs you want played."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Shranjen seznam predvajanja</emphasis> je tradicionalna vrsta "
"seznama predvajanja. Shranjeni seznami predvajanja delujejo kot trenutni "
"seznam predvajanja &amarok;, shranjen v mapi &amarok; bazo podatkov ali vaš "
"datotečni sistem za kasnejšo uporabo. Lahko jih je zabavno uporabljati na "
"dogodkih, ko imate določene pesmi, ki jih želite predvajati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating a saved playlist is very easy with the exact songs and order that "
"you want. For every day use, sometimes it is faster to use <link linkend="
"\"dynamic-playlists\">Dynamic Playlists</link> or the <link linkend="
"\"automatic-playlist-generator\">Automatic Playlist Generator</link> when "
"you have less specific needs for specific tracks and progression."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje shranjenega seznama predvajanja je zelo enostavno z natančnimi "
"skladbami in vrstnim redom, ki ga želite. Za vsakodnevno uporabo je včasih "
"hitreje uporabiti <link linkend=\"dynamic-playlists\">Dinamične sezname "
"predvajanja</link> ali <link linkend=\"automatic-playlist-generator"
"\">Samodejni generator seznamov predvajanja</link>, ko imajo manj posebnih "
"potreb po določenih progah in napredovanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To browse and manage your saved playlists, go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlists</guimenu><guimenuitem>Saved Playlists</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Za brskanje in upravljanje shranjenih seznamov predvajanja pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seznami predvajanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shranjeni "
"seznami predvajanja</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing saved playlists"
msgstr "Upravljanje shranjenih seznamov predvajanja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving a Playlist"
msgstr "Shranjevanje seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can save your current playlist into the &amarok; database by clicking "
"the save icon (<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"document-save.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>) at "
"the bottom of the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> view. You can browse "
"playlists in the &amarok; database by going to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlists</guimenu><guimenuitem>Saved Playlists</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane and "
"expanding the <guilabel>Amarok database</guilabel> section. You will find "
"them in your filesystem here: <filename>~/.kde(4)/share/apps/amarok/"
"playlists</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Svoj trenutni seznam predvajanja lahko shranite v &amarok; zbirko podatkov "
"tako, da kliknete ikono za shranjevanje (<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-save.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>) na dnu <guilabel> Pogled seznama "
"predvajanja</guilabel>. Po seznamih predvajanja lahko brskate v aplikaciji "
"&amarok; zbirko podatkov tako, da obiščete <menuchoice><guimenu>Seznami "
"predvajanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shranjeni seznami predvajanja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel> in "
"razširite <guilabel>razdelek z zbirko podatkov Amarok</guilabel>. Našli jih "
"boste v svojem datotečnem sistemu tukaj: <filename>~/.kde(4)/share/apps/"
"amarok/playlists</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting a Playlist"
msgstr "Izvažanje seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can export your current playlist to your file system by clicking "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlist</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export Playlist As...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the top menubar. From the opening save "
"dialog, you can change the name, location and type of the playlist. Then "
"just click on <guilabel>Save</guilabel>. Remember, playlist files don't "
"contain any music data. If you want to listen the content of the playlist on "
"another computer, you'll need to bring your music with you unless that "
"computer already has the tracks."
msgstr ""
"Trenutni seznam predvajanja lahko izvozite v svoj datotečni sistem tako, da "
"kliknete <menuchoice><guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvozi seznam predvajanja kot ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> v zgornji menijski vrstici. V pogovornem oknu za shranjevanje, "
"ki se odpre, lahko spremenite ime, lokacijo in vrsto seznama predvajanja. "
"Nato kliknite <guilabel>Shrani</guilabel>. Ne pozabite, da datoteke s "
"seznami predvajanja ne vsebujejo glasbenih podatkov. Če želite poslušati "
"vsebino seznama predvajanja v drugem računalniku, boste morali prinesti "
"svojo glasbo s seboj, razen če ta računalnik že ima skladbe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing a Playlist"
msgstr "Uvažanje seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can import a playlist file into &amarok; just by copying it to any "
"directory that &amarok; knows as part of your music collection. When "
"&amarok; detects a new playlist on any folder of your collection, it will "
"add it to the <guilabel>Playlist Files on Disk</guilabel> section of "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlists</guimenu><guimenuitem>Saved Playlists</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane. If "
"the playlist doesn't appear right away, you can update the collection "
"manually by clicking <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Update "
"Collection</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If instead of importing the playlist, "
"you want to just listen it, open it with <menuchoice><guimenu>Amarok</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Play Media...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from menubar. "
"Selected playlist will be added to the current playlist."
msgstr ""
"Datoteko seznama predvajanja lahko uvozite v &amarok; samo tako, da ga "
"kopirate v kateri koli imenik, ki ga &amarok; pozna kot del vaše glasbene "
"zbirke. Ko &amarok; zazna nov seznam predvajanja v kateri koli mapi vaše "
"zbirke, ga bo dodal v razdelek <guilabel>Datoteke seznama predvajanja na "
"disku</guilabel> v <menuchoice><guimenu>Seznami predvajanja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shranjeni seznami predvajanja</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> v podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>. Če se seznam "
"predvajanja ne prikaže takoj, lahko zbirko posodobite ročno, tako da "
"kliknete <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi zbirko</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če namesto uvoza seznama predvajanja želite samo "
"poslušati, ga odprite z <menuchoice><guimenu>Amarok</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Play Media...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski "
"vrstici. Izbrani seznam predvajanja bo dodan trenutnemu seznamu predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist Filtering"
msgstr "Filtriranje seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Search playlist</emphasis> function in &amarok; is very "
"powerful, as it allows you to search for different tracks by various "
"constraints. The search results limits what you can actually see, which "
"makes it easy to queue up wanted tracks, or remove them from the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija <emphasis>Išči seznam predvajanja</emphasis> v &amarok; je zelo "
"zmogljiv, saj omogoča iskanje različnih skladb po različnih omejitvah. "
"Rezultati iskanja omejujejo tisto, kar lahko dejansko vidite, kar olajša "
"postavljanje želenih skladb v čakalno vrsto ali njihovo odstranjevanje s "
"seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you type something in the <guilabel>Search playlist</guilabel> field, "
"&amarok; will search in your playlist and mark matching tracks, artists and "
"so forth."
msgstr ""
"Ko nekaj vtipkate v polje <guilabel>Išči seznam predvajanja</guilabel>, "
"&amarok; bo poiskal na vašem seznamu predvajanja in označil ujemajoče se "
"skladbe, izvajalce ipd."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first track that matches the current search will be highlighted as in "
"this example:"
msgstr ""
"Prva skladba, ki se ujema s trenutnim iskanjem, bo označena kot v tem "
"primeru:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Preferences"
msgstr "Nastavitve iskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a small drop down menu with options for the search field, if you "
"need more than simple search. You can choose which types of searching you "
"want to use in your <guilabel>Search playlist</guilabel>. Check the boxes "
"according to what you need for your search."
msgstr ""
"To je majhen spustni meni z možnostmi za iskalno polje, če potrebujete več "
"kot preprosto iskanje. Izberete lahko, katere vrste iskanja želite uporabiti "
"na vašem <guilabel>Seznamu predvajanja iskanja</guilabel>. Označite polja "
"glede na to, kaj potrebujete za iskanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check boxes"
msgstr "Potrditvena polja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tracks"
msgstr "Skladbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5273
#, no-c-format
msgid "&amarok; will search for text from tag: Track Titles"
msgstr "&amarok; bo iskal besedilo iz oznake: Naslovi skladb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search for text from tag: Album titles"
msgstr "Iskanje besedila iz oznake: Naslovi albumov"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Artists"
msgstr "Umetniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search for text from tag: Artist"
msgstr "Iskanje besedila iz oznake: umetnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search for text from tag: Genre"
msgstr "Iskanje besedila iz oznake: žanr"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Composers"
msgstr "Skladatelji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search for text from tag: Composer"
msgstr "Iskanje besedila iz oznake: Skladatelj"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5310
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Rating</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Ocena</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search the rating of all songs in your playlist"
msgstr "Poiščite oceno vseh skladb na vašem seznamu predvajanja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Years"
msgstr "Leta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search for year of publication"
msgstr "Poiščite leto izdaje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show only matches"
msgstr "Pokaži samo ujemanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this box is marked &amarok; will display only the tracks that match the "
"current search"
msgstr ""
"Ko je to polje označeno z &amarok; bo prikazal samo skladbe, ki ustrezajo "
"trenutnemu iskanju"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show only matches - example"
msgstr "Pokaži samo ujemanja - primer"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Queue Manager"
msgstr "Upravljalnik čakalne vrste"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tracks are loaded in the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel>. In normal track "
"progression, when a song is over, the next one played is the one below the "
"just-played one. The <emphasis>Queue</emphasis> is one way to change the "
"order in which the songs are played."
msgstr ""
"Skladbe se naložijo na <guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel>. Pri "
"običajnem napredovanju skladbe, ko je skladba končana, je naslednja "
"predvajana tista pod pravkar predvajano. <emphasis>Čakalna vrsta</emphasis> "
"je eden od načinov za spreminjanje vrstnega reda predvajanja skladb."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5356
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Create a Queue"
msgstr "Kako ustvariti čakalno vrsto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is very easy to make a Queue; just select one or more tracks and move in "
"the center of &amarok;, to the <emphasis>Pop-Up Dropper</emphasis> (PUD), or "
"right-click and scroll to <guilabel>Queue Track</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Čakalno vrsto je zelo enostavno narediti; samo izberite eno ali več skladb "
"in se pomaknite v sredino &amarok;a do <emphasis>Pojavne kapalke</emphasis> "
"(PUD) ali kliknite z desno miškino tipko in se pomaknite do "
"<guilabel>Skladba v čakalni vrsti</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you select or add songs to the Queue each of them takes a number. The "
"number indicates the order in which songs will play."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete ali dodate skladbe v čakalno vrsto, vsaka od njih dobi številko. "
"Številka označuje vrstni red predvajanja pesmi."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5370
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>First, select the track</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Najprej izberite skladbo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5373
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>First, select the track</para>"
msgstr "<para>Najprej izberite skladbo</para>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Then right-click for context menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nato z desno miškino tipko kliknite kontekstni meni</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5389
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Then right-click for context menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Nato z desno tipko miške kliknite kontekstni meni</para>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5402
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Or queue track by dragging to the PUD</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Ali pa sled postavite v čakalno vrsto tako, da povlečete na PUD</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5405
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Or queue track by dragging to the PUD</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Ali sled postavite v čakalno vrsto tako, da povlečete na PUD</para>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5418
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Queued tracks in playlist</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skladbe v čakalni vrsti na seznamu predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Queued tracks in playlist</para>"
msgstr "<para>Skladbe v čakalni vrsti na seznamu predvajanja</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5428
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Edit the Queue"
msgstr "Kako urediti čakalno vrsto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to make any changes in the <emphasis>Queue</emphasis> you can "
"use the <guilabel>Queue Editor</guilabel>. Start the <guilabel>Queue Editor</"
"guilabel> from the menu in <menuchoice><guimenu>Playlist</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Queue</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite narediti kakršne koli spremembe v <emphasis>Čakalni vrsti</"
"emphasis>, lahko uporabite <guilabel>Urejevalnik čakalnih vrst</guilabel>. "
"Zaženite <guilabel>Urejevalnik čakalne vrste</guilabel> iz menija v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlist</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uredi čakalno vrsto</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Queue Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik čakalne vrste"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:5450 index.docbook:8344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button"
msgstr "Gumb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected track ahead in the list."
msgstr "Premakni izbrano skladbo naprej na seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected track below in the list."
msgstr "Premakni izbrano skladbo spodaj na seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove selected song from the Queue."
msgstr "Odstrani izbrano skladbo iz čakalne vrste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove all songs from the Queue."
msgstr "Odstranite vse pesmi iz čakalne vrste."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5493
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Dynamic Playlists</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dinamični seznami predvajanja</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some media players are designed to load the entire collection of music in a "
"single playlist, then play it in random order, or search/ sorted, then "
"queued. With a larger collection, this way of managing your playlist isn't "
"efficient. &amarok;'s <guilabel>Dynamic Playlist</guilabel> is a better way "
"to explore your music."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri multimedijski predvajalniki so zasnovani tako, da naložijo celotno "
"zbirko glasbe na en seznam predvajanja, jo nato predvajajo v naključnem "
"vrstnem redu ali iščejo/razvrstijo in nato postavijo v čakalno vrsto. Pri "
"večji zbirki ta način upravljanja seznama predvajanja ni učinkovit. &amarok;"
"ov <guilabel>dinamični seznam predvajanja</guilabel> je boljši način za "
"raziskovanje vaše glasbe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Dynamic Playlist</guilabel> is reached from "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Playlists</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dynamic Playlists</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane."
msgstr ""
"Do <guilabel>Dinamičnega seznama predvajanja</guilabel> pridete iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seznami predvajanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dinamični "
"seznami predvajanja</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v podoknu <guilabel>Medijski "
"viri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5511
#, no-c-format
msgid "How the Dynamic Playlist works"
msgstr "Kako deluje dinamični seznam predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dynamic playlist is a list that grows while you listen to your music."
msgstr ""
"Dinamični seznam predvajanja je seznam, ki raste med poslušanjem glasbe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It will keep a certain number of songs in front of the currently played song "
"and it will clean up the playlist by removing old songs."
msgstr ""
"Obdržal bo določeno število pesmi pred trenutno predvajano skladbo in "
"počistil seznam predvajanja tako, da bo odstranil stare pesmi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The songs that will be added to the front of the playlist are determined by "
"the currently selected dynamic playlist."
msgstr ""
"Pesmi, ki bodo dodane na začetek seznama predvajanja, določa trenutno izbran "
"dinamični seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5519
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using a Dynamic Playlist"
msgstr "Uporaba dinamičnega seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable dynamic playlists, click the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-action-dynamic-amarok.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the <guilabel>Dynamic Playlist</"
"guilabel> pane. A bar will be displayed at the top of the "
"<guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane announcing that it is enabled. Select "
"which dynamic playlist to use from the list of options by double clicking "
"it. The currently selected dynamic playlist is bolded."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti dinamične sezname predvajanja, kliknite gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-action-dynamic-"
"amarok.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v "
"<guilabel>Dynamic Podokno seznama predvajanja</guilabel>. Na vrhu podokna "
"<guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel> bo prikazana vrstica, ki oznanja, da "
"je omogočen. Na seznamu možnosti izberite, kateri dinamični seznam "
"predvajanja želite uporabiti, tako da ga dvakrat kliknete. Trenutno izbran "
"dinamični seznam predvajanja je krepko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can adjust the number of songs before and after the currently playing "
"song to be displayed in the playlist with the <guilabel>Previous</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Upcoming</guilabel> fields. You can prevent the same track "
"appearing in the current playlist more than once using the "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-copy.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button. The "
"<guilabel>Repopulate</guilabel> button allows you to generate a new set of "
"tracks. This can be used together with a high <guilabel>Upcoming</guilabel> "
"setting to generate fixed playlists for export."
msgstr ""
"S polji <guilabel>Prejšnje</guilabel> in <guilabel>Prihodnje</guilabel> "
"lahko prilagodite število skladb pred in za trenutno predvajano skladbo, ki "
"bodo prikazane na seznamu predvajanja. Z <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> lahko preprečite, da bi se ista skladba večkrat pojavila "
"na trenutnem seznamu predvajanja. gumb. Gumb <guilabel>Znova zapolni</"
"guilabel> vam omogoča ustvarjanje novega nabora skladb. To lahko uporabite "
"skupaj z visoko nastavitvijo <guilabel>Prihodnje</guilabel> za ustvarjanje "
"fiksnih seznamov predvajanja za izvoz."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5525
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining Dynamic Playlists"
msgstr "Definiranje dinamičnih seznamov predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each dynamic playlist is built of biases. A bias defines a particular "
"constraint on the behaviour of the dynamic playlist, and new items to be "
"added to the playlist are selected at random from a list of all songs which "
"match the biases. Biases may either be a single bias (&eg; the "
"<emphasis>Search</emphasis> bias) or a grouping of other biases (&eg; the "
"<emphasis>Match All</emphasis> bias). Some examples playlists are included, "
"and you can define a new playlist with the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> "
"</inlinemediaobject> button."
msgstr ""
"Vsak dinamični seznam predvajanja je sestavljen iz pristranskosti. "
"Pristranskost določa posebno omejitev glede obnašanja dinamičnega seznama "
"predvajanja, novi elementi, ki se dodajo na seznam predvajanja, pa so "
"naključno izbrani s seznama vseh pesmi, ki se ujemajo s pristranskostmi. "
"Pristranskosti so lahko ena sama pristranskost (&eg; pristranskost "
"<emphasis>Iskanje</emphasis>) ali skupina drugih pristranskosti (&eg; "
"pristranskost <emphasis>Ujemanje vseh</emphasis>). Vključenih je nekaj "
"primerov seznamov predvajanja, nov seznam predvajanja pa lahko določite z "
"gumbom <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-"
"new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name of a playlist, either use the <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-properties.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button or right click on it "
"and select <guilabel>Rename playlist</guilabel>. A bias can be edited with "
"the same button or by right-clicking and selecting <guilabel>Edit bias</"
"guilabel>, and for biases which have sub-biases, a new sub-bias can be added "
"by right clicking and selecting <guilabel>Add new bias</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti ime seznama predvajanja, uporabite gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-"
"properties.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> ali z "
"desnim klikom na in izberite <guilabel>Preimenuj seznam predvajanja</"
"guilabel>. Pristranskost lahko uredite z istim gumbom ali z desnim klikom in "
"izbiro <guilabel>Uredi pristranskost</guilabel>, za pristranskosti, ki imajo "
"podpristranskosti, pa lahko dodate novo podpristranskost z desnim klikom in "
"izbiro <guilabel >Dodaj novo pristranskost</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Biases"
msgstr "Pristranskosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because multiple biases may be defined, &amarok; may at times return an "
"empty playlist. This occurs if it is given a set of impossible-to-fulfill "
"conditions. To avoid this and to better understand each available bias, "
"along with any options it takes, please see below:"
msgstr ""
"Ker je lahko definiranih več pristranskosti, &amarok; lahko včasih vrne "
"prazen seznam predvajanja. To se zgodi, če je podan niz pogojev, ki jih ni "
"mogoče izpolniti. Da bi se temu izognili in bolje razumeli vsako "
"razpoložljivo pristranskost, skupaj z morebitnimi možnostmi, si oglejte "
"spodaj:"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis role=\"bold\">Search</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis role=\"bold\">Iskanje</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bias matches tracks found by a given search query. It uses the same "
"search string used in the collection browser. You may also use the "
"<guilabel>Match meta tag</guilabel> bias to match tags in the same way as "
"the collection search editor."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost se ujema s skladbami, ki jih najde določena iskalna "
"poizvedba. Uporablja enak iskalni niz kot v brskalniku zbirke. Uporabite "
"lahko tudi pristranskost <guilabel>Match meta tag</guilabel> za ujemanje "
"oznak na enak način kot urejevalnik iskanja po zbirkah."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5539
#, no-c-format
msgid "Random"
msgstr "Naključen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5541
#, no-c-format
msgid "This bias matches any track, entirely at random."
msgstr "Ta pristranskost se ujema s katero koli skladbo, povsem naključno."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5544
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>And</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>In</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group bias matches tracks which match <emphasis>all</emphasis> sub-"
"biases."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost skupine se ujema s skladbami, ki se ujemajo z "
"<emphasis>vsemi</emphasis> podpristranskostmi."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5549
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Or</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>Ali</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group bias matches tracks which match <emphasis>any</emphasis> sub-"
"biases."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost skupine se ujema s skladbami, ki se ujemajo s "
"<emphasis>poljubnimi</emphasis> podpristranskostmi."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Partition"
msgstr "Particija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group bias matches tracks from the sub-biases in proportion. The edit "
"window for this bias has sliders for each sub-bias to adjust the "
"proportions. For example, with two sub-biases with their proportion sliders "
"set equal, half of the playlist will match one bias and half the other."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost skupine sorazmerno ujema skladbe iz pod-pristranskosti. "
"Okno za urejanje tega pristranskosti ima drsnike za vsako podpristranskost "
"za prilagoditev razmerij. Na primer, z dvema podnaklonoma z enakima "
"nastavljenima drsnikoma za razmerje se bo polovica seznama predvajanja "
"ujemala z enim nagibom in polovica z drugim."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: The dynamic playlist is internally working with more tracks than you "
"can see, so after clicking <quote>Repopulate</quote> the list might not "
"contain a 50:50 distribution of songs. However as you continue listening to "
"music you will see that in the end it actually matches."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: Dinamični seznam predvajanja interno deluje z več skladbami, kot jih "
"lahko vidite, zato po kliku <quote>Ponovno zapolni</quote> seznam morda ne "
"bo vseboval porazdelitve skladb 50:50. Toda ko nadaljujete s poslušanjem "
"glasbe, boste videli, da se na koncu dejansko ujema."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5560
#, no-c-format
msgid "If Else"
msgstr "Če potem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group bias matches tracks from the first sub bias <emphasis>unless</"
"emphasis> there are no matching tracks found, in which case it matches "
"tracks from the second sub-bias. See the example <guilabel>Album Play</"
"guilabel> playlist for an example of this in use."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost skupine se ujema s skladbami iz prvega podpristranskosti, "
"<emphasis>razen če</emphasis> ni najdenih ujemajočih se sledi, v tem primeru "
"se ujema s skladbami iz drugega podpristranskosti. Oglejte si primer seznama "
"predvajanja <guilabel>Album Play</guilabel> za primer uporabe tega."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match Meta Tag"
msgstr "Ujemanje meta oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bias matches tracks which meet certain conditions on a tag. The "
"selection interface is the same as the search filter editor in the "
"collection browser. Select a tag type from the drop-down and fill in the "
"constraint. (Hint: You can use a number of these in an <guilabel>And</"
"guilabel> bias.)"
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost se ujema s skladbami, ki izpolnjujejo določene pogoje na "
"oznaki. Izbirni vmesnik je enak urejevalniku iskalnega filtra v brskalniku "
"zbirke. V spustnem meniju izberite vrsto oznake in izpolnite omejitev. "
"(Namig: več teh lahko uporabite v pristranskosti <guilabel>In</guilabel>.)"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Album Play"
msgstr "Predvajanje albuma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bias matches tracks related to the previous item in the playlist by "
"album. You can select the details of the bias from the drop-down menu. For "
"example, <guilabel>Track directly follows previous track in album</guilabel> "
"is used in the example <guilabel>Album Play</guilabel> playlist to ensure "
"full albums are played in order."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost ujema skladbe, povezane s prejšnjim elementom na seznamu "
"predvajanja po albumu. V spustnem meniju lahko izberete podrobnosti "
"pristranskosti. Na primer, <guilabel>Skladba neposredno sledi prejšnji "
"skladbi v albumu</guilabel> se uporablja na vzorčnem seznamu predvajanja "
"<guilabel>Predvajanje albuma</guilabel>, da se zagotovi predvajanje celotnih "
"albumov po vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5575
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quiz Play"
msgstr "Igra kviza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bias matches tracks for which the first character of a given tag "
"(title, artist or album) is the same as the last character of the same tag "
"for the previous tag. For example, with artist selected, you could have the "
"following series: Led Zeppeli<guilabel>n</guilabel> -&gt; <guilabel>N</"
"guilabel>ine Inch Nail<guilabel>s</guilabel> -&gt; <guilabel>S</"
"guilabel>antana, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost se ujema s skladbami, pri katerih je prvi znak dane oznake "
"(naslov, izvajalec ali album) enak zadnjemu znaku iste oznake za prejšnjo "
"oznako. Na primer, z izbranim izvajalcem bi lahko imeli naslednjo serijo: "
"Led Zeppeli<guilabel>n</guilabel> -&gt; <guilabel>N</guilabel>palčni "
"žeblji<guilabel>s</guilabel> -&gt; <guilabel>S</guilabel>antana, &etc;"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5580
#, no-c-format
msgid "EchoNest similar artist"
msgstr "EchoNest podoben umetnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bias matches tracks which are similar according to EchoNest, either to "
"the previous track or to any track in the playlist. This allows you to play "
"a set of consistent tracks simply by adding a single track to the playlist "
"and turning on the dynamic playlist, rather than defining all the match "
"rules yourself."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost se ujema s skladbami, ki so glede na EchoNest podobne "
"prejšnji skladbi ali kateri koli skladbi na seznamu predvajanja. To vam "
"omogoča predvajanje nabora doslednih skladb preprosto tako, da dodate eno "
"skladbo na seznam predvajanja in vklopite dinamični seznam predvajanja, "
"namesto da sami definirate vsa pravila ujemanja."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last.fm similar"
msgstr "Last.fm podobno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bias performs the same function as the EchoNest bias, but uses Last.fm "
"to determine similarity. You can also choose similarity to the previous "
"track or to the previous artist."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost opravlja isto funkcijo kot pristranskost EchoNest, vendar "
"za določanje podobnosti uporablja Last.fm. Izberete lahko tudi podobnost s "
"prejšnjo skladbo ali s prejšnjim izvajalcem."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:5590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last.fm weekly top artist"
msgstr "Najboljši tedenski izvajalec Last.fm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bias matches tracks which are on the weekly charts from Last.fm for a "
"given time period."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristranskost se ujema s skladbami, ki so na tedenskih lestvicah Last.fm "
"za dano časovno obdobje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5598 index.docbook:5621
#, no-c-format
msgid "A dynamic playlist in use"
msgstr "V uporabi je dinamičen seznam predvajanja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using your Dynamic Playlist"
msgstr "Uporaba vašega dinamičnega seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable the dynamic playlist you have created simply check the "
"<guilabel>On</guilabel> box in the upper-left corner of the pane. To "
"regenerate the entire playlist at any time, click <guilabel>Repopulate</"
"guilabel>, to the right of <guilabel>On</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti dinamični seznam predvajanja, ki ste ga ustvarili, "
"preprosto potrdite polje <guilabel>Vklopljeno</guilabel> v zgornjem levem "
"kotu podokna. Če želite kadar koli ponovno ustvariti celoten seznam "
"predvajanja, kliknite <guilabel>Znova zapolni</guilabel>, desno od "
"<guilabel>Vklopljeno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default number of items in the playlist is your 5 previous plays plus 10 "
"upcoming items. With the currently playing track, this makes 16 items in the "
"playlist at any given time. The number of tracks can be changed right below "
"the <guilabel>On</guilabel> checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto število elementov na seznamu predvajanja je vaših 5 prejšnjih "
"predvajanj in 10 prihajajočih elementov. S skladbo, ki se trenutno predvaja, "
"je to v vsakem trenutku 16 elementov na seznamu predvajanja. Število skladb "
"lahko spremenite tik pod potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Vklopljeno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below that is the dropdown menu for loading saved playlists, the "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-save.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button to save "
"playlists, and the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button to delete them."
msgstr ""
"Pod tem je spustni meni za nalaganje shranjenih seznamov predvajanja, gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-save.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> za shranjevanje "
"seznamov predvajanja in gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>, da jih izbrišete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Playlist Generator"
msgstr "Samodejni generator seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Automated Playlist Generator (APG)</guilabel> automatically "
"generates playlists based on constraints you set. These constraints can be "
"set based on song data (artist, genre, year) or access time (last played). "
"There are also special constraints to determine how &amarok; is going to "
"look for songs. You will find the <emphasis>APG</emphasis> in your "
"<guilabel>Media Sources</guilabel> pane, <menuchoice><guimenu>Playlists</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Automated Playlist Generator</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samodejni generator seznamov predvajanja (APG)</guilabel> "
"samodejno ustvari sezname predvajanja na podlagi omejitev, ki jih nastavite. "
"Te omejitve je mogoče nastaviti na podlagi podatkov o pesmi (izvajalec, "
"zvrst, leto) ali časa dostopa (zadnje predvajano). Obstajajo tudi posebne "
"omejitve za določanje, kako &amarok; bo iskal pesmi. <emphasis>APG</"
"emphasis> boste našli v podoknu <guilabel>Medijski viri</guilabel>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seznami predvajanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Samodejni "
"generator seznamov predvajanja</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5640
#, no-c-format
msgid "APG Presets Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica za prednastavitve APG"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the <guilabel>APG Presets</guilabel> toolbar. From left to right we "
"have the following buttons:"
msgstr ""
"To je orodna vrstica <guilabel>Prednastavitve APG</guilabel>. Od leve proti "
"desni imamo naslednje gumbe:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5657
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adds a blank preset that can be modified."
msgstr "Doda prazno prednastavitev, ki jo je mogoče spreminjati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens up the <guilabel>APG Preset Editor</guilabel> window to edit the "
"currently selected preset constraints."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno <guilabel>APG Preset Editor</guilabel> za urejanje trenutno "
"izbranih prednastavljenih omejitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the selected preset from the list; can <emphasis>not</emphasis> be "
"undone."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani izbrano prednastavitev s seznama; <emphasis>ni</emphasis> mogoče "
"razveljaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import a preset from a .xml file. Has the potential to be malformed if "
"edited outside &amarok;; use the constraint tester."
msgstr ""
"Uvozi prednastavitev iz datoteke .xml. Lahko se pokvari, če ga urejate zunaj "
"&amarok;; uporabite tester omejitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5661
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export the selected preset to a .xml file that can be imported."
msgstr ""
"Izvozite izbrano prednastavitev v datoteko .xml, ki jo je mogoče uvoziti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Loads <guilabel>APG</guilabel> with the selected preset and automatically "
"generates a playlist."
msgstr ""
"Naloži <guilabel>APG</guilabel> z izbrano prednastavitvijo in samodejno "
"ustvari seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5665
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Presets"
msgstr "Delo s prednastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5674
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>APG Preset Editor window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Okno urejevalnika prednastavitev APG</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5677
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>APG Preset Editor window</para>"
msgstr "<para>Okno urejevalnika prednastavitev APG</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Presets are sets of rules that &amarok; <guilabel>APG</guilabel> will use "
"when generating playlists. These rules are going to be referred to as "
"<emphasis>constraints</emphasis> from now on; every preset is determined by "
"the constraints which create it. Groups of constraints hierarchically and "
"logically organized are called constraint trees."
msgstr ""
"Prednastavitve so nizi pravil, ki jih &amarok; <guilabel>APG</guilabel> bo "
"uporabil pri ustvarjanju seznamov predvajanja. Ta pravila bodo od zdaj "
"naprej imenovana <emphasis>omejitve</emphasis>; vsaka prednastavitev je "
"določena z omejitvami, ki jo ustvarjajo. Skupine omejitev, ki so hierarhično "
"in logično organizirane, se imenujejo drevesa omejitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5684
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraints"
msgstr "Omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Constraints are the building blocks of constraint trees. They are simple "
"statements that the <guilabel>APG</guilabel> will use to add songs to the "
"playlist it generates. To add a constraint to the currently selected preset "
"constraint tree click the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-document-properties.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button in the <guilabel>APG Preset toolbar</guilabel> and "
"click the <guilabel>Add new</guilabel> option on the <guilabel>APG Preset "
"Editor</guilabel> window. Note that this will add the constraint under the "
"selected item (constraint or constraint group)."
msgstr ""
"Omejitve so gradniki dreves omejitev. So preprosti stavki, ki jih bo "
"<guilabel>APG</guilabel> uporabil za dodajanje pesmi na seznam predvajanja, "
"ki ga ustvari. Če želite dodati omejitev v trenutno izbrano prednastavljeno "
"drevo omejitev, kliknite gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-document-properties.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> v <guilabel>Orodna vrstica prednastavitev APG</guilabel> "
"in kliknite možnost <guilabel>Dodaj novo</guilabel> v oknu "
"<guilabel>Urejevalnik prednastavitev APG</guilabel>. Upoštevajte, da boste s "
"tem dodali omejitev pod izbrano postavko (omejitev ali skupina omejitev)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many different kinds of constraints can be added; each works in a different "
"way inside the tree."
msgstr ""
"Doda se lahko veliko različnih vrst omejitev; vsak znotraj drevesa deluje na "
"drugačen način."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint Types"
msgstr "Vrste omejitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; <guilabel>APG</guilabel> supports several types of constraints:"
msgstr "&amarok; <guilabel>APG</guilabel> podpira več vrst omejitev:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:5698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint"
msgstr "Omejitev"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5705
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match Tags"
msgstr "Oznake ujemanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most important constraints, because they can be set to virtually any "
"information regarding the file, including: artist name, album name, genre, "
"year, last played, and score."
msgstr ""
"Najpomembnejše omejitve, saj jih je mogoče nastaviti na skoraj vse "
"informacije o datoteki, vključno z: imenom izvajalca, imenom albuma, žanrom, "
"letom, zadnjim predvajanjem in rezultatom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5713
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist Duration"
msgstr "Trajanje seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the running time (in HH:MM:SS format) that the playlist should have"
msgstr ""
"Nastavite čas predvajanja (v obliki HH:MM:SS), ki naj bi ga imel seznam "
"predvajanja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist Length"
msgstr "Dolžina seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Determine how many songs should be in the playlist"
msgstr "Določite, koliko pesmi naj bo na seznamu predvajanja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5729
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checkpoint"
msgstr "Kontrolna točka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tell &amarok; where to start and stop looking for tracks"
msgstr "Povej &amarok;u kje začeti in nehati iskati sledi"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:5737
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prevent Duplicates"
msgstr "Preprečite dvojnike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prevent &amarok; from selecting the same tracks, songs from the same artist, "
"or the same album"
msgstr ""
"Prepreči &amarok; od izbire istih skladb, skladb istega izvajalca ali istega "
"albuma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you can change how constraints work in various manners, such as "
"setting the fuzzy-exact slider, which determines how closely the constraint "
"is going to be followed."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko način delovanja omejitev spremenite na različne "
"načine, na primer z nastavitvijo mehkega natančnega drsnika, ki določa, kako "
"natančno se bo upoštevala omejitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way to modify constraints that is present on <guilabel>Match Tags</"
"guilabel> with a textbased tag is found in the line below the "
"<guilabel>Field</guilabel> option box. In the text field to the right you "
"write the text to be matched and in the option box at the left of the value "
"you can select <guilabel>contains</guilabel> (which will consider any songs "
"that have the according text in their tag), <guilabel>matches</guilabel> "
"(which will consider songs whose corresponding tag match exactly the one in "
"the text box), <guilabel>starts with</guilabel> and <guilabel>ends with</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Drug način za spreminjanje omejitev, ki so prisotne na <guilabel>Ujemanje "
"oznak</guilabel> z besedilno oznako, najdete v vrstici pod poljem možnosti "
"<guilabel>Polje</guilabel>. V polje z besedilom na desni vpišete besedilo, "
"ki ga želite ujemati, in v polju z možnostmi na levi strani vrednosti lahko "
"izberete <guilabel>vsebuje</guilabel> (kar bo upoštevalo vse pesmi, ki imajo "
"v oznaki ustrezno besedilo ), <guilabel>ujema se</guilabel> (ki upošteva "
"pesmi, katerih ustrezna oznaka se natančno ujema s tisto v besedilnem "
"polju), <guilabel>se začne z</guilabel> in <guilabel>konča z</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, you can also edit the way value-based constraints (such as the "
"<guilabel>Playlist Length</guilabel> constraints and the playcount "
"<guilabel>Match Tag</guilabel> constraint) behave by changing the option "
"close to the text to settings such as <guilabel>fewer than</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>equals</guilabel> and <guilabel>more than</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Podobno lahko uredite tudi način obnašanja omejitev na podlagi vrednosti "
"(kot so omejitve <guilabel>Dolžina seznama predvajanja</guilabel> in "
"omejitev števila predvajanj <guilabel>Ujemanje oznake</guilabel>), tako da "
"spremenite možnost blizu besedila na nastavitve, kot so <guilabel>manj kot</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>je enako</guilabel> in <guilabel>več kot</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way to change constraint behavior is to check the <guilabel>invert</"
"guilabel> checkbox on them, this makes them behave the opposite way, a "
"<quote>Match Tag: artist contains <replaceable>name</replaceable></quote> "
"becomes <quote>Match Tag: artist not contains <replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Drug način za spremembo obnašanja omejitev je, da označite potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Invert</guilabel> na njih, zaradi česar se obnašajo nasprotno, "
"<quote>Oznaka za ujemanje: umetnik vsebuje <replaceable>ime</replaceable></"
"quote > postane <quote>Oznaka za ujemanje: izvajalec ne vsebuje "
"<replaceable>ime</replaceable></quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5755
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint Groups"
msgstr "Skupine omejitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Constraint groups can be added from the <guilabel>Add new</guilabel> option "
"from the <guilabel>APG Preset Editor</guilabel> window, constraints under a "
"group are logically linked, the same applies to groups under groups."
msgstr ""
"Skupine omejitev lahko dodate z možnostjo <guilabel>Dodaj novo</guilabel> v "
"oknu <guilabel>Urejevalnik prednastavitev APG</guilabel>, omejitve pod "
"skupino so logično povezane, enako velja za skupine pod skupinami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are currently two kinds of constraint groups: <quote>Match all</quote> "
"groups and <quote>Match any</quote> groups. <quote>Match all</quote> groups "
"require that all the constraints under them are met by the song. "
"<quote>Match any</quote> groups require that at least one of the constraints "
"under them are met by the song. To add a constraint under a specific group "
"highlight it on the preset editor and use the <guilabel>Add new</guilabel> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno obstajata dve vrsti omejitvenih skupin: skupine <quote>Ujemanje z "
"vsemi</quote> in skupine <quote>Ujemanje s katero koli</quote>. Skupine "
"<quote>Match all</quote> zahtevajo, da skladba izpolnjuje vse omejitve pod "
"njimi. Skupine <quote>Match any</quote> zahtevajo, da skladba izpolnjuje "
"vsaj eno od omejitev pod njimi. Če želite dodati omejitev pod določeno "
"skupino, jo označite v urejevalniku prednastavitev in uporabite možnost "
"<guilabel>Dodaj novo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using your Presets"
msgstr "Uporaba vaših prednastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you set up a preset, you just have to select it on the <guilabel>APG "
"Presets</guilabel> panel in the <guilabel>Automated Playlist Generator "
"(APG)</guilabel> and click <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-go-next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> the toolbar to run <guilabel>APG</guilabel> with the "
"selected preset. You will then have a playlist matching your criteria, like "
"this:"
msgstr ""
"Ko nastavite prednastavitev, jo morate samo izbrati na plošči "
"<guilabel>Prednastavitve APG</guilabel> v <guilabel>Automated Playlist "
"Generator (APG)</guilabel> in klikniti <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> orodno vrstico za zagon <guilabel>APG</guilabel> z "
"izbrano prednastavitvijo. Nato boste imeli seznam predvajanja, ki ustreza "
"vašim merilom, kot je ta:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist generated by the constraint tree below.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Seznam predvajanja, ustvarjen s spodnjim drevesom omejitev.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5776
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Playlist generated by the constraint tree below.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Seznam predvajanja, ustvarjen s spodnjim drevesom omejitev.</para>"

