#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5812
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Moodbar"
msgstr "Vrstica razpoloženja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Moodbar</emphasis> shows you the <quote>mood</quote> of a "
"track, which you can then use to figure out when something interesting "
"happens in the song."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Vrstica razpoloženja</emphasis> vam pokaže <quote>razpoloženje</"
"quote> skladbe, ki jo lahko uporabite, da ugotovite, kdaj se v pesmi zgodi "
"kaj zanimivega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order for &amarok; to display moodbars for your music, you will need the "
"<guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> program (see below for <link linkend=\"source-"
"downloads\">downloads</link> and binary packages)."
msgstr ""
"Da bi &amarok; za prikaz vrstic razpoloženja za vašo glasbo boste "
"potrebovali program <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> (glejte spodaj za <link "
"linkend=\"source-downloads\">prenose</link> in binarne pakete)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> package requires <guilabel>GStreamer</"
"guilabel> and various plugins depending on the filetypes you use (see <link "
"linkend=\"supported-filetypes\">Supported filetypes</link>). You will "
"<emphasis>not</emphasis> need the phonon-backend-gstreamer package to "
"create .mood files."
msgstr ""
"Paket <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> zahteva <guilabel>GStreamer</guilabel> in "
"različne vtičnike, odvisno od vrst datotek, ki jih uporabljate (glejte <link "
"linkend=\"supported-filetypes\">Podprte vrste datotek</link>). Za "
"ustvarjanje datotek .mood <emphasis>ne</emphasis> boste potrebovali paketa "
"phonon-backend-gstreamer."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two parts to the new <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> implementation: "
"the <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> package, which contains a program that "
"takes a music file and generates a .mood file, and support code in the "
"&amarok; source, which runs the binary and displays the Moodbar. The "
"<guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> package depends on the <emphasis>GStreamer</"
"emphasis> libraries. Without the <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> package, "
"&amarok; cannot generate the moodbars for your music."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva dela nove izvedbe <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel>: paket "
"<guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel>, ki vsebuje program, ki sprejme glasbeno "
"datoteko in ustvari datoteko .mood, in podporno kodo v &amarok;u ; vir, ki "
"izvaja binarno datoteko in prikazuje Moodbar. Paket <guilabel>Moodbar</"
"guilabel> je odvisen od knjižnic <emphasis>GStreamer</emphasis>. Brez paketa "
"<guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel>, &amarok; ne more ustvariti vrstic razpoloženja "
"za vašo glasbo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As an alternative, there is a new script which will create moodbar files for "
"tracks in an &amarok; playlist; this is an exception to the above. The "
"script needs nothing but &amarok; to work, but it only creates the .mood "
"files as they are played in the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Kot alternativa je na voljo nov skript, ki bo ustvaril datoteke vrstice "
"razpoloženja za skladbe v &amarok; seznam predvajanja; to je izjema od "
"zgoraj navedenega. Skript ne potrebuje nič drugega kot &amarok; da deluje, "
"vendar ustvari samo datoteke .mood, ko se predvajajo na <guilabel>Playlist</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> is due to the work of Gavin Wood and Simon "
"O'Keefe, who designed the algorithms; their original paper is <ulink url="
"\"http://cratoo.de/amarok/ismir-crc.pdf\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> je posledica dela Gavina Wooda in Simona "
"O'Keefeja, ki sta oblikovala algoritme; njihov izvirni dokument je <ulink "
"url=\"http://cratoo.de/amarok/ismir-crc.pdf\">tukaj</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5825
#, no-c-format
msgid "Summary of Requirements"
msgstr "Povzetek zahtev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> binary, in your PATH (it should be listed "
"upon running <userinput>which moodbar</userinput> from a console) &mdash; "
"Remember to configure the <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> package with proper "
"path, &eg; build and install with commands <userinput>./autogen.sh --"
"prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix gstreamer-1.0` &amp;&amp; make &amp;"
"&amp; sudo make install</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Binarna datoteka <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> v vaši POTI (navedena bi "
"morala biti ob zagonu <userinput>which moodbar</userinput> iz konzole) "
"&mdash; Ne pozabite konfigurirati paketa <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> z "
"ustrezno potjo, &eg; zgradite in namestite z ukazi <userinput>./autogen.sh --"
"prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix gstreamer-1.0` &amp;&amp; narediti &amp;"
"&amp; sudo make install</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The GStreamer 1.0 library and <link linkend=\"supported-filetypes\">plugins</"
"link> for the formats you want <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> to be able to "
"analyse. (An earlier GStreamer 0.10 based version is also still available "
"for some distributions)"
msgstr ""
"Knjižnica GStreamer 1.0 in <link linkend=\"supported-filetypes\">vtičniki</"
"link> za formate, za katere želite, da jih <guilabel>Moodbar</guilabel> "
"lahko analizira. (Za nekatere distribucije je še vedno na voljo prejšnja "
"različica, ki temelji na GStreamer 0.10)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Fastest Fourier Transform In The West</emphasis> (<ulink url="
"\"http://www.fftw.org\">fftw.org</ulink>) FFTW library version 3.0 or above "
"(at least single-precision floating point version - libfftw3f) &mdash; If "
"your platform does not provide this for you or you need to compile your own "
"version, remember to configure the FFTW package with <userinput>./configure "
"--enable-single</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Najhitrejša Fourierjeva transformacija na Zahodu</emphasis> "
"(<ulink url=\"http://www.fftw.org\">fftw.org</ulink>) Knjižnica FFTW "
"različica 3.0 ali novejša (vsaj en- natančna različica s plavajočo vejico - "
"libfftw3f) &mdash; Če vaša platforma tega ne omogoča ali morate prevesti "
"svojo različico, ne pozabite konfigurirati paketa FFTW z <userinput>./"
"configure --enable-single</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A version of &amarok; with a <guilabel>Use moods</guilabel> option in the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> section of the configuration screen. This means "
"1.4.4 or higher in the 1.4 series or 2.2.2 or higher in the 2.x series."
msgstr ""
"Različica &amarok; z možnostjo <guilabel>Uporabi razpoloženja</guilabel> v "
"razdelku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> konfiguracijskega zaslona. To pomeni "
"1.4.4 ali višje v seriji 1.4 ali 2.2.2 ali višje v seriji 2.x."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Systems with package managers should automatically install the GStreamer "
"plugins and FFTW along with the Moodbar package if available; this "
"information is provided mostly for people who want or need to compile from "
"source or manually install packages, or where the distribution specific "
"instructions are outdated and no updated moodbar package is yet available."
msgstr ""
"Sistemi z upravljalniki paketov morajo samodejno namestiti vtičnike "
"GStreamer in FFTW skupaj s paketom Moodbar, če je na voljo; te informacije "
"so večinoma na voljo ljudem, ki želijo ali morajo prevesti iz izvorne kode "
"ali ročno namestiti pakete ali kjer so posebna navodila za distribucijo "
"zastarela in še ni na voljo posodobljen paket moodbar."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently .mood files <emphasis>must</emphasis> be generated manually. "
"&amarok; cannot do it for you. To do this for your entire collection, use "
"the <link linkend=\"moodbar-file-generation-script\">Moodbar File Generation "
"Script</link> described below."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno je datoteke .mood <emphasis>treba</emphasis> ustvariti ročno. "
"&amarok; ne more storiti namesto vas. Če želite to narediti za celotno "
"zbirko, uporabite spodaj opisani <link linkend=\"moodbar-file-generation-"
"script\">skript za generiranje datoteke Moodbar</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable the display of moodbars in &amarok;, activate it in the "
"configuration: <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>General</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Show "
"Moodbar in Progress Slider</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Moodbars should now "
"appear in the track sliders in the player window and <guilabel>Playlist</"
"guilabel>; there will also be a mood field that you may add to your playlist "
"layouts."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti prikaz vrstic razpoloženja v &amarok;u, jo aktivirajte v "
"konfiguraciji: <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Amarok</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Splošno</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Pokaži vrstico razpoloženja v Drsnik napredka</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Vrstice razpoloženja bi se morale zdaj prikazati "
"v drsnikih skladb v oknu predvajalnika in <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel>; na "
"voljo bo tudi polje razpoloženja, ki ga lahko dodate na svoje postavitve "
