msgid "Amarok Menu"
msgstr "Meni Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some of the common actions in &amarok; are here, mostly to control media "
"playback."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera pogosta dejanja v &amarok;u so tukaj, predvsem za nadzor "
"predvajanja medijev."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:6960
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Amarok Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni Amarok</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6963
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Amarok Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Amarok</para>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6975 index.docbook:7261 index.docbook:8104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Bližnjica"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:6981
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Play Media...</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Play Media ...</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6984
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a media file to be played."
msgstr "Odpre predstavnostno datoteko za predvajanje."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:6987 index.docbook:8153
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:6992
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Previous Track</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Prejšnja skladba</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6995
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skips back to the last track played within your current session."
msgstr "Preskoči nazaj na zadnjo predvajano skladbo v trenutni seji."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7003
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Play/Pause</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Predvajaj/Premor</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7006
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts or temporarily stops the playing of the current media file."
msgstr "Začne ali začasno ustavi predvajanje trenutne medijske datoteke."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:7009 index.docbook:8161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Space"
msgstr "Vesolje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7014
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Stop</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Ustavi</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7017
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stops all playback in progress."
msgstr "Ustavi vse predvajanje v teku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7025
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop after current Track"
msgstr "Ustavi po trenutni skladbi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Waits until the current track ends before stopping the playback. This is "
"useful when using a playlist."
msgstr ""
"Počaka, da se trenutna skladba konča, preden ustavi predvajanje. To je "
"uporabno pri uporabi seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7036
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Next Track</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Naslednja skladba</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skips playback to the next media file in your playlist."
msgstr ""
"Preskoči predvajanje na naslednjo predstavnostno datoteko na seznamu "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7044
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Quit</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Zapri</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7047
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exits out of &amarok;."
msgstr "Zapusti &amarok;."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:7050 index.docbook:8193
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7058
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>View Menu</title>"
msgstr "<title>Meni Pogled</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This top-level menu contains options to adjust the layout of &amarok;, and a "
"checkbox to lock the configuration; use this to prevent any accidental "
"changes to the &amarok; window layout."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni na najvišji ravni vsebuje možnosti za prilagajanje postavitve "
"&amarok; in potrditveno polje za zaklepanje konfiguracije; uporabite to, da "
"preprečite morebitne nenamerne spremembe datoteke &amarok; postavitev oken."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:7069
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>View Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ogled menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7072
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>View Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Pogled</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the Amarok Toolbar"
msgstr "Spreminjanje orodne vrstice Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also two radio buttons in this menu, which are used to choose "
"which <emphasis>Toolbar</emphasis> &amarok; will use. The <emphasis>Main "
"Toolbar</emphasis> has a larger height and slightly different controls than "
"the <emphasis>Slim Toolbar.</emphasis> The <emphasis>Main Toolbar</emphasis> "
"contains two main control buttons: a <guilabel>Play</guilabel> / "
"<guilabel>Pause</guilabel> button and a button for controlling the volume. "
"It also displays the name of the current media file and a slider for "
"showing, as well as changing, the position of playback. More about <link "
"linkend=\"toolbar\">the Toolbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"V tem meniju sta tudi dva izbirna gumba, ki se uporabljata za izbiro "
"<emphasis>Orodne vrstice</emphasis> &amarok; bo uporabil. <emphasis>Glavna "
"orodna vrstica</emphasis> ima večjo višino in nekoliko drugačne kontrolnike "
"kot <emphasis>Ozka orodna vrstica.</emphasis> <emphasis>Glavna orodna "
"vrstica</emphasis> vsebuje dva glavna gumba za upravljanje: <guilabel> Gumb "
"za predvajanje</guilabel> / <guilabel>Premor</guilabel> in gumb za nadzor "
"glasnosti. Prikaže tudi ime trenutne medijske datoteke in drsnik za prikaz "
"in spreminjanje položaja predvajanja. Več o <link linkend=\"toolbar\">orodni "
"vrstici</link>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:7088
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Main Toolbar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavna orodna vrstica</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7091
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Main Toolbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavna orodna vrstica</para>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:7104
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Slim Toolbar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Orodna vrstica Slim</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Slim Toolbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Orodna vrstica Slim</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amarok Window Layouts"
msgstr "Postavitve oken Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Lock Layout</guilabel> button is unchecked, the "
"<emphasis>Media Sources</emphasis>, <emphasis>Context</emphasis> and "
"<emphasis>Playlist</emphasis> tabs can be toggled and many layouts can be "
"created as shown below:"
msgstr ""
"Če gumb <guilabel>Zakleni postavitev</guilabel> ni označen, lahko "
"preklapljate med zavihki <emphasis>Medijski viri</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Kontekst</emphasis> in <emphasis>Seznam predvajanja</emphasis> in "
"številne postavitve lahko ustvarite, kot je prikazano spodaj:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist Menu"
