#, no-c-format
msgid "Network Request Viewer"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik omrežnih zahtev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the Network Requests Viewer."
msgstr "Prikaže pregledovalnik omrežnih zahtev."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7557
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Update Collection</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Posodobi zbirko</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checks the tracks in your collection and updates the database."
msgstr "Preveri skladbe v vaši zbirki in posodobi bazo podatkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Statistics.."
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj statistiko.."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7568
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the Statistics Synchronization dialog."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno za sinhronizacijo statistike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7574
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Bookmark Manager</title>"
msgstr "<title>Upravljalnik zaznamkov</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bookmark manager allows you to bookmark different kinds of things to "
"recall them later. You can also create folders to organize your collection "
"of bookmarks. The search box provides a convenient way to find bookmarks. "
"The context menu offers the possibility to <guilabel>Load</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Delete</guilabel> the bookmark."
msgstr ""
"Upravljalnik zaznamkov vam omogoča dodajanje različnih vrst stvari med "
"zaznamke, da jih pozneje prikličete. Ustvarite lahko tudi mape za "
"organiziranje svoje zbirke zaznamkov. Iskalno polje omogoča priročen način "
"iskanja zaznamkov. Kontekstni meni ponuja možnost <guilabel>Naloži</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Izbriši</guilabel> zaznamek."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7602
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark Context View Applets"
msgstr "Programčki za kontekstni pogled med zaznamke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7605
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the currently used view applets."
msgstr "Shrani trenutno uporabljene programčke pogleda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark Media Source View"
msgstr "Zaznamek Pogled vira medija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the current view of the media source tree."
msgstr "Shrani trenutni pogled drevesa medijskega vira."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark Playlist Setup"
msgstr "Zaznamek Nastavitev seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the current playlist setup."
msgstr "Shrani trenutno nastavitev seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark Track Position"
msgstr "Položaj skladbe med zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the position in the current track."
msgstr "Shrani položaj v trenutni skladbi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows all albums in your collection. Here you can set custom album covers "
"and fetch missing ones. More about the <link linkend=\"cover-manager\">Cover "
"Manager</link>, shown below."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže vse albume v vaši zbirki. Tukaj lahko nastavite naslovnice albumov "
"po meri in pridobite manjkajoče. Več o <link linkend=\"cover-manager"
"\">Upravljalnik naslovnic</link> je prikazano spodaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7653
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Equalizer</title>"
msgstr "<title>Izenačevalnik</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides the possibility to configure sound settings. You can choose between "
"manually adjusting the settings and using templates. Right now, the "
"<emphasis>Phonon</emphasis> <emphasis>GStreamer</emphasis> is required for a "
"functional equalizer."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja možnost konfiguracije zvočnih nastavitev. Izbirate lahko med ročnim "
"prilagajanjem nastavitev in uporabo predlog. Trenutno je za funkcionalni "
"izenačevalnik potreben <emphasis>Phonon</emphasis> <emphasis>GStreamer</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network Requests Viewer"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik omrežnih zahtev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Network Requests Viewer</guilabel> allows you to monitor the "
"network requests made by &amarok;. Selecting this option will open this "
"window:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pregledovalnik omrežnih zahtev</guilabel> vam omogoča spremljanje "
"omrežnih zahtev, ki jih naredi &amarok;. Če izberete to možnost, se odpre to "
"okno:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7687
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Update Collection</title>"
msgstr "<title>Posodobi zbirko</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checks the files in the folders you defined as your collection. New files "
"will be added and missing ones removed from the left pane."
msgstr ""
"Preveri datoteke v mapah, ki ste jih določili kot svojo zbirko. V levem "
"podoknu bodo dodane nove datoteke, manjkajoče pa odstranjene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7691
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Statistics"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj statistiko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to synchronize statistics of your various "
"collections. This is a new feature in &amarok; since version 2.7 For more "
"information, see also <link linkend=\"statistics-synchronization"
"\">Statistics Synchronization Between Collections and with Last.fm</link> in "
"the handbook."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča sinhronizacijo statistike vaših različnih zbirk. To "
"je nova funkcija v &amarok;u od različice 2.7 Za več informacij glejte tudi "
"<link linkend=\"statistics-synchronization\">Sinhronizacija statistike med "
"zbirkami in z Last.fm</link> v priročniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7696
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7697
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is where you change settings and configure &amarok;."
msgstr "Tukaj spremenite nastavitve in konfigurirate &amarok;."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:7707
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Amarok Settings Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni z nastavitvami Amarok</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7710
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Amarok Settings Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni z nastavitvami Amarok</para>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7727
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Show Menubar</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Pokaži menijsko vrstico</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hide the menu bar. Show it again by pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>M</"
"keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"Skrij menijsko vrstico. Ponovno ga pokažite s pritiskom <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7735
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Replay Gain Mode</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Način povečanja ponovitve</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to set the Replay Gain mode; <guilabel>Off</guilabel>, by "
"<guilabel>Track</guilabel>, or by <guilabel>Album</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Omogoča nastavitev načina Replay Gain; <guilabel>Izklopljeno</guilabel>, "
"glede na <guilabel>Skladbo</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Album</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7743
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Configure Shortcuts...</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7746
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to make custom keyboard shortcuts"
msgstr "Omogoča ustvarjanje bližnjic na tipkovnici po meri"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7751
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Configure Amarok...</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Konfiguriraj Amarok...</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure General options, Internet Services, Playback, Notifications, and "
"Database"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte splošne možnosti, internetne storitve, predvajanje, obvestila "
"in zbirko podatkov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7760
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Show Menubar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pokaži menijsko vrstico</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7761
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clicking this option will hide the menu bar."
msgstr "Če kliknete to možnost, boste skrili menijsko vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The only way to show the menu bar again is by pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>, because you can't de-select the menu option "
"when no menu bar is shown. More about the <link linkend=\"menu-and-command-"
"reference\">Menus in the Menubar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Edini način, da ponovno prikažete menijsko vrstico, je, da pritisnete "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>, ker ne morete preklicati "
"izbire menijske možnosti, ko menijska vrstica ni prikazana. Več o <link "
"linkend=\"menu-and-command-reference\">menijih v menijski vrstici</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7766
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Replay Gain Mode</title>"
msgstr "<title>Način povečanja ponovitve</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The replay gain mode will change the volume depending on meta information of "
"the track. More about replay gain: <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Replay_Gain\">Wikipedia entry for replay gain</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Način povečanja ponovnega predvajanja bo spremenil glasnost glede na "
"metainformacije skladbe. Več o povečanju ponovitve: <ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Replay_Gain\">Vnos v Wikipediji za pridobitev ponovitve</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch the replay gain mechanism off, use a track-based or the album-"
"based replay gain."
msgstr ""
"Mehanizem za ponovno predvajanje lahko izklopite, uporabite ojačenje za "
"ponovno predvajanje na podlagi skladbe ali albuma."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7772
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Configure Shortcuts...</title>"
msgstr "<title>Konfiguriraj bližnjice ...</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change and define new keyboard shortcuts, or turn on multimedia keys if your "
"keyboard has them. More about <link linkend=\"keybinding-reference"
"\">Shortcuts</link>."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite in določite nove bližnjice na tipkovnici ali vklopite "
"multimedijske tipke, če jih ima vaša tipkovnica. Več o <link linkend="
"\"keybinding-reference\">Bližnjicah</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7776
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Configure Amarok...</title>"
msgstr "<title>Konfigurirajte Amarok ...</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:7785
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure Amarok</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfigurirajte Amarok</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7788
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Configure Amarok</para>"
msgstr "<para>Konfigurirajte Amarok</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure many aspects of &amarok;. Details in <link linkend=\"configuring-"
"amarok\">Configuring Amarok</link>."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte številne vidike &amarok;. Podrobnosti v <link linkend="
"\"configuring-amarok\">Konfiguriranje Amaroka</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7797
