#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7828
#, no-c-format
msgid "Report Bug..."
msgstr "Prijavi napako..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7831
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Report bugs to the bug tracker directly, with much of your information "
"automatically supplied to the database form."
msgstr ""
"Prijavi hrošče neposredno v sledilnik hrošča, pri čemer se večina vaših "
"informacij samodejno vnese v obrazec zbirke podatkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7836
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amarok Handbook"
msgstr "Priročnik Amarok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7839
#, no-c-format
msgid "This Handbook in Docbook format."
msgstr "Ta priročnik v formatu Docbook."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7844
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send a Comment to the Developers"
msgstr "Pošljite komentar razvijalcem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send a brief comment to &amarok; developers. Do NOT use to send bug reports."
msgstr ""
"Pošlji kratek komentar na &amarok; razvijalci. NE uporabljajte za pošiljanje "
"poročil o napakah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7852
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Feedback Icons"
msgstr "Pokaži ikone povratnih informacij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7855
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check to show feedback icons on every &amarok; screen and sub-menu."
msgstr ""
"Označite za prikaz ikon povratnih informacij na vsakem &amarok; zaslonu in "
"podmeni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7860
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch Application Language..."
msgstr "Preklop jezika aplikacije..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7863
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change &amarok; menus and label language or back-up language."
msgstr "Spremeni &amarok; jezik menijev in nalepk ali rezervni jezik."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7868
#, no-c-format
msgid "About Amarok"
msgstr "O Amaroku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7871
#, no-c-format
msgid "&amarok; version, web site, contributors and donors."
msgstr "&amarok; različica, spletna stran, sodelavci in donatorji."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Diagnostics"
msgstr "Diagnostika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7879
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays complete information necessary for filing good bug reports, such as "
"Amarok Version, KDE, Qt, Phonon, and Phonon Backend versions, and whether or "
"not PulseAudio is installed, as well as what Amarok Scripts are installed, "
"and whether or not they are running. There is a button on the bottom to copy "
"the information to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže popolne informacije, ki so potrebne za vložitev dobrih poročil o "
"napakah, kot so različice Amarok Version, KDE, Qt, Phonon in Phonon Backend "
"ter ali je PulseAudio nameščen ali ne, kot tudi kateri skripti Amarok so "
"nameščeni in ali se izvajajo ali ne. Na dnu je gumb za kopiranje informacij "
"v odložišče."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:7884
#, no-c-format
msgid "About KDE"
msgstr "O KDE"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information about KDE, and links to join and support KDE."
msgstr "Informacije o KDE in povezave za pridružitev in podporo KDE."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7896
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keybinding Reference"
msgstr "Referenca za vezavo tipk"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7897
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice na tipkovnici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keyboard shortcuts let you quickly access &amarok;<command>'s</command> "
"power. Change the shortcuts using <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Bližnjice na tipkovnici vam omogočajo hiter dostop do moči &amarok;"
"<command></command>. Spremenite bližnjice z <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

