#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:8400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select an action, that opens a sub-window where you can choose "
"between two radio buttons, <guilabel>Default</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Custom</guilabel>. If you choose <guilabel>Default</guilabel> "
"you'll use the default shortcut. If you choose <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> "
"you'll configure and use your shortcut for this action."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete dejanje, se odpre podokno, kjer lahko izbirate med dvema "
"izbirnima gumboma, <guilabel>Privzeto</guilabel> in <guilabel>Po meri</"
"guilabel>. Če izberete <guilabel>Privzeto</guilabel>, boste uporabili "
"privzeto bližnjico. Če izberete <guilabel>Po meri</guilabel>, boste za to "
"dejanje konfigurirali in uporabili svojo bližnjico."

